#. Tag: title
#: development.docbook:1459
#, no-c-format
msgid "Metadata"
msgstr "Metapodatki"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:1461
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The &JSON; object of the <userinput>metadata</userinput> key contains "
"relevant information on the theme. This object has the following keys:"
msgstr ""
"&JSON; predmet ključa <userinput>metapodatki</userinput> vsebuje ustrezne "
"informacije o temi. Ta predmet ima naslednje ključe:"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:1465
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<userinput>name</userinput>: It is a <emphasis>string</emphasis> sets the "
"name of the language. It appears in the menus and dialogs afterwards. It is "
"mandatory."
msgstr ""
"<userinput>ime</userinput>: To je <emphasis>niz</emphasis>, ki nastavi ime "
"jezika. Kasneje se prikaže v menijih in pogovornih oknih. Je obvezno."

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:1469
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<userinput>revision</userinput>: It is an <emphasis>integer</emphasis> "
"number that specifies the current revision of the theme file. Whenever you "
"update a color theme file, make sure to increase this number. It is "
"mandatory."
msgstr ""
"<userinput>revizija</userinput>: To je <emphasis>celo</emphasis> število, ki "
"določa trenutno revizijo datoteke teme. Kadarkoli posodobite datoteko barvne "
"teme, povečajte to število. Je obvezno."

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:1474
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<userinput>license</userinput>: It is a <emphasis>string</emphasis> that "
"defines the license of the theme, using the identifier <userinput>SPDX-"
"License-Identifier</userinput> from the standard <ulink url=\"https://spdx."
"dev/\">SPDX license communication format</ulink>. It is optional."
msgstr ""
"<userinput>licenca</userinput>: To je <emphasis>niz</emphasis>, ki definira "
"licenco teme z uporabo identifikatorja <userinput>SPDX-License-Identifier</"
"userinput> iz standardnega <ulink url=\"https://spdx.dev/\">komunikacijski "
"format licence SPDX</ulink>. To ni obvezno."

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:1479
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can see the full list of SPDX license identifiers <ulink url=\"https://"
"spdx.org/licenses/\">here</ulink>."
msgstr ""
"Celoten seznam identifikatorjev licenc SPDX si lahko ogledate <ulink url="
"\"https://spdx.org/licenses/\">tukaj</ulink>."

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:1482
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<userinput>copyright</userinput>: It is an <emphasis>array</emphasis> of "
"<emphasis>strings</emphasis> that specifies the authors of the theme, using "
"the identifier <userinput>SPDX-FileCopyrightText</userinput> from the "
"standard <ulink url=\"https://spdx.dev/\">SPDX license communication format</"
"ulink>. It is optional."
msgstr ""
"<userinput>copyright</userinput>: Je <emphasis>niz</emphasis> "
"<emphasis>nizov</emphasis>, ki določa avtorje teme z uporabo identifikatorja "
"<userinput>SPDX-FileCopyrightText</userinput> iz standardne <ulink url="
"\"https://spdx.dev/\">komunikacijske oblike licence SPDX</ulink>. To ni "
"obvezno."

#. Tag: programlisting
#: development.docbook:1490
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"\"metadata\": {\n"
"    \"name\" : \"Breeze Light\",\n"
"    \"revision\" : 5,\n"
"    \"copyright\": [\n"
"        \"SPDX-FileCopyrightText: 2016 Volker Krause &lt;vkrause@kde.org&gt;"
"\",\n"
"        \"SPDX-FileCopyrightText: 2016 Dominik Haumann &lt;dhaumann@kde."
"org&gt;\"\n"
"    ],\n"
"    \"license\": \"SPDX-License-Identifier: MIT\"\n"
"}"
msgstr ""
"\"metapodatki\": {\n"
"     \"ime\": \"svetloba vetriča\",\n"
"     \"revizija\" : 5,\n"
"     \"avtorske pravice\": [\n"
"         \"SPDX-FileCopyrightText: 2016 Volker Krause &lt;vkrause@kde.org&gt;"
"\",\n"
"         \"SPDX-FileCopyrightText: 2016 Dominik Haumann &lt;dhaumann@kde."
"org&gt;\"\n"
"     ],\n"
"     \"license\": \"SPDX-Identifikator licence: MIT\"\n"
"}"

#. Tag: title
#: development.docbook:1498
#, no-c-format
msgid "Colors in Detail"
msgstr "Barve v podrobnostih"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:1500
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This section details all the available color attributes and available color "
"settings."
msgstr ""
"V tem razdelku so podrobno opisani vsi razpoložljivi barvni atributi in "
"razpoložljive barvne nastavitve."

#. Tag: title
#: development.docbook:1505
#, no-c-format
msgid "Editor Colors"
msgstr "Barve urejevalnika"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:1507
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Corresponds to the colors of the <link linkend=\"kate-part\">text editing "
"area</link>."
msgstr ""
"Ustreza barvam <link linkend=\"kate-part\">območja za urejanje besedila</"
"link>."

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:1509
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In the <link linkend=\"color-themes-json\">&JSON; theme file</link>, the "
"respective key <userinput>editor-colors</userinput> has as value an "
"<emphasis>object</emphasis> where each key references an attribute color of "
"the text editor. Here, <userinput>all available keys are mandatory</"
"userinput>, their values are <userinput>strings</userinput> with hexadecimal "
"color codes, like <quote>#00B5CF</quote>."
msgstr ""
"V <link linkend=\"color-themes-json\">&JSON; datoteka teme</link>, ima "
"ustrezen ključ <userinput>barve-urejevalnika</userinput> kot vrednost "
"<emphasis>objekt</emphasis>, kjer se vsak ključ sklicuje na barvo atributa "
"urejevalnika besedila. Tu so <userinput>vsi razpoložljivi ključi obvezni</"
"userinput>, njihove vrednosti so <userinput>nizi</userinput> s "
"šestnajstiškimi barvnimi kodami, kot je <quote>#00B5CF</quote>."

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:1516
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In <link linkend=\"color-themes-gui\">the &GUI; to manage themes of "
"KTextEditor</link>, these attributes can be modified in the "
"<userinput><guilabel>Colors</guilabel></userinput> tab."
msgstr ""
"V <link linkend=\"color-themes-gui\">&GUI; za upravljanje tem KTextEditor</"
"link> lahko te atribute spremenite na zavihku <userinput><guilabel>Barve</"
"guilabel></userinput>."

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:1520
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The available keys are the following; the keys used in the <link linkend="
"\"color-themes-json\">&JSON; file</link> are listed in <emphasis>bold</"
"emphasis>, the names used in the <link linkend=\"color-themes-gui\">&GUI;</"
"link> are shown in parentheses."
msgstr ""
"Na voljo so naslednji ključi; ključi, uporabljeni v <link linkend=\"color-"
"themes-json\">&JSON; datoteke</link> so navedene <emphasis>krepko</"
"emphasis>, imena, uporabljena v <link linkend=\"color-themes-gui\">&GUI;</"
"link>, so prikazana v oklepajih."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: development.docbook:1528
#, no-c-format
msgid "Editor Background Colors"
msgstr "Barve ozadja urejevalnika"

#. Tag: term
#: development.docbook:1534
#, no-c-format
msgid "<userinput>BackgroundColor</userinput> (<guilabel>Text Area</guilabel>)"
msgstr ""
"<userinput>Barva ozadja</userinput> (<guilabel>Območje besedila</guilabel>)"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:1535
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This is the default background for the editor area, it will be the dominant "
"color on the editor area."
msgstr ""
"To je privzeto ozadje za območje urejevalnika in bo prevladujoča barva na "
"območju urejevalnika."

#. Tag: term
#: development.docbook:1545
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<userinput>TextSelection</userinput> (<guilabel>Selected Text</guilabel>)"
msgstr ""
"<userinput>IzbiraBesedila</userinput> (<guilabel>Izbrano besedilo</guilabel>)"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:1546
#, no-c-format
msgid "This is the background for selected text."
msgstr "To je ozadje za izbrano besedilo."

#. Tag: term
#: development.docbook:1556
#, no-c-format
msgid "<userinput>CurrentLine</userinput> (<guilabel>Current Line</guilabel>)"
msgstr ""
"<userinput>TrenutnaVrstica</userinput> (<guilabel>Trenutna vrstica</"
"guilabel>)"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:1557
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Set the color for the current line. Setting this a bit different from the "
"Normal text background helps to keep focus on the current line."
msgstr ""
"Nastavite barvo za trenutno vrstico. Če to nastavite nekoliko drugačno od "
"običajnega ozadja besedila, pomaga ohraniti fokus na trenutni vrstici."

#. Tag: term
#: development.docbook:1568
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<userinput>SearchHighlight</userinput> (<guilabel>Search Highlight</"
"guilabel>)"
msgstr ""
"<userinput>IščiPoudarek</userinput> (<guilabel>Išči poudarek</guilabel>)"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:1569
#, no-c-format
msgid "Set the color for the text that matches your last search."
msgstr "Nastavite barvo za besedilo, ki se ujema z vašim zadnjim iskanjem."

#. Tag: term
#: development.docbook:1579
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<userinput>ReplaceHighlight</userinput> (<guilabel>Replace Highlight</"
"guilabel>)"
msgstr ""
"<userinput>Zamenjaj poudarek</userinput> (<guilabel>Zamenjaj poudarek</"
"guilabel>)"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:1580
#, no-c-format
msgid "Set the color for the text that matches your last replace operation."
msgstr ""
"Nastavite barvo za besedilo, ki se ujema z vašo zadnjo operacijo zamenjave."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: development.docbook:1594
#, no-c-format
msgid "Icon Border"
msgstr "Obroba ikone"

#. Tag: term
#: development.docbook:1599
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<userinput>IconBorder</userinput> (<guilabel>Background Area</guilabel>)"
msgstr ""
"<userinput>ObrobaIkone</userinput> (<guilabel>Območje ozadja</guilabel>)"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:1600
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This color is used for the marks, line numbers and folding marker borders in "
"the left side of the editor view when they are displayed."
msgstr ""
"Ta barva se uporablja za oznake, številke vrstic in robove pregibnih oznak "
"na levi strani pogleda urejevalnika, ko so prikazani."

#. Tag: term
#: development.docbook:1606
#, no-c-format
msgid "<userinput>LineNumbers</userinput> (<guilabel>Line Numbers</guilabel>)"
msgstr ""
"<userinput>Številke vrstic</userinput> (<guilabel>Številke vrstic</guilabel>)"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:1607
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This color is used to draw the line numbers on the left side of the view "
"when displayed."
msgstr ""
"Ta barva se uporablja za risanje številk vrstic na levi strani pogleda, ko "
"je prikazan."

#. Tag: term
#: development.docbook:1612
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<userinput>CurrentLineNumber</userinput> (<guilabel>Current Line Number</"
"guilabel>)"
msgstr ""
"<userinput>ŠtevilkaTrenutneVrstice</userinput> (<guilabel>Trenutna številka "
"vrstice</guilabel>)"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:1613
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This color is used to draw the line number of the current line, on the left "
"side of the view when displayed. Setting this a bit different from "
"<quote>LineNumbers</quote> helps to keep focus on the current line."
msgstr ""
"Ta barva se uporablja za risanje številke vrstice trenutne vrstice na levi "
"strani pogleda, ko je prikazana. Če to nastavite nekoliko drugačno od "
"<quote>številkeVrstic</quote>, pomaga ohraniti fokus na trenutno vrstico."

#. Tag: term
#: development.docbook:1620
#, no-c-format
msgid "<userinput>Separator</userinput> (<guilabel>Separator</guilabel>)"
msgstr "<userinput>Ločilo</userinput> (<guilabel>Ločilo</guilabel>)"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:1621
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This color is used to draw the vertical line that separates the icon border "
"from the background of the text area."
msgstr ""
"Ta barva se uporablja za risanje navpične črte, ki ločuje rob ikone od "
"ozadja področja besedila."

#. Tag: term
#: development.docbook:1631
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<userinput>WordWrapMarker</userinput> (<guilabel>Word Wrap Marker</guilabel>)"
msgstr ""
"<userinput>OznakaZaPrelomBesed</userinput> (<guilabel>Oznaka za prelom "
"besed</guilabel>)"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:1632
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This color is used to draw a pattern to the left of dynamically wrapped "
"lines when those are aligned vertically, as well as for the static word wrap "
"marker."
msgstr ""
"Ta barva se uporablja za risanje vzorca na levi strani dinamično zavitih "
"črt, ko so te poravnane navpično, kot tudi za statični marker za prelom "
"besed."

#. Tag: term
#: development.docbook:1643
#, no-c-format
msgid "<userinput>CodeFolding</userinput> (<guilabel>Code Folding</guilabel>)"
msgstr ""
"<userinput>ZlaganjeKode</userinput> (<guilabel>Zlaganje Kode</guilabel>)"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:1644
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This color is used to highlight the section of code that would be folded "
"when you click on the code folding arrow to the left of a document. For more "
"information, see <link linkend=\"advanced-editing-tools-code-folding\">the "
"code folding documentation</link>."
msgstr ""
"Ta barva se uporablja za označevanje dela kode, ki bi bil prepognjen, ko "
"kliknete puščico za prepogibanje kode na levi strani dokumenta. Za več "
"informacij glejte <link linkend=\"advanced-editing-tools-code-folding"
"\">dokumentacijo za zlaganje kode</link>."

#. Tag: term
#: development.docbook:1657
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<userinput>ModifiedLines</userinput> (<guilabel>Modified Lines</guilabel>)"
msgstr ""
"<userinput>SpremenjeneVrstice</userinput> (<guilabel>Spremenjene vrstice</"
"guilabel>)"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:1658
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This color is used to highlight to the left of a document lines that have "
"been modified but not yet saved. For more information, see <xref linkend="
"\"kate-part-line-modification\"/>."
msgstr ""
"Ta barva se uporablja za označevanje vrstic na levi strani dokumenta, ki so "
"bile spremenjene, vendar še niso shranjene. Za več informacij glejte <xref "
"linkend=\"kate-part-line-modification\"/>."

#. Tag: term
#: development.docbook:1664
#, no-c-format
msgid "<userinput>SavedLines</userinput> (<guilabel>Saved Lines</guilabel>)"
msgstr ""
"<userinput>ShranjeneVrstice</userinput> (<guilabel>Shranjene vrstice</"
"guilabel>)"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:1665
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This color is used to highlight to the left of a document lines that have "
"been modified this session and saved. For more information, see <xref "
"linkend=\"kate-part-line-modification\"/>."
msgstr ""
"Ta barva se uporablja za označevanje vrstic na levi strani dokumenta, ki so "
"bile v tej seji spremenjene in shranjene. Za več informacij glejte <xref "
"linkend=\"kate-part-line-modification\"/>."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: development.docbook:1680
#, no-c-format
msgid "Text Decorations"
msgstr "Besedilni okraski"

#. Tag: term
#: development.docbook:1685
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<userinput>SpellChecking</userinput> (<guilabel>Spelling Mistake Line</"
"guilabel>)"
msgstr ""
"<userinput>Preverjanje črkovanja</userinput> (<guilabel>Vrstica črkovalnih "
"napak</guilabel>)"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:1686
#, no-c-format
msgid "This color is used to indicate spelling mistakes."
msgstr "Ta barva se uporablja za označevanje črkovalnih napak."

#. Tag: term
#: development.docbook:1695
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<userinput>TabMarker</userinput> (<guilabel>Tab and Space Markers</guilabel>)"
msgstr ""
"<userinput>Označevalnik zavihkov</userinput> (<guilabel>Označevalniki "
"zavihkov in presledkov</guilabel>)"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:1696
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This color is used to draw white space indicators, when they are enabled."
msgstr ""
"Ta barva se uporablja za risanje indikatorjev praznega prostora, ko so "
"omogočeni."

#. Tag: term
#: development.docbook:1706
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<userinput>IndentationLine</userinput> (<guilabel>Indentation Line</"
"guilabel>)"
msgstr ""
"<userinput>VrsticaVdolbine</userinput> (<guilabel>Vrstica vdolbine</"
"guilabel>)"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:1707
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This color is used to draw a line to the left of indented blocks, if <link "
"linkend=\"appearance-general\">that feature is enabled</link>."
msgstr ""
"Ta barva se uporablja za risanje črte levo od zamaknjenih blokov, če je "
"<link linkend=\"appearance-general\">ta funkcija omogočena</link>."

#. Tag: term
#: development.docbook:1717
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<userinput>BracketMatching</userinput> (<guilabel>Bracket Highlight</"
"guilabel>)"
msgstr ""
"<userinput>OznačevanjeOklepaja</userinput> (<guilabel>Označevanje oklepaja</"
"guilabel>)"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:1718
#, no-c-format
msgid "This color is used to draw the background of matching brackets."
msgstr "Ta barva se uporablja za risanje ozadja ujemajočih se oklepajev."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: development.docbook:1732
#, no-c-format
msgid "Marker Colors"
msgstr "Barve markerjev"

#. Tag: term
#: development.docbook:1737
#, no-c-format
msgid "<userinput>MarkBookmark</userinput> (<guilabel>Bookmark</guilabel>)"
msgstr "<userinput>OznačiZaznamek</userinput> (<guilabel>Zaznamek</guilabel>)"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:1738
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This color is used to indicate bookmarks. Note that this color has an "
"opacity of 22% (and 33% for the current line) with respect to the "
"background. For more information, see <xref linkend=\"kate-part-bookmarks\"/"
">."
msgstr ""
"Ta barva se uporablja za označevanje zaznamkov. Upoštevajte, da ima ta barva "
"motnost 22 % (in 33 % za trenutno vrstico) glede na ozadje. Za več "
"informacij glejte <xref linkend=\"kate-part-bookmarks\"/>."

#. Tag: term
#: development.docbook:1749
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<userinput>MarkBreakpointActive</userinput> (<guilabel>Active Breakpoint</"
"guilabel>)"
msgstr ""
"<userinput>OznačiAktivnoTočkoPrekinitve</userinput> (<guilabel>Aktivna točka "
"prekinitve</guilabel>)"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:1750
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This color is used by the GDB plugin to indicate an active breakpoint. "
"Notice that this color has an opacity to the background. For more "
"information, see <ulink url=\"help:/kate/kate-application-plugin-gdb.html"
"\">the GDB Plugin documentation</ulink>."
msgstr ""
"To barvo uporablja vtičnik GDB za označevanje aktivne prekinitvene točke. "
"Upoštevajte, da ima ta barva motnost ozadja. Za več informacij si oglejte "
"<ulink url=\"help:/kate/kate-application-plugin-gdb.html\">dokumentacijo "
"vtičnika GDB</ulink>."

#. Tag: term
#: development.docbook:1757
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<userinput>MarkBreakpointReached</userinput> (<guilabel>Reached Breakpoint</"
"guilabel>)"
msgstr ""
"<userinput>OznačiDoseženoTočkoPrekinitve</userinput> (<guilabel>Dosežena "
"točka prekinitve</guilabel>)"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:1758
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This color is used by the GDB plugin to indicate a breakpoint you have "
"reached while debugging. Notice that this color has an opacity to the "
"background. For more information, see <ulink url=\"help:/kate/kate-"
"application-plugin-gdb.html\">the GDB Plugin documentation</ulink>."
msgstr ""
"To barvo uporablja vtičnik GDB za označevanje prekinitvene točke, ki ste jo "
"dosegli med odpravljanjem napak. Upoštevajte, da ima ta barva motnost "
"ozadja. Za več informacij si oglejte <ulink url=\"help:/kate/kate-"
"application-plugin-gdb.html\">dokumentacijo vtičnika GDB</ulink>."

#. Tag: term
#: development.docbook:1766
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<userinput>MarkBreakpointDisabled</userinput> (<guilabel>Disabled "
"Breakpoint</guilabel>)"
msgstr ""
"<userinput>OznačiOnemogočenoPrelomnoTočko</userinput> (<guilabel>Onemogočena "
"prelomna točka</guilabel>)"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:1767
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This color is used by the GDB plugin to indicate an inactive breakpoint. "
"Notice that this color has an opacity to the background. For more "
"information, see <ulink url=\"help:/kate/kate-application-plugin-gdb.html"
"\">the GDB Plugin documentation</ulink>."
msgstr ""
"To barvo uporablja vtičnik GDB za označevanje neaktivne prekinitvene točke. "
"Upoštevajte, da ima ta barva motnost ozadja. Za več informacij si oglejte "
"<ulink url=\"help:/kate/kate-application-plugin-gdb.html\">dokumentacijo "
"vtičnika GDB</ulink>."

#. Tag: term
#: development.docbook:1774
#, no-c-format
msgid "<userinput>MarkExecution</userinput> (<guilabel>Execution</guilabel>)"
msgstr ""
"<userinput>OznačiIzvajanje</userinput> (<guilabel>Izvajanje</guilabel>)"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:1775
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This color is used by the GDB plugin the line presently being executed. "
"Notice that this color has an opacity to the background. For more "
"information, see <ulink url=\"help:/kate/kate-application-plugin-gdb.html"
"\">the GDB Plugin documentation</ulink>."
msgstr ""
"To barvo uporablja vtičnik GDB, ki se trenutno izvaja. Upoštevajte, da ima "
"ta barva motnost ozadja. Za več informacij si oglejte <ulink url=\"help:/"
"kate/kate-application-plugin-gdb.html\">dokumentacijo vtičnika GDB</ulink>."

#. Tag: term
#: development.docbook:1782
#, no-c-format
msgid "<userinput>MarkWarning</userinput> (<guilabel>Warning</guilabel>)"
msgstr ""
"<userinput>Označi opozorilo</userinput> (<guilabel>Opozorilo</guilabel>)"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:1783
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This color is used by the build plugin to indicate a line that has caused a "
"compiler warning. Notice that this color has an opacity to the background. "
"For more information, see <ulink url=\"help:/kate/kate-application-plugin-"
"build.html\">the Build Plugin documentation</ulink>."
msgstr ""
"To barvo uporablja vtičnik gradnje za označevanje vrstice, ki je povzročila "
"opozorilo prevajalnika. Upoštevajte, da ima ta barva motnost ozadja. Za več "
"informacij si oglejte <ulink url=\"help:/kate/kate-application-plugin-build."
"html\">dokumentacijo vtičnika Build Plugin</ulink>."

#. Tag: term
#: development.docbook:1790
#, no-c-format
msgid "<userinput>MarkError</userinput> (<guilabel>Error</guilabel>)"
msgstr "<userinput>OznačiNapake</userinput> (<guilabel>Napaka</guilabel>)"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:1791
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This color is used by the build plugin to indicate a line that has caused a "
"compiler error. Notice that this color has an opacity to the background. For "
"more information, see <ulink url=\"help:/kate/kate-application-plugin-build."
"html\">the Build Plugin documentation</ulink>."
msgstr ""
"To barvo uporablja vtičnik gradnje za označevanje vrstice, ki je povzročila "
"napako prevajalnika. Upoštevajte, da ima ta barva motnost ozadja. Za več "
"informacij si oglejte <ulink url=\"help:/kate/kate-application-plugin-build."
"html\">dokumentacijo vtičnika Build Plugin</ulink>."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: development.docbook:1802
#, no-c-format
msgid "Text Templates &amp; Snippets"
msgstr "Besedilne predloge"

#. Tag: term
#: development.docbook:1807
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<userinput>TemplateBackground</userinput> (<guilabel>Background</guilabel>)"
msgstr "<userinput>OzadjePredloge</userinput> (<guilabel>Ozadje</guilabel>)"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:1808
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This color is used by the &kate; Snippets plugin to mark the background of a "
"snippet. For more information, see <ulink url=\"help:/kate/kate-application-"
"plugin-snippets.html\">the &kate; Snippets documentation</ulink>."
msgstr ""
"To barvo uporablja &kate; Vtičnik izrezkov za označevanje ozadja izrezka. Za "
"več informacij si oglejte <ulink url=\"help:/kate/kate-application-plugin-"
"snippets.html\">dodatek &kate; Dokumentacija izrezkov</ulink>."

#. Tag: term
#: development.docbook:1815
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<userinput>TemplatePlaceholder</userinput> (<guilabel>Editable Placeholder</"
"guilabel>)"
msgstr ""
"<userinput>NadomestniZnakPredloge</userinput> (<guilabel>Urejevalni "
"Nadomestni znak</guilabel>)"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:1816
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This color is used by the &kate; Snippets plugin to mark a placeholder that "
"you can click in to edit manually. For more information, see <ulink url="
"\"help:/kate/kate-application-plugin-snippets.html\">the &kate; Snippets "
"documentation</ulink>."
msgstr ""
"To barvo uporablja &kate; Vtičnik izrezkov za označevanje nadomestnega "
"mesta, ki ga lahko kliknete za ročno urejanje. Za več informacij si oglejte "
"<ulink url=\"help:/kate/kate-application-plugin-snippets.html\">dodatek "
"&kate; Dokumentacija izrezkov</ulink>."

#. Tag: term
#: development.docbook:1823
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<userinput>TemplateFocusedPlaceholder</userinput> (<guilabel>Focused "
"Editable Placeholder</guilabel>)"
msgstr ""
"<userinput>NadomestniZnakOsredotočenNaPredlogo</userinput> "
"(<guilabel>Osredotočen nadomestni znak za urejanje</guilabel>)"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:1824
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This color is used by the &kate; Snippets plugin to mark the placeholder "
"that you are presently editing. For more information, see <ulink url=\"help:/"
"kate/kate-application-plugin-snippets.html\">the &kate; Snippets "
"documentation</ulink>."
msgstr ""
"To barvo uporablja &kate; Vtičnik izrezkov za označevanje nadomestnega "
"mesta, ki ga trenutno urejate. Za več informacij si oglejte <ulink url="
"\"help:/kate/kate-application-plugin-snippets.html\">dodatek &kate; "
"Dokumentacija izrezkov</ulink>."

#. Tag: term
#: development.docbook:1836
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<userinput>TemplateReadOnlyPlaceholder</userinput> (<guilabel>Not Editable "
"Placeholder</guilabel>)"
msgstr ""
"<userinput>OznakaMestaSamoZaBranjePredloge</userinput> (<guilabel>Oznaka "
"mesta, ki je ni mogoče urejati</guilabel>)"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:1837
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This color is used by the &kate; Snippets plugin to mark a placeholder that "
"cannot be edited manually, such as one that is automatically populated. For "
"more information, see <ulink url=\"help:/kate/kate-application-plugin-"
"snippets.html\">the &kate; Snippets documentation</ulink>."
msgstr ""
"To barvo uporablja &kate; Vtičnik izrezkov za označevanje nadomestnega "
"mesta, ki ga ni mogoče urejati ročno, na primer tistega, ki se samodejno "
"izpolni. Za več informacij si oglejte <ulink url=\"help:/kate/kate-"
"application-plugin-snippets.html\">dodatek &kate; Dokumentacija izrezkov</"
"ulink>."

#. Tag: title
#: development.docbook:1859 development.docbook:2270
#, no-c-format
msgid "Default Text Styles"
msgstr "Privzeti slogi besedila"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:1861 development.docbook:2272
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The default text styles are inherited by the highlight text styles, allowing "
"the editor to present text in a very consistent way, for example comment "
"text is using the same style in almost all of the text formats that "
"KSyntaxHighlighting can highlight."
msgstr ""
"Privzete sloge besedila podedujejo slogi besedila za označevanje, kar "
"omogoča urejevalniku, da predstavi besedilo na zelo dosleden način, na "
"primer besedilo komentarja uporablja isti slog v skoraj vseh formatih "
"besedila, ki jih lahko KSyntaxHighlighting označi."

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:1867
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"These text styles can be referenced from the <userinput>default styles</"
"userinput> used in <link linkend=\"highlight\">syntax highlighting</link> "
"definition &XML; files, for example, the <quote>Normal</quote> attribute is "
"equivalent to <quote>dsNormal</quote> in the &XML; files, and "
"<quote>DataType</quote> is equivalent to <quote>dsDataType</quote>. See "
"<xref linkend=\"kate-highlight-default-styles\"/> in the syntax highlighting "
"documentation."
msgstr ""
"Na te besedilne sloge se lahko sklicujete iz <userinput>privzetih slogov</"
"userinput>, uporabljenih v definiciji <link linkend=\"highlight"
"\">označevanja sintakse</link> &XML; datoteke, na primer, je atribut "
"<quote>Normal</quote> enakovreden <quote>dsNormal</quote> v datoteki &XML; "
"datotek in <quote>DataType</quote> je enakovreden <quote>dsDataType</quote>. "
"Glejte <xref linkend=\"kate-highlight-default-styles\"/> v dokumentaciji za "
"označevanje sintakse."

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:1877
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Make sure to choose readable colors with good contrast especially in "
"combination with the <userinput><link linkend=\"color-themes-editor-colors"
"\">Editor Colors</link></userinput>. See <xref linkend=\"color-themes-"
"contrast\"/>."
msgstr ""
"Poskrbite, da boste izbrali berljive barve z dobrim kontrastom, zlasti v "
"kombinaciji z <userinput><link linkend=\"color-themes-editor-colors\">barve "
"urejevalnika</link></userinput>. Glejte <xref linkend=\"color-themes-contrast"
"\"/>."

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:1884
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In the <link linkend=\"color-themes-json\">&JSON; file</link>, the "
"respective key <userinput>text-styles</userinput> has as value an "
"<emphasis>object</emphasis> where each key corresponds to the name of a "
"<emphasis>default text style</emphasis>, which are equivalent to those used "
"in the syntax highlighting definitions. Here, <userinput>all available text "
"style keys are mandatory</userinput>, these are listed below."
msgstr ""
"V <link linkend=\"color-themes-json\">&JSON; datoteka</link>, ima ustrezni "
"ključ <userinput>besedilni slogi</userinput> kot vrednost <emphasis>objekt</"
"emphasis>, kjer vsak ključ ustreza imenu <emphasis>privzetega besedilnega "
"sloga</emphasis> , ki so enakovredni tistim, uporabljenim v definicijah "
"označevanja sintakse. Tu so <userinput>obvezni vsi razpoložljivi ključi "
"sloga besedila</userinput>, ki so navedeni spodaj."

#. Tag: programlisting
#: development.docbook:1891
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"\"text-styles\": {\n"
"    \"Normal\" : {\n"
"        \"text-color\" : \"#1f1c1b\",\n"
"        \"selected-text-color\" : \"#ffffff\",\n"
"        \"bold\" : false,\n"
"        \"italic\" : false,\n"
"        \"underline\" : false,\n"
"        \"strike-through\" : false\n"
"    },\n"
"    \"Keyword\" : {\n"
"        \"text-color\" : \"#1f1c1b\",\n"
"        \"selected-text-color\" : \"#ffffff\",\n"
"        \"bold\" : true\n"
"    },\n"
"    \"Function\" : {\n"
"        \"text-color\" : \"#644a9b\",\n"
"        \"selected-text-color\" : \"#452886\"\n"
"    },\n"
"    <replaceable>The other text style keys...</replaceable>\n"
"}"
msgstr ""
"\"slogi-besedila\": {\n"
"    \"Normal\" : {\n"
"        \"barva besedila\" : \"#1f1c1b\",\n"
"        \"barva-izbranega-besedila\" : \"#ffffff\",\n"
"        \"krepko\" : false,\n"
"        \"ležeče\" : false,\n"
"        \"podčrtano\" : false,\n"
"        \"prečrtano\" : false\n"
"    },\n"
"    \"ključna beseda\" : {\n"
"        \"barva-besedila\" : \"#1f1c1b\",\n"
"        \"barva-izbranega-besedila\" : \"#ffffff\",\n"
"        \"krepko\" : true\n"
"    },\n"
"    \"Function\" : {\n"
"        \"barva-besedila\" : \"#644a9b\",\n"
"        \"barva-izbranega-besedila\" : \"#452886\"\n"
"    },\n"
"    <replaceable>Tipke ostalih slogov besedila...</replaceable>\n"
"}"

#. Tag: term
#: development.docbook:1896
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Each key of <emphasis>default text style</emphasis> has a &JSON; object as "
"its value, where values such as <emphasis>color</emphasis>, <emphasis>bold</"
"emphasis>, <emphasis>italic</emphasis>, etc. are specified. These keys are "
"as follows:"
msgstr ""
"Vsak ključ <emphasis>privzetega sloga besedila</emphasis> ima &JSON; predmet "
"kot svojo vrednost, kjer so določene vrednosti, kot so <emphasis>barva</"
"emphasis>, <emphasis>krepko</emphasis>, <emphasis>ležeče</emphasis> itd. Ti "
"ključi so naslednji:"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:1903
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<userinput>text-color</userinput>: It is a <emphasis>string</emphasis> with "
"the text color in hexadecimal color code. This key/value is required."
msgstr ""
"<userinput>barva besedila</userinput>: Je <emphasis>niz</emphasis> z barvo "
"besedila v šestnajstiški barvni kodi. Ta ključ/vrednost je obvezen."

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:1906
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<userinput>selected-text-color</userinput>: The text color when it is "
"selected is generally the same value as <quote>text-color</quote>. When the "
"text is selected, the background is defined by the value of <link linkend="
"\"variable-pref-colors-selected-text\">TextSelection</link> in the <link "
"linkend=\"color-themes-editor-colors\">Editor Colors</link>, so you must "
"ensure that the text has good contrast and is readable with this background. "
"The value is a <emphasis>string</emphasis> with a hexadecimal color code. "
"This key/value is required."
msgstr ""
"<userinput>barva-izbranega-besedila</userinput>: Barva besedila, ko je "
"izbrana, je na splošno enaka vrednosti kot <quote>barva-besedila</quote>. Ko "
"je besedilo izbrano, je ozadje definirano z vrednostjo <link linkend="
"\"variable-pref-colors-selected-text\">Izbira besedila</link> v <link "
"linkend=\"color-themes-editor-colors\" >Barve urejevalnika</link>, zato "
"morate zagotoviti, da ima besedilo dober kontrast in da je berljivo s tem "
"ozadjem. Vrednost je <emphasis>niz</emphasis> s šestnajstiško barvno kodo. "
"Ta ključ/vrednost je obvezen."

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:1914
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<userinput>bold</userinput>: It is a <emphasis>boolean</emphasis> that "
"determines if the text is in bold. This key is optional, the default value "
"is <userinput>false</userinput>."
msgstr ""
"<userinput>krepko</userinput>: To je <emphasis>logična vrednost</emphasis>, "
"ki določa, ali je besedilo krepko. Ta ključ ni obvezen, privzeta vrednost je "
"<userinput>false</userinput>."

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:1917
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<userinput>italic</userinput>: It is a <emphasis>boolean</emphasis> that "
"determines if the text is curved. This key is optional, the default value is "
"<userinput>false</userinput>."
msgstr ""
"<userinput>ležeče</userinput>: To je <emphasis>logična vrednost</emphasis>, "
"ki določa, ali je besedilo ukrivljeno. Ta ključ ni obvezen, privzeta "
"vrednost je <userinput>false</userinput>."

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:1920
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<userinput>underline</userinput>: It is a <emphasis>boolean</emphasis> that "
"determines if the text is underlined. This key is optional, the default "
"value is <userinput>false</userinput>."
msgstr ""
"<userinput>podčrtano</userinput>: To je <emphasis>logična vrednost</"
"emphasis>, ki določa, ali je besedilo podčrtano. Ta ključ ni obvezen, "
"privzeta vrednost je <userinput>false</userinput>."

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:1923
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<userinput>strike-through</userinput>: It is a <emphasis>boolean</emphasis> "
"that determines if the text is strike through. This key is optional, the "
"default value is <userinput>false</userinput>."
msgstr ""
"<userinput>prečrtano</userinput>: To je <emphasis>logična vrednost</"
"emphasis>, ki določa, ali je besedilo prečrtano. Ta ključ ni obvezen, "
"privzeta vrednost je <userinput>false</userinput>."

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:1926
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<userinput>background-color</userinput>: Determines the background of the "
"text, used for example in alerts in comments. The value is a "
"<emphasis>string</emphasis> with a hexadecimal color code. This key is "
"optional, by default there is no background."
msgstr ""
"<userinput>barva-ozadje</userinput>: Določa ozadje besedila, uporabljeno na "
"primer v opozorilih v komentarjih. Vrednost je <emphasis>niz</emphasis> s "
"šestnajstiško barvno kodo. Ta ključ ni obvezen, privzeto ni ozadja."

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:1930
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<userinput>selected-background-color</userinput>: Determines the background "
"of the text when it is selected. The value is a <emphasis>string</emphasis> "
"with a hexadecimal color code. This key is optional, by default there is no "
"background."
msgstr ""
"<userinput>barva-izbranega-ozadja</userinput>: Določa ozadje besedila, ko je "
"izbrano. Vrednost je <emphasis>niz</emphasis> s šestnajstiško barvno kodo. "
"Ta ključ ni obvezen, privzeto ni ozadja."

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:1938
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In <link linkend=\"color-themes-gui\">the &GUI; to manage color themes of "
"KTextEditor</link>, these attributes can be modified in the "
"<userinput><guilabel>Default Text Styles</guilabel></userinput> tab. The "
"name in the list of styles is using the style configured for the item, "
"providing you with an immediate preview when configuring a style. Each style "
"lets you select common attributes as well as foreground and background "
"colors. To unset a background color, right-click to use the context menu."
msgstr ""
"V <link linkend=\"color-themes-gui\">&GUI; za upravljanje barvnih tem "
"KTextEditor</link> lahko te atribute spremenite na zavihku "
"<userinput><guilabel>Privzeti besedilni slogi</guilabel></userinput>. Ime na "
"seznamu slogov uporablja slog, konfiguriran za element, kar vam omogoča "
"takojšen predogled, ko konfigurirate slog. Vsak slog vam omogoča izbiro "
"skupnih atributov ter barv ospredja in ozadja. Če želite razveljaviti barvo "
"ozadja, z desnim klikom uporabite kontekstni meni."

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:1945
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The available text style keys are the following; the keys used in the <link "
"linkend=\"color-themes-json\">&JSON; file</link> are listed in "
"<emphasis>bold</emphasis>, the names used in the <link linkend=\"color-"
"themes-gui\">&GUI;</link> are shown in parentheses if they are different."
msgstr ""
"Razpoložljivi ključi slogov besedila so naslednji; ključi, uporabljeni v "
"<link linkend=\"color-themes-json\">&JSON; datoteke</link> so navedene v "
"<emphasis>krepkem tisku</emphasis>, imena, uporabljena v <link linkend="
"\"color-themes-gui\">&GUI;</link>, so prikazana v oklepajih, če se "
"razlikujejo."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: development.docbook:1952
#, no-c-format
msgid "Normal Text &amp; Source Code"
msgstr "Običajno besedilo &amp; Izvorna koda"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:1954
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<userinput>Normal</userinput>: Default text style for normal text and source "
"code without special highlighting."
msgstr ""
"<userinput>Normalno</userinput>: Privzeti slog besedila za običajno besedilo "
"in izvorno kodo brez posebnega označevanja."

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:1957
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<userinput>Keyword</userinput>: Text style for built-in language keywords."
msgstr ""
"<userinput>Ključna beseda</userinput>: slog besedila za vgrajene jezikovne "
"ključne besede."

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:1960
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<userinput>Function</userinput>: Text style for function definitions and "
"function calls."
msgstr ""
"<userinput>Funkcija</userinput>: slog besedila za definicije funkcij in "
"klice funkcij."

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:1963
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<userinput>Variable</userinput>: Text style for variables, if applicable. "
"For instance, variables in PHP/Perl typically start with a <userinput>$</"
"userinput>, so all identifiers following the pattern <userinput>$foo</"
"userinput> are highlighted as variable."
msgstr ""
"<userinput>Spremenljivka</userinput>: slog besedila za spremenljivke, če je "
"na voljo. Na primer, spremenljivke v PHP/Perl se običajno začnejo z "
"<userinput>$</userinput>, zato so vsi identifikatorji, ki sledijo vzorcu "
"<userinput>$foo</userinput>, označeni kot spremenljivka."

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:1968
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<userinput>ControlFlow</userinput> (<guilabel>Control Flow</guilabel>): Text "
"style for control flow keywords, such as <emphasis>if</emphasis>, "
"<emphasis>then</emphasis>, <emphasis>else</emphasis>, <emphasis>return</"
"emphasis>, <emphasis>switch</emphasis>, <emphasis>break</emphasis>, "
"<emphasis>yield</emphasis>, <emphasis>continue</emphasis>, etc."
msgstr ""
"<userinput>NadzorPretoka</userinput> (<guilabel>Nadzor pretoka</guilabel>): "
"slog besedila za ključne besede nadzornega toka, kot so <emphasis>če</"
"emphasis>, <emphasis>potem</emphasis>, <emphasis> drugače</emphasis>, "
"<emphasis>vrnitev</emphasis>, <emphasis>preklop</emphasis>, "
"<emphasis>prekinitev</emphasis>, <emphasis>dobi</emphasis>, "
"<emphasis>nadaljuj</emphasis> itd."

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:1973
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<userinput>Operator</userinput>: Text style for operators, such as "
"<userinput>+</userinput>, <userinput>-</userinput>, <userinput>*</"
"userinput>, <userinput>/</userinput>, <userinput>%</userinput>, etc."
msgstr ""
"<userinput>Operator</userinput>: slog besedila za operatorje, kot so "
"<userinput>+</userinput>, <userinput>-</userinput>, <userinput>*</"
"userinput>, <userinput>/</userinput >, <userinput>%</userinput> itd."

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:1977
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<userinput>BuiltIn</userinput> (<guilabel>Built-in</guilabel>): Text style "
"for built-in language classes, functions and objects."
msgstr ""
"<userinput>Vgrajeno</userinput> (<guilabel>Vgrajeno</guilabel>): Slog "
"besedila za vgrajene jezikovne razrede, funkcije in predmete."

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:1980
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<userinput>Extension</userinput>: Text style for well-known extensions, such "
"as &Qt; classes, functions/macros in C++ and Python or boost."
msgstr ""
"<userinput>Razširitev</userinput>: slog besedila za dobro znane razširitve, "
"kot je npr."

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:1984
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<userinput>Preprocessor</userinput>: Text style for preprocessor statements "
"or macro definitions."
msgstr ""
"<userinput>Predprocesor</userinput>: slog besedila za stavke predprocesorja "
"ali definicije makrov."

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:1987
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<userinput>Attribute</userinput>: Text style for annotations or attributes "
"of functions or objects, e.g. <userinput>@override</userinput> in Java, or "
"<userinput>__declspec(...)</userinput> and <userinput>__attribute__((...))</"
"userinput> in C++."
msgstr ""
"<userinput>Atribut</userinput>: slog besedila za opombe ali atribute funkcij "
"ali predmetov, npr. <userinput>@override</userinput> v Javi ali "
"<userinput>__declspec(...)</userinput> in <userinput>__attribute__((...))</"
"userinput> v C++."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: development.docbook:1995
#, no-c-format
msgid "Numbers, Types &amp; Constants"
msgstr "Številke, vrste &amp; Konstante"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:1997
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<userinput>DataType</userinput> (<guilabel>Data Type</guilabel>): Text style "
"for built-in data types such as <emphasis>int</emphasis>, <emphasis>char</"
"emphasis>, <emphasis>float</emphasis>, <emphasis>void</emphasis>, "
"<emphasis>u64</emphasis>, etc."
msgstr ""
"<userinput>PodatkovniTip</userinput> (<guilabel>Podatkovni tip</guilabel>): "
"slog besedila za vgrajene podatkovne tipe, kot so <emphasis>int</emphasis>, "
"<emphasis>char</emphasis>, <emphasis >float</emphasis>, <emphasis>void</"
"emphasis>, <emphasis>u64</emphasis> itd."

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:2001
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<userinput>DecVal</userinput> (<guilabel>Decimal/Value</guilabel>): Text "
"style for decimal values."
msgstr ""
"<userinput>DecVal</userinput> (<guilabel>Decimalna/Vrednost</guilabel>): "
"slog besedila za decimalne vrednosti."

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:2004
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<userinput>BaseN</userinput> (<guilabel>Base-N Integer</guilabel>): Text "
"style for numbers with base other than 10."
msgstr ""
"<userinput>OsnovaN</userinput> (<guilabel>Celo število z osnovo N</"
"guilabel>): slog besedila za števila z osnovo, ki ni 10."

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:2007
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<userinput>Float</userinput> (<guilabel>Floating Point</guilabel>): Text "
"style for floating point numbers."
msgstr ""
"<userinput>Plavajoča</userinput> (<guilabel>Plavajoča vejica</guilabel>): "
"slog besedila za števila s plavajočo vejico."

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:2010
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<userinput>Constant</userinput>: Text style for language constants and user "
"defined constants, e.g. <emphasis>True</emphasis>, <emphasis>False</"
"emphasis>, <emphasis>None</emphasis> in Python or <emphasis>nullptr</"
"emphasis> in C/C++; or math constants like <emphasis>PI</emphasis>."
msgstr ""
"<userinput>Konstanta</userinput>: slog besedila za jezikovne konstante in "
"uporabniško določene konstante, npr. <emphasis>True</emphasis>, "
"<emphasis>False</emphasis>, <emphasis>Brez</emphasis> v Pythonu ali "
"<emphasis>nullptr</emphasis> v C/C++; ali matematične konstante, kot je "
"<emphasis>PI</emphasis>."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: development.docbook:2018
#, no-c-format
msgid "Strings &amp; Characters"
msgstr "Niz znakov &amp; Znaki"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:2020
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<userinput>Char</userinput> (<guilabel>Character</guilabel>): Text style for "
"single characters such as <userinput>'x'</userinput>."
msgstr ""
"<userinput>Znak</userinput> (<guilabel>Znak</guilabel>): slog besedila za "
"posamezne znake, kot je <userinput>'x'</userinput>."

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:2023
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<userinput>SpecialChar</userinput> (<guilabel>Special Character</guilabel>): "
"Text style for escaped characters in strings, e.g. <quote><userinput>hello"
"\\n</userinput></quote>, and other characters with special meaning in "
"strings, such as substitutions or regex operators."
msgstr ""
"<userinput>PosebniZnak</userinput> (<guilabel>Posebni znak</guilabel>): slog "
"besedila za ubežne znake v nizih, npr. <quote><userinput>zdravo\\n</"
"userinput></quote> in drugi znaki s posebnim pomenom v nizih, kot so "
"zamenjave ali operatorji regularnih izrazov."

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:2027
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<userinput>String</userinput>: Text style for strings like "
"<quote><userinput>hello world</userinput></quote>."
msgstr ""
"<userinput>Niz</userinput>: slog besedila za nize, kot je "
"<quote><userinput>zdravo, svet</userinput></quote>."

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:2030
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<userinput>VerbatimString</userinput> (<guilabel>Verbatim String</"
"guilabel>): Text style for verbatim or raw strings like <userinput>'raw "
"\\backlash'</userinput> in Perl, CoffeeScript, and shells, as well as "
"<userinput>r'\\raw'</userinput> in Python, or such as HERE docs."
msgstr ""
"<userinput>VerbatimString</userinput> (<guilabel>Verbatim String</"
"guilabel>): Slog besedila za dobesedne ali neobdelane nize, kot je "
"<userinput>'raw \\backlash'</userinput> v Perlu, CoffeeScriptu in tudi "
"lupinah kot <userinput>r'\\raw'</userinput> v Pythonu ali kot TUKAJ "
"dokumenti."

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:2035
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<userinput>SpecialString</userinput> (<guilabel>Special String</guilabel>): "
"Text style for special strings, such as regular expressions in ECMAScript, "
"the &latex; math mode, SQL, etc."
msgstr ""
"<userinput>SpecialString</userinput> (<guilabel>Special string</guilabel>): "
"slog besedila za posebne nize, kot so regularni izrazi v ECMAScript, &latex; "
"matematični način, SQL itd."

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:2039
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<userinput>Import</userinput> (<guilabel>Imports, Modules, Includes</"
"guilabel>): Text style for includes, imports, modules or &latex; packages."
msgstr ""
"<userinput>Uvoz</userinput> (<guilabel>Uvozi, moduli, vključuje</guilabel>): "
"slog besedila za vključitve, uvoze, module ali &latex; paketi."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: development.docbook:2045
#, no-c-format
msgid "Comments &amp; Documentation"
msgstr "Komentarji &amp; Dokumentacija"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:2047
#, no-c-format
msgid "<userinput>Comment</userinput>: Text style for normal comments."
msgstr "<userinput>Komentar</userinput>: slog besedila za običajne komentarje."

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:2050
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<userinput>Documentation</userinput>: Text style for comments that reflect "
"API documentation, such as <userinput>/** doxygen comments */</userinput> or "
"<userinput>\"\"\"docstrings\"\"\"</userinput>."
msgstr ""
"<userinput>Dokumentacija</userinput>: slog besedila za komentarje, ki "
"odražajo dokumentacijo API-ja, kot so <userinput>/** komentarji doxygen */</"
"userinput> ali <userinput>\"\"\"docstrings\"\"\"</userinput>."

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:2054
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<userinput>Annotation</userinput>: Text style for annotations in comments or "
"documentation commands, such as <userinput>@param</userinput> in Doxygen or "
"JavaDoc."
msgstr ""
"<userinput>Pripomba</userinput>: Slog besedila za opombe v komentarjih ali "
"dokumentacijskih ukazih, kot je <userinput>@param</userinput> v Doxygen ali "
"JavaDoc."

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:2058
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<userinput>CommentVar</userinput> (<guilabel>Comment Variable</guilabel>): "
"Text style that refers to variables names used in above commands in a "
"comment, such as <userinput>foobar</userinput> in <quote><userinput>@param "
"foobar</userinput></quote>, in Doxygen or JavaDoc."
msgstr ""
"<userinput>CommentVar</userinput> (<guilabel>Spremenljivka komentarja</"
"guilabel>): slog besedila, ki se nanaša na imena spremenljivk, uporabljena v "
"zgornjih ukazih v komentarju, kot je <userinput>foobar</userinput> v "
"<quote><userinput>@param foobar</userinput></quote>, v Doxygen ali JavaDoc."

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:2063
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<userinput>RegionMarker</userinput> (<guilabel>Region Marker</guilabel>): "
"Text style for region markers, typically defined by <userinput>//BEGIN</"
"userinput> and <userinput>//END</userinput> in comments."
msgstr ""
"<userinput>OznakaRegije</userinput> (<guilabel>Oznaka regije</guilabel>): "
"Slog besedila za regijske označevalce, ki ga običajno definirata "
"<userinput>//BEGIN</userinput> in <userinput>//END</userinput> v komentarjih."

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:2067
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<userinput>Information</userinput>: Text style for information, notes and "
"tips, such as the keyword <userinput>@note</userinput> in Doxygen."
msgstr ""
"<userinput>Informacije</userinput>: slog besedila za informacije, opombe in "
"nasvete, kot je ključna beseda <userinput>@note</userinput> v Doxygenu."

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:2071
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<userinput>Warning</userinput>: Text style for warnings, such as the keyword "
"<userinput>@warning</userinput> in Doxygen."
msgstr ""
"<userinput>Opozorilo</userinput>: Slog besedila za opozorila, kot je ključna "
"beseda <userinput>@warning</userinput> v Doxygenu."

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:2074
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<userinput>Alert</userinput>: Text style for special words in comments, such "
"as <userinput>TODO</userinput>, <userinput>FIXME</userinput>, "
"<userinput>XXXX</userinput> and <userinput>WARNING</userinput>."
msgstr ""
"<userinput>Opozorilo</userinput>: slog besedila za posebne besede v "
"komentarjih, kot so <userinput>TODO</userinput>, <userinput>FIXME</"
"userinput>, <userinput>XXXX</userinput> in <userinput>OPOZORILO </userinput>."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: development.docbook:2081
#, no-c-format
msgid "Miscellaneous"
msgstr "Razno"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:2083
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<userinput>Error</userinput>: Text style indicating error highlighting and "
"wrong syntax."
msgstr ""
"<userinput>Napaka</userinput>: Slog besedila označuje označevanje napak in "
"napačno sintakso."

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:2086
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<userinput>Others</userinput>: Text style for attributes that do not match "
"any of the other default styles."
msgstr ""
"<userinput>Drugo</userinput>: Slog besedila za atribute, ki se ne ujemajo z "
"nobenim drugim privzetim slogom."

#. Tag: title
#: development.docbook:2096
#, no-c-format
msgid "Custom Highlighting Text Styles"
msgstr "Slogi besedila za označevanje po meri"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:2098
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Here you can establish text styles for a specific syntax highlighting "
"definition, overriding the <userinput>default text style</userinput> "
"described in <link linkend=\"color-themes-text-styles\">the previous "
"section</link>."
msgstr ""
"Tukaj lahko določite sloge besedila za določeno definicijo označevanja "
"sintakse, pri čemer preglasite <userinput>privzeti slog besedila</"
"userinput>, opisan v <link linkend=\"color-themes-text-styles\">prejšnjem "
"razdelku</link>."

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:2103
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In the <link linkend=\"color-themes-json\">&JSON; theme file</link>, this "
"corresponds to the <userinput>custom-styles</userinput> key, whose value is "
"an <emphasis>object</emphasis> where each subschema key corresponds to the "
"<userinput>name of a syntax highlighting definition</userinput>. Its value "
"is an <emphasis>object</emphasis> where each key refers to the "
"<userinput>style attributes name</userinput> defined in <link linkend=\"kate-"
"highlight-sections\">the <userinput>itemData</userinput> elements</link> of "
"the syntax highlighting &XML; file, and the respective value is a sub-object "
"with the keys <emphasis>text-color</emphasis>, <emphasis>selected-text-"
"color</emphasis>, <emphasis>bold</emphasis>, <emphasis>italic</emphasis>, "
"<emphasis>underline</emphasis>, <emphasis>strike-through</emphasis>, "
"<emphasis>background-color</emphasis> and <emphasis>selected-background-"
"color</emphasis>, defined in <link linkend=\"color-themes-text-styles\">the "
"previous section</link>. Each of these values are optional, since if they "
"are not present, the style set in <userinput>text-styles</userinput> is "
"considered."
msgstr ""
"V <link linkend=\"color-themes-json\">&JSON; datoteka teme</link>, to "
"ustreza ključu <userinput>custom-styles</userinput>, katerega vrednost je "
"<emphasis>objekt</emphasis>, kjer vsak ključ podsheme ustreza "
"<userinput>imenu označevanja sintakse definicija</userinput>. Njegova "
"vrednost je <emphasis>objekt</emphasis>, kjer se vsak ključ nanaša na "
"<userinput>ime atributov sloga</userinput>, definirano v <link linkend="
"\"kate-highlight-sections\"><userinput>podatkiPredmeta</userinput > "
"elementi</link> označevanja sintakse &XML; datoteka, ustrezna vrednost pa je "
"podobjekt s tipkami <emphasis>barva-besedila</emphasis>, <emphasis>barva-"
"izbranega-besedila</emphasis>, <emphasis>krepko</emphasis>, <emphasis> "
"ležeče</emphasis>, <emphasis>podčrtano</emphasis>, <emphasis>prečrtano</"
"emphasis>, <emphasis>barva-ozadja</emphasis> in <emphasis>izbrana-barva-"
"ozadja</emphasis>, določeno v <link linkend=\"color-themes-text-styles"
"\">prejšnjem razdelku</link>. Vsaka od teh vrednosti je neobvezna, saj se, "
"če nista prisotni, upošteva slog, nastavljen v <userinput>besedilni-stili</"
"userinput>."

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:2116
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"For example, in this piece of code, the <quote>ISO C++</quote> syntax "
"highlighting definition has a special text style for the <quote>Type "
"Modifiers</quote> and <quote>Standard Classes</quote> attributes. In the "
"corresponding &XML; file <quote>isocpp.xml</quote>, the defined attribute "
"<quote>Standard Classes</quote> uses the default style <userinput>BuiltIn</"
"userinput> (or dsBuiltIn). In this attribute, only the value of "
"<userinput>text-color</userinput> is overwritten by the new color "
"<quote>#6431b3</quote>."
msgstr ""
"Na primer, v tem delu kode ima definicija označevanja sintakse <quote>ISO C+"
"+</quote> poseben slog besedila za atribute <quote>Modifikatorji vrst</"
"quote> in <quote>Standardni razredi</quote>. V ustreznem &XML; datoteke "
"<quote>isocpp.xml</quote>, definirani atribut <quote>Standardni razredi</"
"quote> uporablja privzeti slog <userinput>BuiltIn</userinput> (ali "
"dsBuiltIn). V tem atributu je samo vrednost <userinput>besedilna-barva</"
"userinput> prepisana z novo barvo <quote>#6431b3</quote>."

#. Tag: programlisting
#: development.docbook:2124
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"\"custom-styles\": {\n"
"    \"ISO C++\": {\n"
"        \"Standard Classes\": {\n"
"            \"text-color\": \"#6431b3\"\n"
"        },\n"
"        \"Type Modifiers\": {\n"
"            \"bold\": true,\n"
"            \"selected-text-color\": \"#009183\",\n"
"            \"text-color\": \"#00b5cf\"\n"
"        }\n"
"    }\n"
"}"
msgstr ""
"\"slogi po meri\": {\n"
"     \"ISO C++\": {\n"
"         \"Standardni razredi\": {\n"
"             \"barva besedila\": \"#6431b3\"\n"
"         },\n"
"         \"Modifikatorji vrste\": {\n"
"             \"krepko\": res,\n"
"             \"barva-izbranega-besedila\": \"#009183\",\n"
"             \"barva-besedila\": \"#00b5cf\"\n"
"         }\n"
"     }\n"
"}"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:2130
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You should consider that these text styles are associated with the attribute "
"names defined in the syntax highlighting &XML; files. If an XML file is "
"updated and some attributes are renamed or removed, the custom style defined "
"in the theme will no longer apply."
msgstr ""
"Upoštevajte, da so ti slogi besedila povezani z imeni atributov, "
"definiranimi v označevanju sintakse &XML; datoteke. Če je datoteka XML "
"posodobljena in so nekateri atributi preimenovani ali odstranjeni, slog po "
"meri, definiran v temi, ne bo več veljal."

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:2136
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Syntax highlighting definitions often include other definitions. For "
"example, the <quote>QML</quote> highlighter includes the <quote>JavaScript</"
"quote> highlighter, since they share functionality in highlighting."
msgstr ""
"Definicije označevanja sintakse pogosto vključujejo druge definicije. Na "
"primer, označevalnik <quote>QML</quote> vključuje označevalnik "
"<quote>JavaScript</quote>, saj imata skupno funkcijo označevanja."

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:2144
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In <link linkend=\"color-themes-gui\">the &GUI; to manage themes of "
"KTextEditor</link>, these attributes can be modified in the "
"<userinput><guilabel>Highlighting Text Styles</guilabel></userinput> tab. By "
"default, the editor preselects the highlighting of the current document. You "
"will notice that many highlights contain other highlights represented by "
"groups in the style list. For example most highlights import the "
"<quote>Alert</quote> highlight, and many source code formats import the "
"<quote>Doxygen</quote> highlight."
msgstr ""
"V <link linkend=\"color-themes-gui\">&GUI; za upravljanje tem KTextEditor</"
"link> lahko te atribute spremenite na zavihku "
"<userinput><guilabel>Označevanje besedilnih slogov</guilabel></userinput>. "
"Privzeto urejevalnik vnaprej izbere označevanje trenutnega dokumenta. "
"Opazili boste, da številni poudarki vsebujejo druge poudarke, ki jih "
"predstavljajo skupine na seznamu slogov. Večina poudarkov na primer uvozi "
"poudarek <quote>Opozorilo</quote>, številni formati izvorne kode pa poudarek "
"<quote>Doxygen</quote>."

#. Tag: title
#: development.docbook:2159
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Color Themes &GUI;"
msgstr "Barvne teme &GUI;"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:2161
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The simplest way to create and edit color themes is through the &GUI; within "
"the <link linkend=\"config-dialog\"><quote>Configure</quote> dialog</link> "
"provided by <ulink url=\"https://api.kde.org/frameworks/ktexteditor/html/"
"\">KTextEditor</ulink>. To access it, select <menuchoice><guimenu>Settings</"
"guimenu> <guimenuitem>Configure <replaceable>Application</replaceable>...</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> from the menubar in your text editor. This brings "
"up the <guilabel>Configure</guilabel> dialog box, there select "
"<guilabel>Color Themes</guilabel> in the side panel."
msgstr ""
"Najenostavnejši način ustvarjanja in urejanja barvnih tem je prek &GUI; v "
"pogovornem oknu <link linkend=\"config-dialog\"><quote>Konfiguriraj</quote></"
"link>, ki ga ponuja <ulink url=\"https://api.kde.org/frameworks/ktexteditor/"
"html/\"> KTextEditor</ulink>. Za dostop do njega izberite "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Nastavitve</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Konfiguriraj "
"<replaceable>Aplikacijo</replaceable>...</guimenuitem></menuchoice> v "
"menijski vrstici urejevalnika besedil. To prikliče pogovorno okno "
"<guilabel>Konfiguriraj</guilabel>, tam izberite <guilabel>Barvne teme</"
"guilabel> na stranskem podoknu."

#. Tag: phrase
#: development.docbook:2172
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<phrase>&kate;'s settings dialog box with the color theme management.</"
"phrase>"
msgstr ""
"<phrase>Pogovorno okno z nastavitvami &kate; z upravljanjem barvnih tem.</"
"phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:2173
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<para>&kate;'s settings dialog box with the color theme management.</para>"
msgstr ""
"<para>Pogovorno okno z nastavitvami &kate; z upravljanjem barvnih tem.</para>"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:2177
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In this <link linkend=\"config-dialog\">dialog</link> you can configure all "
"the colors in any theme you have, as well as create/copy new themes, delete "
"them, export them to a <userinput>.theme</userinput> file with <link linkend="
"\"color-themes-json\">&JSON; format</link> or import them from external "
"<userinput>.theme</userinput> files. Each theme has settings for text colors "
"and styles."
msgstr ""
"V tem <link linkend=\"config-dialog\">pogovornem oknu</link> lahko "
"konfigurirate vse barve v kateri koli temi, ki jo imate, kot tudi ustvarjate/"
"kopirate nove teme, jih brišete, izvozite v <userinput>.teme </userinput> "
"datoteka s <link linkend=\"color-themes-json\">&JSON; format</link> ali jih "
"uvozite iz zunanjih datotek <userinput>.teme</userinput>. Vsaka tema ima "
"nastavitve za barve in sloge besedila."

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:2184
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The built-in themes cannot be modified by default. To do this, you need to "
"copy them and give them a new name."
msgstr ""
"Vgrajenih tem privzeto ni mogoče spreminjati. Če želite to narediti, jih "
"morate kopirati in jim dati novo ime."

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:2187
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To use a theme permanently in your text editor, you must select it in the "
"combobox labeled <guilabel>Default theme for <replaceable>Application</"
"replaceable></guilabel> at the bottom of the dialog and press "
"<guibutton>Apply</guibutton> or <guibutton>OK</guibutton>. By default, the "
"<userinput><guilabel>Automatic Selection</guilabel></userinput> option is "
"active, which chooses a more appropriate color theme according to the "
"<emphasis>&kde; &plasma; color scheme</emphasis> used in the text editing "
"application; it usually chooses between <quote>Breeze Light</quote> and "
"<quote>Breeze Dark</quote> if the scheme is light or dark, respectively."
msgstr ""
"Če želite trajno uporabiti temo v urejevalniku besedil, jo morate izbrati v "
"kombiniranem polju z oznako <guilabel>Privzeta tema za "
"<replaceable>Aplikacijo</replaceable></guilabel> na dnu pogovornega okna in "
"pritisniti <guibutton>Uporabi</guibutton> ali <guibutton>V redu</guibutton>. "
"Privzeto je aktivna možnost <userinput><guilabel>Samodejna izbira</"
"guilabel></userinput>, ki izbere ustreznejšo barvno temo glede na "
"<emphasis>&kde; &plasma; barvna shema</emphasis> uporabljena v aplikaciji za "
"urejanje besedila; običajno izbira med <quote>Breeze Light</quote> in "
"<quote>Breeze Dark</quote>, če je shema svetla oziroma temna."

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:2198
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can adjust the &kde; global color scheme in the <ulink url=\"help:/"
"kcontrol/colors/\"><quote>Colors</quote> module in &systemsettings;</ulink>. "
"You can also change it in some applications individually such as &kate; or "
"&kdevelop;, from the menu <menuchoice><guimenu>Settings</"
"guimenu><guisubmenu>Color Scheme</guisubmenu></menuchoice>."
msgstr ""
"Prilagodite lahko &kde; globalna barvna shema v modulu <ulink url=\"help:/"
"kcontrol/colors/\"><quote>Barve</quote> v &systemsettings;</ulink>. "
"Spremenite ga lahko tudi v nekaterih aplikacijah posamično, kot je &kate; "
"ali &kdevelop;, v meniju <menuchoice><guimenu>Nastavitve</"
"guimenu><guisubmenu>Barvna shema</guisubmenu></menuchoice>."

#. Tag: title
#: development.docbook:2208
#, no-c-format
msgid "Create a new theme"
msgstr "Ustvarite novo temo"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:2210
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To create a new theme, it is first necessary to copy an existing one. Select "
"an existing theme which you want to use as a base, such as <quote>Breeze "
"Light</quote> or <quote>Breeze Dark</quote>, and click <guibutton>Copy</"
"guibutton>. Then write a name for the new theme."
msgstr ""
"Če želite ustvariti novo temo, morate najprej kopirati obstoječo. Izberite "
"obstoječo temo, ki jo želite uporabiti kot osnovo, na primer <quote>Breeze "
"Light</quote> ali <quote>Breeze Dark</quote>, in kliknite "
"<guibutton>Kopiraj</guibutton>. Nato napišite ime za novo temo."

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:2215
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you want to modify a built-in or read-only theme, you must first copy it "
"under a different name."
msgstr ""
"Če želite spremeniti vgrajeno temo ali temo samo za branje, jo morate "
"najprej kopirati pod drugim imenom."

#. Tag: title
#: development.docbook:2221
#, no-c-format
msgid "Import or export &JSON; theme files"
msgstr "Uvozi ali izvozi &JSON; tematske datoteke"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:2223
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can export a selected theme (including built-in ones) to a <link linkend="
"\"color-themes-json\">&JSON; file</link> with <userinput>.theme</userinput> "
"extension, with the <guibutton>Export</guibutton> button. This will open a "
"dialog to save the file. To add a color theme from an external <link linkend="
"\"color-themes-json\">&JSON; file</link>, just press the <guibutton>Import</"
"guibutton> button and select the <userinput>.theme</userinput> file from the "
"dialog."
msgstr ""
"Izbrano temo (vključno z vgrajenimi) lahko izvozite v <link linkend=\"color-"
"themes-json\">&JSON; datoteka</link> s končnico <userinput>.teme</userinput> "
"z gumbom <guibutton>Izvozi</guibutton>. To bo odprlo pogovorno okno za "
"shranjevanje datoteke. Če želite dodati barvno temo iz zunanjega <link "
"linkend=\"color-themes-json\">&JSON; datoteko</link>, preprosto pritisnite "
"gumb <guibutton>Uvozi</guibutton> in v pogovornem oknu izberite datoteko "
"<userinput>.teme</userinput>."

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:2236
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"As <link linkend=\"color-themes-json-overview\">mentioned above</link>, user-"
"customized theme files are stored in the <filename class=\"directory\">org."
"kde.syntax-highlighting/themes/</filename> directory. When you copy or "
"create a theme, it will automatically appear there. Also, importing or "
"adding a theme is equivalent to copying an external <userinput>.theme</"
"userinput> file into this directory. KSyntaxHighlighting automatically picks "
"up color theme files from this directory."
msgstr ""
"Kot <link linkend=\"color-themes-json-overview\">omenjeno zgoraj</link>, so "
"uporabniško prilagojene datoteke tem shranjene v <filename class=\"directory"
"\">org.kde.syntax-highlighting/themes/</filename> imenik. Ko kopirate ali "
"ustvarite temo, se samodejno prikaže tam. Poleg tega je uvoz ali dodajanje "
"teme enakovredno kopiranju zunanje datoteke <userinput>.teme</userinput> v "
"ta imenik. KSyntaxHighlighting samodejno pobere datoteke barvnih tem iz tega "
"imenika."

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:2244
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you want to publish a theme created by you, it is essential to check the "
"<link linkend=\"color-themes-json-metadata\">metadata</link> object of the "
"<link linkend=\"color-themes-json\">&JSON; file</link>, adding the "
"respective license and checking the revision number."
msgstr ""
"Če želite objaviti temo, ki ste jo ustvarili sami, je nujno, da preverite "
"objekt <link linkend=\"color-themes-json-metadata\">metapodatki</link> v "
"<link linkend=\"color-themes-json\" >&JSON; datoteka</link>, dodajanje "
"ustrezne licence in preverjanje številke revizije."

#. Tag: title
#: development.docbook:2257
#, no-c-format
msgid "Editing color themes"
msgstr "Urejanje barvnih tem"

#. Tag: title
#: development.docbook:2261
#, no-c-format
msgid "Colors"
msgstr "Barve"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:2263
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Here the colors of the text editing area are adjusted. These are detailed in "
"<xref linkend=\"color-themes-editor-colors\"/>."
msgstr ""
"Tukaj se prilagodijo barve območja za urejanje besedila. Ti so podrobno "
"opisani v <xref linkend=\"color-themes-editor-colors\"/>."

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:2276 development.docbook:2296
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The name in the list of styles is using the style configured for the item, "
"providing you with an immediate preview when configuring a style."
msgstr ""
"Ime na seznamu slogov uporablja slog, konfiguriran za element, kar vam "
"omogoča takojšen predogled, ko konfigurirate slog."

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:2279
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Each style lets you select common attributes as well as foreground and "
"background colors. To unset a background color, right-click to use the "
"context menu."
msgstr ""
"Vsak slog vam omogoča izbiro skupnih atributov ter barv ospredja in ozadja. "
"Če želite razveljaviti barvo ozadja, z desnim klikom uporabite kontekstni "
"meni."

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:2282
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The attributes of this area are detailed in <xref linkend=\"color-themes-"
"text-styles\"/>."
msgstr ""
"Atributi tega območja so podrobno opisani v <xref linkend=\"color-themes-"
"text-styles\"/>."

#. Tag: title
#: development.docbook:2289
#, no-c-format
msgid "Highlighting Text Styles"
msgstr "Označevanje besedilnih slogov"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:2291
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Here you can edit the text styles used by a specific highlight definition. "
"The editor preselects the highlight used by your current document. To work "
"on a different highlight, select one in the <guilabel>Highlight</guilabel> "
"combobox above the style list."
msgstr ""
"Tukaj lahko urejate besedilne sloge, ki jih uporablja določena definicija "
"osvetlitve. Urejevalnik vnaprej izbere osvetlitev, ki jo uporablja vaš "
"trenutni dokument. Če želite delati na drugem poudarku, ga izberite v "
"kombiniranem polju <guilabel>Označi</guilabel> nad seznamom slogov."

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:2299
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Each style lets you select common attributes as well as foreground and "
"background colors. To unset a background color, right-click to use the "
"context menu. In addition you can see if a style is equal to the default "
"style used for the item, and set it to that if not."
msgstr ""
"Vsak slog vam omogoča izbiro skupnih atributov ter barv ospredja in ozadja. "
"Če želite razveljaviti barvo ozadja, z desnim klikom uporabite kontekstni "
"meni. Poleg tega lahko vidite, ali je slog enak privzetemu slogu, "
"uporabljenemu za element, in ga nastavite na to, če ni."

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:2303
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You will notice that many highlights contain other highlights represented by "
"groups in the style list. For example most highlights import the Alert "
"highlight, and many source code formats imports the Doxygen highlight. "
"Editing colors in those groups only affects the styles when used in the "
"edited highlight format."
msgstr ""
"Opazili boste, da številni poudarki vsebujejo druge poudarke, ki jih "
"predstavljajo skupine na seznamu slogov. Večina poudarkov na primer uvozi "
"poudarek opozorila, številni formati izvorne kode pa uvozijo poudarek "
"Doxygen. Urejanje barv v teh skupinah vpliva samo na sloge, če se "
"uporabljajo v urejenem formatu osvetlitve."

#. Tag: title
#: development.docbook:2322
#, no-c-format
msgid "Contrast of Text Colors"
msgstr "Kontrast barv besedila"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:2324
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"An important aspect when working with color themes is to choose a text "
"contrast that makes it easier to read, especially in combination with the "
"background."
msgstr ""
"Pomemben vidik pri delu z barvnimi temami je izbira kontrasta besedila, ki "
"olajša branje, zlasti v kombinaciji z ozadjem."

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:2327
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <userinput>Kontrast</userinput> application is a color contrast checker. "
"It tells you that the text color and background color combinations are "
"readable and accessible, so this is an excellent tool to help you create "
"color themes."
msgstr ""
"Aplikacija <userinput>Kontrast</userinput> je preverjalnik barvnega "
"kontrasta. Pove vam, da so kombinacije barv besedila in barv ozadja berljive "
"in dostopne, zato je to odlično orodje za pomoč pri ustvarjanju barvnih tem."

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:2331
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can download <userinput>Kontrast</userinput> from <ulink url=\"https://"
"apps.kde.org/en/kontrast\">the &kde; Applications website</ulink> or from "
"<ulink url=\"https://flathub.org/apps/details/org.kde.kontrast\">the Flatpak "
"package on Flathub</ulink> (only in GNU/Linux)."
msgstr ""
"<userinput>Kontrast</userinput> lahko prenesete iz <ulink url=\"https://apps."
"kde.org/en/kontrast\">&kde; Spletno mesto z aplikacijami</ulink> ali iz "
"<ulink url=\"https://flathub.org/apps/details/org.kde.kontrast\">paketa "
"Flatpak na Flathubu</ulink> (samo v GNU/Linux)."

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:2336
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The GNOME <userinput>Contrast</userinput> application is similar. You can "
"download <ulink url=\"https://flathub.org/apps/details/org.gnome.design."
"Contrast\">the Flatpak package on Flathub</ulink> (only in GNU/Linux)."
msgstr ""
"Aplikacija GNOME <userinput>Kontrast</userinput> je podobna. <ulink url="
"\"https://flathub.org/apps/details/org.gnome.design.Contrast\">paket Flatpak "
"lahko prenesete na Flathub</ulink> (samo v GNU/Linux)."

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:2340
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A python script in <ulink url=\"https://invent.kde.org/frameworks/syntax-"
"highlighting/-/blob/master/utils/theme_contrast_checker.py?ref_type=heads"
"\">Syntax Highlighting repository</ulink> lets you visualize all the colors "
"in a theme, as well as the contrast with the various backgrounds configured."
msgstr ""
"Python skript v <ulink url=\"https://invent.kde.org/frameworks/syntax-"
"highlighting/-/blob/master/utils/theme_contrast_checker.py?ref_type=heads"
"\">skladišču označevanja skladnje</ulink> vam omogoča vizualizacijo vseh "
"barv v temi in v kontrastu s konfiguriranimi ozadji."

#. Tag: title
#: development.docbook:2348
#, no-c-format
msgid "Suggestions of Consistency with Syntax Highlighting"
msgstr "Predlogi za skladnost z označevanjem sintakse"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:2350
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"KSyntaxHighlighting includes <ulink url=\"https://kate-editor.org/syntax/"
"\">more than 300 syntax highlighting definitions</ulink>, therefore it is "
"ideal that you make sure your new theme looks good in all syntax "
"highlighting definitions. The built-in color themes have the following "
"similarities that it is recommended (but not required) to follow to achieve "
"a correct display of all syntax highlighting definitions:"
msgstr ""
"KSyntaxHighlighting vključuje <ulink url=\"https://kate-editor.org/syntax/"
"\">več kot 300 definicij označevanja sintakse</ulink>, zato je idealno, da "
"poskrbite, da bo vaša nova tema videti dobro v vseh definicijah označevanja "
"sintakse . Vgrajene barvne teme imajo naslednje podobnosti, ki jih je "
"priporočljivo (vendar ni obvezno) upoštevati, da dosežete pravilen prikaz "
"vseh definicij označevanja sintakse:"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:2358
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Use bold for the <quote>Keyword</quote> and <quote>ControlFlow</quote> <link "
"linkend=\"color-themes-text-styles\">text styles</link>."
msgstr ""
"Uporabite krepko za <quote>Ključna Beseda</quote> in <quote>Kontrola "
"Pretoka</quote> <link linkend=\"color-themes-text-styles\">besedilne sloge</"
"link>."

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:2361
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Do not use background color in any <link linkend=\"color-themes-text-styles"
"\">text style</link>, except <quote>Alert</quote> and <quote>RegionMarker</"
"quote>."
msgstr ""
"Ne uporabljajte barve ozadja v nobenem <link linkend=\"color-themes-text-"
"styles\">slogu besedila</link>, razen <quote>Opozorilo</quote> in "
"<quote>Označevalnik regije</quote>."

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:2366
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Most of the syntax highlighters are intended to look good on the default "
"themes <quote>Breeze Light</quote> and <quote>Breeze Dark</quote>, "
"therefore, another way to maintain consistency is to use similar colors in "
"the <link linkend=\"color-themes-text-styles\">text styles</link>, like "
"<emphasis>green</emphasis> for <quote>Preprocessor</quote> and "
"<quote>Others</quote>, <emphasis>blue</emphasis> for <quote>DataType</quote> "
"and <quote>Attribute</quote>, or <emphasis>purple</emphasis> for "
"<quote>Function</quote>."
msgstr ""
"Večina označevalcev sintakse je namenjena temu, da izgleda dobro na "
"privzetih temah <quote>Breeze Light</quote> in <quote>Breeze Dark</quote>, "
"zato je drug način za ohranjanje doslednosti uporaba podobnih barv v <link "
"linkend=\"color-themes-text-styles\">besedilni slogi</link>, kot je "
"<emphasis>zelena</emphasis> za <quote>Predprocesor</quote> in <quote>Ostalo</"
"quote>, <emphasis> modra</emphasis> za <quote>TipPodatkov</quote> in "
"<quote>Atribut</quote> ali <emphasis>vijolična</emphasis> za "
"<quote>Funkcija</quote>."

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:2374
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Note that these recommendations are not mandatory when creating and "
"publishing a theme."
msgstr ""
"Upoštevajte, da ta priporočila niso obvezna pri ustvarjanju in objavi teme."

#. Tag: title
#: development.docbook:2385
#, no-c-format
msgid "Scripting with &javascript;"
msgstr "Skriptiranje z &javascript;"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:2387
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The &kappname; editor component is easily extensible by writing scripts. The "
"scripting language is ECMAScript (widely known as &javascript;). &kappname; "
"supports two kinds of scripts: indentation and command line scripts. A "
"functionality similar to command line scripts is also provided in the <ulink "
"url=\"help:/kate/kate-application-plugin-snippets.html\">snippets plugin</"
"ulink>."
msgstr ""
"Komponento urejevalnika &kappname; je mogoče enostavno razširiti s pisanjem "
"skriptov. Skriptni jezik je ECMAScript (splošno znan kot &javascript;). "
"&kappname; podpira dve vrsti skriptov: zamike in skripte ukazne vrstice. "
"Funkcionalnost, podobna skriptom ukazne vrstice, je na voljo tudi v vtičniku "
"<ulink url=\"help:/kate/kate-application-plugin-snippets.html\">koščkov "
"kode</ulink>."

#. Tag: title
#: development.docbook:2396
#, no-c-format
msgid "Indentation Scripts"
msgstr "Skripte za zamik"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:2398
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Indentation scripts - also referred as indenters - automatically indent the "
"source code while typing text. As an example, after hitting the return key "
"the indentation level often increases."
msgstr ""
"Skripti za zamike – imenovani tudi zamiki – samodejno zamikajo izvorno kodo "
"med tipkanjem besedila. Na primer, po pritisku tipke za vrnitev se raven "
"zamika pogosto poveča."

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:2404
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The following sections describe step by step how to create the skeleton for "
"a simple indenter. As a first step, create a new <filename>*.js</filename> "
"file called &eg; <filename>javascript.js</filename> in the local home folder "
"<filename>$<envar>XDG_DATA_HOME</envar>/katepart5/script/indentation</"
"filename>. Therein, the environment variable <envar>XDG_DATA_HOME</envar> "
"typically expands to either <filename>~/.local</filename> or <filename>~/."
"local/share</filename>."
msgstr ""
"Naslednji razdelki korak za korakom opisujejo, kako ustvariti okostje za "
"preprost zamik. Kot prvi korak ustvarite novo datoteko <filename>*.js</"
"filename> z imenom &eg; <filename>javascript.js</filename> v lokalni domači "
"mapi <filename>$<envar>XDG_DATA_HOME</envar>/katepart5/script/indentation</"
"filename>. Tam se spremenljivka okolja <envar>XDG_DATA_HOME</envar> običajno "
"razširi na <filename>~/.local</filename> ali <filename>~/.local/share</"
"filename>."

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:2412 development.docbook:2502
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"On &Windows; these files are located in <filename>%USERPROFILE%\\AppData"
"\\Local\\katepart5\\script\\indentation</filename>. <replaceable>%USERPROFILE"
"%</replaceable> usually expands to <filename>C:\\\\Users\\"
"\\<replaceable>user</replaceable></filename>."
msgstr ""
"V &Windows; te datoteke se nahajajo v <filename>%USERPROFILE%\\AppData\\Local"
"\\katepart5\\script\\indentation</filename>. <replaceable>%USERPROFILE%</"
"replaceable> se običajno razširi v <filename>C:\\\\Users\\"
"\\<replaceable>user</replaceable></filename>."

#. Tag: title
#: development.docbook:2416
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Indentation Script Header"
msgstr "Glava skripta za zamik"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:2417
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The header of the file <filename>javascript.js</filename> is embedded as "
"&JSON; at the beginning of the document as follows: <programlisting>\n"
"var katescript = {\n"
"    \"name\": \"JavaScript\",\n"
"    \"author\": \"Example Name &lt;example.name@some.address.org&gt;\",\n"
"    \"license\": \"BSD License\",\n"
"    \"revision\": 1,\n"
"    \"kate-version\": \"5.1\",\n"
"    \"required-syntax-style\": \"javascript\",\n"
"    \"indent-languages\": [\"javascript\"],\n"
"    \"priority\": 0,\n"
"}; // kate-script-header, must be at the start of the file without comments\n"
"</programlisting> Each entry is explained in detail now:"
msgstr ""
"Glava datoteke <filename>javascript.js</filename> je vdelana kot &JSON; na "
"začetku dokumenta kot sledi: <programlisting>\n"
"var katescript = {\n"
"     \"ime\": \"JavaScript\",\n"
"     \"author\": \"Primer imena &lt;example.name@some.address.org&gt;\",\n"
"     \"license\": \"Licenca BSD\",\n"
"     \"revizija\": 1,\n"
"     \"kate-različica\": \"5.1\",\n"
"     \"required-syntax-style\": \"javascript\",\n"
"     \"indent-languages\": [\"javascript\"],\n"
"     \"prednost\": 0,\n"
"}; // kate-script-header, mora biti na začetku datoteke brez komentarjev\n"
"</programlisting> Vsak vnos je zdaj podrobno razložen:"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:2424
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<literal>name</literal> [required]: This is the indenter name that appears "
"in the menu <menuchoice><guimenu>Tools</guimenu><guimenuitem>Indentation</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> and in the configuration dialog."
msgstr ""
"<literal>ime</literal> [obvezno]: To je ime zamika, ki se prikaže v meniju "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Orodja</guimenu><guimenuitem>Zamik</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice> in v konfiguracijskem pogovornem oknu ."

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:2429 development.docbook:2558
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<literal>author</literal> [optional]: The author's name and contact "
"information."
msgstr ""
"<literal>avtor</literal> [neobvezno]: ime in kontaktni podatki avtorja."

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:2432
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<literal>license</literal> [optional]: Short form of the license, such as "
"BSD License or LGPLv3."
msgstr ""
"<literal>licenca</literal> [izbirno]: kratka oblika licence, kot je licenca "
"BSD ali LGPLv3."

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:2435 development.docbook:2560
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<literal>revision</literal> [required]: The revision of the script. This "
"number should be increased whenever the script is modified."
msgstr ""
"<literal>revizija</literal> [zahtevano]: revizija skripta. To število je "
"treba povečati vsakič, ko je skript spremenjen."

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:2438 development.docbook:2561
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<literal>kate-version</literal> [required]: Minimum required &kappname; "
"version."
msgstr ""
"<literal>različica-kate</literal> [zahtevano]: Zahtevano najmanj &kappname; "
"različica."

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:2441
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<literal>required-syntax-style</literal> [optional]: The required syntax "
"style, which matches the specified <literal>style</literal> in syntax "
"highlighting files. This is important for indenters that rely on specific "
"highlight information in the document. If a required syntax style is "
"specified, the indenter is available only when the appropriate highlighter "
"is active. This prevents <quote>undefined behavior</quote> caused by using "
"the indenter without the expected highlighting schema. For instance, the "
"Ruby indenter makes use of this in the files <filename>ruby.js</filename> "
"and <filename>ruby.xml</filename>."
msgstr ""
"<literal>zahtevan-slog-sintakse</literal> [neobvezno]: Zahtevani slog "
"sintakse, ki se ujema z navedenim <literal>slog</literal> v datotekah za "
"označevanje sintakse. To je pomembno za zamike, ki se zanašajo na posebne "
"informacije o poudarkih v dokumentu. Če je naveden zahtevani slog sintakse, "
"je zamik na voljo le, če je aktiven ustrezen označevalnik. To prepreči "
"<quote>nedefinirano vedenje</quote>, ki ga povzroča uporaba zamika brez "
"pričakovane sheme označevanja. Na primer, Ruby indenter to uporablja v "
"datotekah <filename>ruby.js</filename> in <filename>ruby.xml</filename>."

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:2444
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<literal>indent-languages</literal> [optional]: &JSON; array of syntax "
"styles the indenter can indent correctly, &eg;: <literal>[\"c++\", \"java"
"\"]</literal>."
msgstr ""
"<literal>alinej-jezikov</literal> [izbirno]: &JSON; niz skladenjskih slogov, "
"ki jih lahko zamik pravilno zamakne, &eg;: <literal>[\"c++\", \"java\"]</"
"literal>."

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:2447
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<literal>priority</literal> [optional]: If several indenters are suited for "
"a certain highlighted file, the priority decides which indenter is chosen as "
"default indenter."
msgstr ""
"<literal>prioriteta</literal> [neobvezno]: Če je za določeno označeno "
"datoteko primernih več zamikov, prednost določi, kateri zamik je izbran kot "
"privzeti zamik."

#. Tag: title
#: development.docbook:2456
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Indenter Source Code"
msgstr "Izvorna koda Indenter"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:2457
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Having specified the header this section explains how the indentation "
"scripting itself works. The basic skeleton of the body looks like this: "
"<programlisting>\n"
"// required katepart js libraries, &eg; range.js if you use Range\n"
"require (\"range.js\");\n"
"\n"
"triggerCharacters = \"{}/:;\";\n"
"function indent(line, indentWidth, ch)\n"
"{\n"
"    // called for each newline (ch == '\\n') and all characters specified "
"in\n"
"    // the global variable triggerCharacters. When calling "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Tools</guimenu><guimenuitem>Format Indentation</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice>\n"
"    // the variable ch is empty, i.e. ch == ''.\n"
"    //\n"
"    // see also: Scripting API\n"
"    return -2;\n"
"}\n"
"</programlisting> The function <function>indent()</function> has three "
"parameters: <itemizedlist> <listitem><para><literal>line</literal>: the line "
"that has to be indented</para></listitem> "
"<listitem><para><literal>indentWidth</literal>: the indentation width in "
"number of spaces</para></listitem> <listitem><para><literal>ch</literal>: "
"either a newline character (<literal>ch == '\\n'</literal>), the trigger "
"character specified in <literal>triggerCharacters</literal> or empty if the "
"user invoked the action <menuchoice><guimenu>Tools</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Format Indentation</guimenuitem></menuchoice>.</para></"
"listitem> </itemizedlist> The return value of the <function>indent()</"
"function> function specifies how the line will be indented. If the return "
"value is a simple integer number, it is interpreted as follows: "
"<itemizedlist> <listitem><para>return value <literal>-2</literal>: do "
"nothing</para></listitem> <listitem><para>return value <literal>-1</"
"literal>: keep indentation (searches for previous non-blank line)</para></"
"listitem> <listitem><para>return value <literal> 0</literal>: numbers &gt;= "
"0 specify the indentation depth in spaces</para></listitem> </itemizedlist> "
"Alternatively, an array of two elements can be returned: <itemizedlist> "
"<listitem><para><literal>return [ indent, align ];</literal></para></"
"listitem> </itemizedlist> In this case, the first element is the indentation "
"depth as above with the same meaning of the special values. However, the "
"second element is an absolute value representing a column for "
"<quote>alignment</quote>. If this value is higher than the indent value, the "
"difference represents a number of spaces to be added after the indentation "
"of the first parameter. Otherwise, the second number is ignored. Using tabs "
"and spaces for indentation is often referred to as <quote>mixed mode</quote>."
msgstr ""
"Ko smo določili glavo, ta razdelek pojasnjuje, kako deluje sam skript za "
"zamik. Osnovno okostje telesa izgleda takole: <programlisting>\n"
"// zahtevane knjižnice katepart js, &eg; range.js, če uporabljate Range\n"
"zahtevaj (\"range.js\");\n"
"\n"
"triggerCharacters = \"{}/:;\";\n"
"funkcija indent(vrstica, indentWidth, ch)\n"
"{\n"
"     // klicano za vsako novo vrstico (ch == '\\n') in vse znake, navedene "
"v\n"
"     // globalna spremenljivka triggerCharacters. Pri klicu "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Orodja</guimenu><guimenuitem>Zamik oblikovanja</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice>\n"
"     // spremenljivka ch je prazna, tj. ch == ''.\n"
"     //\n"
"     // glejte tudi: API za skriptiranje\n"
"     vrnitev -2;\n"
"}\n"
"</programlisting> Funkcija <function>indent()</function> ima tri parametre: "
"<itemizedlist> <listitem><para><literal>vrstica</literal>: vrstica, ki jo je "
"treba zamakniti</para></listitem> <listitem><para><literal>indentWidth</"
"literal>: širina zamika v številu presledkov</para></listitem> "
"<listitem><para><literal>ch</literal>: bodisi znak za novo vrstico "
"(<literal>ch == '\\n'</literal>), sprožilni znak, določen v "
"<literal>sprožilniZnaki</literal> ali prazen, če je uporabnik priklical "
"dejanje <menuchoice><guimenu>Orodja</guimenu ><guimenuitem>Oblika zamika</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice>.</para></listitem> </itemizedlist> Vrnjena "
"vrednost funkcije <function>indent()</function> določa, kako bo vrstica "
"zamaknjena . Če je vrnjena vrednost preprosto celo število, se razlaga na "
"naslednji način: <itemizedlist> <listitem><para>vrnjena vrednost "
"<literal>-2</literal>: ne naredi ničesar</para></listitem> <listitem> "
"<para>vrnjena vrednost <literal>-1</literal>: ohrani zamik (išče prejšnjo "
"neprazno vrstico)</para></listitem> <listitem><para>vrne vrednost <literal> "
"0</literal> : numbers &gt;= 0 določajo globino zamika v presledkih</para></"
"listitem> </itemizedlist> Druga možnost je, da se vrne niz dveh elementov: "
"<itemizedlist> <listitem><para><literal>return [ indent , align ];</"
"literal></para></listitem> </itemizedlist> V tem primeru je prvi element "
"globina zamika kot zgoraj z enakim pomenom posebnih vrednosti. Vendar pa je "
"drugi element absolutna vrednost, ki predstavlja stolpec za "
"<quote>poravnavo</quote>. Če je ta vrednost višja od vrednosti zamika, "
"razlika predstavlja število presledkov, ki jih je treba dodati po zamiku "
"prvega parametra. V nasprotnem primeru se druga številka ne upošteva. "
"Uporaba tabulatorjev in presledkov za zamik se pogosto imenuje <quote>mešani "
"način</quote>."

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:2489
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Consider the following example: Assume using tabs to indent, and tab width "
"is set to 4. Here, &lt;tab&gt; represents a tab and '.' a space: "
"<programlisting>\n"
"1: &lt;tab&gt;&lt;tab&gt;foobar(\"hello\",\n"
"2: &lt;tab&gt;&lt;tab&gt;.......\"world\");\n"
"</programlisting> When indenting line 2, the <function>indent()</function> "
"function returns [8, 15]. As result, two tabs are inserted to indent to "
"column 8, and 7 spaces are added to align the second parameter under the "
"first, so that it stays aligned if the file is viewed with a different tab "
"width."
msgstr ""
"Razmislite o naslednjem primeru: Predpostavimo, da za zamik uporabljate "
"tabulatorje, širina tabulatorja pa je nastavljena na 4. Tukaj &lt;tab&gt; "
"predstavlja zavihek in '.' presledek: <programlisting>\n"
"1: &lt;tab&gt;&lt;tab&gt;foobar(\"zdravo\",\n"
"2: &lt;tab&gt;&lt;tab&gt;.......\"svet\");\n"
"</programlisting> Pri zamiku vrstice 2 vrne funkcija <function>indent()</"
"function> [8, 15]. Posledično sta vstavljena dva zavihka za zamik v stolpec "
"8 in dodanih je 7 presledkov za poravnavo drugega parametra pod prvim, tako "
"da ostane poravnan, če si datoteko ogledate z drugačno širino zavihka."

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:2499
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A default &kde; installation ships &kappname; with several indenters. The "
"corresponding &javascript; source code can be found in <filename>"
"$<envar>XDG_DATA_DIRS</envar>/katepart5/script/indentation</filename>."
msgstr ""
"Privzeti &kde; namestitev pošilja &kappname; z več vdolbinami. Ustrezni "
"&javascript; izvorno kodo lahko najdete v <filename>$<envar>XDG_DATA_DIRS</"
"envar>/katepart5/script/indentation</filename>."

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:2506
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Developing an indenter requires reloading the scripts to see whether the "
"changes behave appropriately. Instead of restarting the application, simply "
"switch to the command line and invoke the command <command>reload-scripts</"
"command>."
msgstr ""
"Razvijanje zamika zahteva ponovno nalaganje skriptov, da se preveri, ali se "
"spremembe obnašajo ustrezno. Namesto ponovnega zagona aplikacije preprosto "
"preklopite v ukazno vrstico in pokličite ukaz <command>reload-scripts</"
"command>."

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:2512 development.docbook:2624
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you develop useful scripts please consider contributing to the &kappname; "
"Project by providing a merge request to <ulink url=\"https://invent.kde.org/"
"frameworks/ktexteditor\">our GitLab project</ulink>."
msgstr ""
"Če razvijate uporabne skripte, prosimo, razmislite o prispevanju k projektu "
"&kappname; tako da pošljete zahtevo za združitev na <ulink url=\"https://"
"invent.kde.org/frameworks/ktexteditor\">naš projekt GitLab</ulink>."

#. Tag: title
#: development.docbook:2521
#, no-c-format
msgid "Command Line Scripts"
msgstr "Skripti ukazne vrstice"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:2524
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A functionality similar to command line scripts is also provided in the "
"<ulink url=\"help:/kate/kate-application-plugin-snippets.html\">snippets "
"plugin</ulink>. This plugin may provide an easier starting point, especially "
"for small custom scripts."
msgstr ""
"Funkcionalnost, podobna skriptom ukazne vrstice, je na voljo tudi v <ulink "
"url=\"help:/kate/kate-application-plugin-snippets.html\">vtičniku koščkov "
"kode</ulink>. Ta vtičnik lahko ponudi lažje izhodišče, zlasti za majhne "
"skripte po meri."

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:2529
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"As it is hard to satisfy everyone's needs, &kappname; supports little helper "
"tools for quick text manipulation through the <link linkend=\"advanced-"
"editing-tools-commandline\">built-in command line</link>. For instance, the "
"command <command>sort</command> is implemented as a script. This section "
"explains how to create <filename>*.js</filename> files to extend &kappname; "
"with arbitrary helper scripts."
msgstr ""
"Ker je težko zadovoljiti potrebe vseh, je &kappname; podpira majhna pomočna "
"orodja za hitro manipulacijo besedila prek <link linkend=\"advanced-editing-"
"tools-commandline\">vgrajene ukazne vrstice</link>. Na primer, ukaz "
"<command>sort</command> je implementiran kot skript. Ta razdelek pojasnjuje, "
"kako ustvariti datoteke <filename>*.js</filename> za razširitev &kappname; s "
"poljubnimi pomožnimi skripti."

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:2538
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Command line scripts are located in the same folder as indentation scripts. "
"So as a first step, create a new <filename>*.js</filename> file called "
"<filename>myutils.js</filename> in the local home folder <filename>"
"$<envar>XDG_DATA_HOME</envar>/katepart5/script/commands</filename>. Therein, "
"the environment variable <envar>XDG_DATA_HOME</envar> typically expands to "
"either <filename>~/.local</filename> or <filename>~/.local/share</filename>."
msgstr ""
"Skripti ukazne vrstice se nahajajo v isti mapi kot skripti za zamik. Torej "
"kot prvi korak ustvarite novo datoteko <filename>*.js</filename> z imenom "
"<filename>myutils.js</filename> v lokalni domači mapi <filename>"
"$<envar>XDG_DATA_HOME</envar>/katepart5 /script/commands</filename>. Tam se "
"spremenljivka okolja <envar>XDG_DATA_HOME</envar> običajno razširi na "
"<filename>~/.local</filename> ali <filename>~/.local/share</filename>."

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:2545
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"On &Windows; these files are located in <filename>%USERPROFILE%\\AppData"
"\\Local\\katepart5\\script\\commands</filename>. <replaceable>%USERPROFILE%</"
"replaceable> usually expands to <filename>C:\\\\Users\\\\<replaceable>user</"
"replaceable></filename>."
msgstr ""
"V &Windows; te datoteke se nahajajo v <filename>%USERPROFILE%\\AppData\\Local"
"\\katepart5\\script\\commands</filename>. <replaceable>%USERPROFILE%</"
"replaceable> se običajno razširi v <filename>C:\\\\Users\\"
"\\<replaceable>user</replaceable></filename>."

#. Tag: title
#: development.docbook:2550
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Command Line Script Header"
msgstr "Glava skripta ukazne vrstice"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:2551
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The header of each command line script is embedded in &JSON; at the "
"beginning of the script as follows: <programlisting>\n"
"var katescript = {\n"
"    \"author\": \"Example Name &lt;example.name@some.address.org&gt;\",\n"
"    \"license\": \"LGPLv2+\",\n"
"    \"revision\": 1,\n"
"    \"kate-version\": \"5.1\",\n"
"    \"functions\": [\"sort\", \"moveLinesDown\"],\n"
"    \"actions\": [\n"
"        {   \"function\": \"sort\",\n"
"            \"name\": \"Sort Selected Text\",\n"
"            \"category\": \"Editing\",\n"
"            \"interactive\": \"false\"\n"
"        },\n"
"        {   \"function\": \"moveLinesDown\",\n"
"            \"name\": \"Move Lines Down\",\n"
"            \"category\": \"Editing\",\n"
"            \"shortcut\": \"Ctrl+Shift+Down\",\n"
"            \"interactive\": \"false\"\n"
"        }\n"
"    ]\n"
"}; // kate-script-header, must be at the start of the file without comments\n"
"</programlisting> Each entry is explained in detail now:"
msgstr ""
"Glava vsakega skripta ukazne vrstice je vdelana v &JSON; na začetku skripta "
"kot sledi: <programlisting>\n"
"var katescript = {\n"
"     \"avtor\": \"Primer imena &lt;example.name@some.address.org&gt;\",\n"
"     \"licenca\": \"LGPLv2+\",\n"
"     \"revizija\": 1,\n"
"     \"kate-različica\": \"5.1\",\n"
"     \"funkcije\": [\"sort\", \"moveLinesDown\"],\n"
"     \"akcije\": [\n"
"         { \"funkcija\": \"razvrsti\",\n"
"             \"ime\": \"Razvrsti izbrano besedilo\",\n"
"             \"kategorija\": \"Urejanje\",\n"
"             \"interactive\": \"false\"\n"
"         },\n"
"         { \"funkcija\": \"premakniLinesDown\",\n"
"             \"ime\": \"Premakni vrstice navzdol\",\n"
"             \"kategorija\": \"Urejanje\",\n"
"             \"bližnjica\": \"Ctrl+Shift+dol\",\n"
"             \"interactive\": \"false\"\n"
"         }\n"
"     ]\n"
"}; // kate-script-header, mora biti na začetku datoteke brez komentarjev\n"
"</programlisting> Vsak vnos je zdaj podrobno razložen:"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:2559
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<literal>license</literal> [optional]: Short form of the license, such as "
"BSD License or LGPLv2."
msgstr ""
"<literal>licenca</literal> [izbirno]: kratka oblika licence, kot je licenca "
"BSD ali LGPLv2."

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:2562
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<literal>functions</literal> [required]: &JSON; array of commands in the "
"script."
msgstr "<literal>funkcije</literal> [obvezno]: &JSON; niz ukazov v skriptu."

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:2563
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<literal>actions</literal> [optional]: &JSON; Array of &JSON; objects that "
"defines the actions that appear in the application menu. Detailed "
"information is provided in the section <link linkend=\"advanced-editing-"
"tools-commandline\">Binding Shortcuts</link>."
msgstr ""
"<literal>dejanja</literal> [izbirno]: &JSON; Niz &JSON; objekte, ki določajo "
"dejanja, ki se prikažejo v meniju aplikacije. Podrobne informacije so na "
"voljo v razdelku <link linkend=\"advanced-editing-tools-commandline"
"\">Bližnjice za vezavo</link>."

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:2567
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Since the value of <literal>functions</literal> is a &JSON; array, a single "
"script is able to contain an arbitrary number of command line commands. Each "
"function is available through &kappname;'s <link linkend=\"advanced-editing-"
"tools-commandline\">built-in command line</link>."
msgstr ""
"Ker je vrednost <literal>funkcij</literal> &JSON; array, lahko en sam skript "
"vsebuje poljubno število ukazov ukazne vrstice. Vsaka funkcija je na voljo "
"prek <link linkend=\"advanced-editing-tools-commandline\">vgrajene ukazne "
"vrstice</link> &kappname;."

#. Tag: title
#: development.docbook:2575
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Script Source Code"
msgstr "Izvorna koda skripta"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:2577
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"All functions specified in the header have to be implemented in the script. "
"For instance, the script file from the example above needs to implement the "
"two functions <command>sort</command> and <command>moveLinesDown</command>. "
"All functions have the following syntax:"
msgstr ""
"Vse funkcije, navedene v glavi, morajo biti implementirane v skriptu. Na "
"primer, datoteka skripta iz zgornjega primera mora implementirati dve "
"funkciji <command>uredi</command> in <command>premakniVrsticoDol</command>. "
"Vse funkcije imajo naslednjo sintakso:"

#. Tag: programlisting
#: development.docbook:2583
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"// required katepart js libraries, &eg; range.js if you use Range\n"
"require (\"range.js\");\n"
"\n"
"function &lt;name&gt;(arg1, arg2, ...)\n"
"{\n"
"    // ... implementation, see also: Scripting API\n"
"}"
msgstr ""
"// zahtevane knjižnice katepart js, &eg; range.js, če uporabljate Range\n"
"zahtevaj (\"range.js\");\n"
"\n"
"&lt;ime&gt; funkcije (arg1, arg2, ...)\n"
"{\n"
"     // ... implementacija, glejte tudi: API za skriptiranje\n"
"}"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:2586
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Arguments in the command line are passed to the function as <parameter>arg1</"
"parameter>, <parameter>arg2</parameter>, &etc; In order to provide "
"documentation for each command, simply implement the '<function>help</"
"function>' function as follows: <programlisting>\n"
"function help(cmd)\n"
"{\n"
"    if (cmd == \"sort\") {\n"
"        return i18n(\"Sort the selected text.\");\n"
"    } else if (cmd == \"...\") {\n"
"        // ...\n"
"    }\n"
"}\n"
"</programlisting> Executing <command>help sort</command> in the command line "
"then calls this help function with the argument <parameter>cmd</parameter> "
"set to the given command, &ie; <parameter>cmd == \"sort\"</parameter>. "
"&kappname; then presents the returned text as documentation to the user. "
"Make sure to <link linkend=\"dev-scripting-api-i18n\">translate the strings</"
"link>."
msgstr ""
"Argumenti v ukazni vrstici so posredovani funkciji kot <parameter>arg1</"
"parameter>, <parameter>arg2</parameter> &etc; Če želite zagotoviti "
"dokumentacijo za vsak ukaz, preprosto implementirajte funkcijo "
"'<function>pomoč</function>', kot sledi: <programlisting>\n"
"funkcija pomoč (cmd)\n"
"{\n"
"     če (cmd == \"razvrsti\") {\n"
"         return i18n(\"Razvrsti izbrano besedilo.\");\n"
"     } else if (cmd == \"...\") {\n"
"         // ...\n"
"     }\n"
"}\n"
"</programlisting> Izvajanje <command>help sort</command> v ukazni vrstici "
"nato pokliče to funkcijo pomoči z argumentom <parameter>cmd</parameter>, "
"nastavljenim na podani ukaz, &ie; <parameter>cmd == \"sort\"</parameter>. "
"&kappname; nato uporabniku vrnjeno besedilo predstavi kot dokumentacijo. Ne "
"pozabite <link linkend=\"dev-scripting-api-i18n\">prevesti nize</link>."

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:2601
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Developing a command line script requires reloading the scripts to see "
"whether the changes behave appropriately. Instead of restarting the "
"application, simply switch to the command line and invoke the command "
"<command>reload-scripts</command>."
msgstr ""
"Razvijanje skripta ukazne vrstice zahteva ponovno nalaganje skriptov, da se "
"preveri, ali se spremembe obnašajo ustrezno. Namesto ponovnega zagona "
"aplikacije preprosto preklopite v ukazno vrstico in pokličite ukaz "
"<command>reload-scripts</command>."

#. Tag: title
#: development.docbook:2608
#, no-c-format
msgid "Binding Shortcuts"
msgstr "Bližnjice za vezavo"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:2609
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In order to make the scripts accessible in the application menu and assign "
"shortcuts, the script needs to provide an appropriate script header. In the "
"above example, both functions <literal>sort</literal> and "
"<literal>moveLinesDown</literal> appear in the menu due to the following "
"part in the script header: <programlisting>\n"
"var katescript = {\n"
"    ...\n"
"    \"actions\": [\n"
"        {   \"function\": \"sort\",\n"
"            \"name\": \"Sort Selected Text\",\n"
"            \"icon\": \"\",\n"
"            \"category\": \"Editing\",\n"
"            \"interactive\": \"false\"\n"
"        },\n"
"        {   \"function\": \"moveLinesDown\",\n"
"            \"name\": \"Move Lines Down\",\n"
"            \"icon\": \"\",\n"
"            \"category\": \"Editing\",\n"
"            \"shortcut\": \"Ctrl+Shift+Down\",\n"
"            \"interactive\": \"false\"\n"
"        }\n"
"    ]\n"
"};\n"
"</programlisting> The fields for one action are as follows:"
msgstr ""
"Če želite omogočiti dostop do skriptov v meniju aplikacije in dodeliti "
"bližnjice, mora skript zagotoviti ustrezno glavo skripta. V zgornjem primeru "
"sta obe funkciji <literal>sort</literal> in <literal>moveLinesDown</literal> "
"prikazani v meniju zaradi naslednjega dela v glavi skripta: "
"<programlisting>\n"
"var katescript = {\n"
"     ...\n"
"     \"akcije\": [\n"
"         { \"funkcija\": \"razvrsti\",\n"
"             \"ime\": \"Razvrsti izbrano besedilo\",\n"
"             \"ikona\": \"\",\n"
"             \"kategorija\": \"Urejanje\",\n"
"             \"interactive\": \"false\"\n"
"         },\n"
"         { \"funkcija\": \"premakniLinesDown\",\n"
"             \"ime\": \"Premakni vrstice navzdol\",\n"
"             \"ikona\": \"\",\n"
"             \"kategorija\": \"Urejanje\",\n"
"             \"bližnjica\": \"Ctrl+Shift+dol\",\n"
"             \"interactive\": \"false\"\n"
"         }\n"
"     ]\n"
"};\n"
"</programlisting> Polja za eno dejanje so naslednja:"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:2615
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<literal>function</literal> [required]: The function that should appear in "
"the menu <menuchoice><guimenu>Tools</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Scripts</"
"guisubmenu></menuchoice>."
msgstr ""
"<literal>funkcija</literal> [zahtevano]: Funkcija, ki bi se morala pojaviti "
"v meniju <menuchoice><guimenu>Orodja</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Skripti</"
"guisubmenu></menuchoice>."

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:2616
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<literal>name</literal> [required]: The text appears in the script menu."
msgstr ""
"<literal>ime</literal> [zahtevano]: Besedilo se pojavi v meniju skripta."

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:2617
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<literal>icon</literal> [optional]: The icon appears next to the text in the "
"menu. All &kde; icon names can be used here."
msgstr ""
"<literal>ikona</literal> [neobvezno]: Ikona se pojavi poleg besedila v "
"meniju. Vsi &kde; tukaj lahko uporabite imena ikon."

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:2618
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<literal>category</literal> [optional]: If a category is specified, the "
"script appears in a submenu."
msgstr ""
"<literal>kategorija</literal> [izbirno]: če je podana kategorija, se skript "
"pojavi v podmeniju."

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:2619
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<literal>shortcut</literal> [optional]: The shortcut given here is the "
"default shortcut. Example: <literal>Ctrl+Alt+t</literal>. See the <ulink url="
"\"https://doc.qt.io/qt-5/qt.html#Key-enum\">&Qt; documentation</ulink> for "
"further details."
msgstr ""
"<literal>bližnjica</literal> [izbirno]: tukaj podana bližnjica je privzeta "
"bližnjica. Primer: <literal>Ctrl+Alt+t</literal>. Oglejte si <ulink url="
"\"https://doc.qt.io/qt-5/qt.html#Key-enum\">&Qt; dokumentacija</ulink> za "
"nadaljnje podrobnosti."

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:2620
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<literal>interactive</literal> [optional]: If the script needs user input in "
"the command line, set this to <literal>true</literal>."
msgstr ""
"<literal>interactive</literal> [neobvezno]: Če skript potrebuje uporabniški "
"vnos v ukazni vrstici, to nastavite na <literal>true</literal>."

#. Tag: title
#: development.docbook:2634
#, no-c-format
msgid "Scripting API"
msgstr "API za skriptiranje"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:2636
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The scripting API presented here is available to all scripts, &ie; "
"indentation scripts and command line commands. The <classname>Cursor</"
"classname> and <classname>Range</classname> classes are provided by library "
"files in <filename>$<envar>XDG_DATA_DIRS</envar>/katepart5/libraries</"
"filename>. If you want to use them in your script, which needs to use some "
"of the <classname>Document</classname> or <classname>View</classname> "
"functions, please include the necessary library by using:"
msgstr ""
"Tukaj predstavljeni skriptni API je na voljo za vse skripte, &ie; skripte za "
"zamik in ukaze ukazne vrstice. Razreda <classname>Cursor</classname> in "
"<classname>Range</classname> zagotavljajo knjižnične datoteke v <filename>"
"$<envar>XDG_DATA_DIRS</envar>/katepart5/libraries</filename>. Če jih želite "
"uporabiti v svojem skriptu, ki mora uporabiti nekatere funkcije "
"<classname>Document</classname> ali <classname>View</classname>, vključite "
"potrebno knjižnico z uporabo:"

#. Tag: programlisting
#: development.docbook:2642
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"// required katepart js libraries, &eg; range.js if you use Range\n"
"require (\"range.js\");"
msgstr ""
"// zahtevane knjižnice katepart js, &eg; range.js, če uporabljate Range\n"
"require (\"range.js\");"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:2645
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To extend the standard scripting API with your own functions and prototypes "
"simply create a new file in &kde;'s local configuration folder <filename>"
"$<envar>XDG_DATA_HOME</envar>/katepart5/libraries</filename> and include it "
"into your script using:"
msgstr ""
"Če želite razširiti standardni skriptni API z lastnimi funkcijami in "
"prototipi, preprosto ustvarite novo datoteko v lokalni konfiguracijski mapi "
"&kde; <filename>$<envar>XDG_DATA_HOME</envar>/katepart5/libraries</filename> "
"in jo vključite v svoj skript z uporabo:"

#. Tag: programlisting
#: development.docbook:2650
#, no-c-format
msgid "require (\"myscriptnamehere.js\");"
msgstr "require (\"myscriptnamehere.js\");"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:2654
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"On &Windows; these files are located in <filename>%USERPROFILE%\\AppData"
"\\Local\\katepart5\\libraries</filename>. <replaceable>%USERPROFILE%</"
"replaceable> usually expands to <filename>C:\\\\Users\\\\<replaceable>user</"
"replaceable></filename>."
msgstr ""
"V &Windows; te datoteke se nahajajo v <filename>%USERPROFILE%\\AppData\\Local"
"\\katepart5\\libraries</filename>. <replaceable>%USERPROFILE%</replaceable> "
"se običajno razširi v <filename>C:\\\\Users\\\\<replaceable>uporabnik</"
"replaceable></filename>."

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:2657
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To extend existing prototypes like <classname>Cursor</classname> or "
"<classname>Range</classname>, the recommended way is to <emphasis>not</"
"emphasis> modify the global <filename>*.js</filename> files. Instead, change "
"the <classname>Cursor</classname> prototype in &javascript; after the "
"<filename>cursor.js</filename> is included into your script via "
"<literal>require</literal>."
msgstr ""
"Če želite razširiti obstoječe prototipe, kot sta <classname>Kazalka</"
"classname> ali <classname>Doseg</classname>, je priporočen način, da "
"<emphasis>ne</emphasis> spreminjate globalnih datotek <filename>*.js</"
"filename> . Namesto tega spremenite prototip <classname>Kazalka</classname> "
"v &javascript; potem ko je <filename>cursor.js</filename> vključen v vaš "
"skript prek <literal>potrebuje</literal>."

#. Tag: title
#: development.docbook:2666
#, no-c-format
msgid "Cursors and Ranges"
msgstr "Kazalci in Dosegi"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:2668
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"As &kappname; is a text editor, all the scripting API is based on cursors "
"and ranges whenever possible. A Cursor is a simple <literal>(line, column)</"
"literal> tuple representing a text position in the document. A Range spans "
"text from a starting cursor position to an ending cursor position. The API "
"is explained in detail in the next sections."
msgstr ""
"Kot &kappname; je urejevalnik besedil, vsi skriptni API temeljijo na "
"kazalcih in obsegih, kadar koli je to mogoče. Kazalec je preprost nabor "
"<literal>(vrstica, stolpec)</literal>, ki predstavlja položaj besedila v "
"dokumentu. Obseg obsega besedilo od začetnega položaja kazalca do končnega "
"položaja kazalca. API je podrobno razložen v naslednjih razdelkih."

#. Tag: title
#: development.docbook:2677
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Cursor Prototype"
msgstr "Prototip kazalca"

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:2680
#, no-c-format
msgid "Cursor();"
msgstr "Cursor();"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:2681
#, no-c-format
msgid "Constructor. Returns a Cursor at position <literal>(0, 0)</literal>."
msgstr "Constructor. Vrne kazalko na položaju <literal>(0, 0)</literal>."

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:2683
#, no-c-format
msgid "Example: <function>var cursor = new Cursor();</function>"
msgstr "Primer: <function>var cursor = new Cursor();</function>"

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:2689
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Cursor(<parameter>int <replaceable>line</replaceable></parameter>, "
"<parameter>int <replaceable>column</replaceable></parameter>);"
msgstr ""
"Cursor(<parameter>int <replaceable>vrstica</replaceable></parameter>, "
"<parameter>int <replaceable>column</replaceable></parameter>);"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:2690
#, no-c-format
msgid "Constructor. Returns a Cursor at position (line, column)."
msgstr "Constructor. Vrne kazalec na položaj (vrstica, stolpec)."

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:2693
#, no-c-format
msgid "Example: <function>var cursor = new Cursor(3, 42);</function>"
msgstr "Primer: <function>var cursor = new Cursor(3, 42);</function>"

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:2699
#, no-c-format
msgid "Cursor(<parameter>Cursor <replaceable>other</replaceable></parameter>);"
msgstr ""
"Cursor(<parameter>Cursor <replaceable>other</replaceable></parameter>);"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:2700
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Copy constructor. Returns a copy of the cursor <replaceable>other</"
"replaceable>."
msgstr ""
"Kopija construktorja. Vrne kopijo kazalca <replaceable>drugo</replaceable>."

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:2703
#, no-c-format
msgid "Example: <function>var copy = new Cursor(other);</function>"
msgstr "Primer: <function>var copy = new Cursor(other);</function>"

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:2709
#, no-c-format
msgid "Cursor Cursor.clone();"
msgstr "Kazalec Cursor.clone();"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:2710
#, no-c-format
msgid "Returns a clone of the cursor."
msgstr "Vrne klon kazalke."

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:2712
#, no-c-format
msgid "Example: <function>var clone = cursor.clone();</function>"
msgstr "Primer: <function>var clone = cursor.clone();</function>"

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:2718
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Cursor.setPosition(<parameter>int <replaceable>line</replaceable></"
"parameter>, <parameter>int <replaceable>column</replaceable></parameter>);"
msgstr ""
"Cursor.setPosition(<parameter>int <replaceable>vrstica</replaceable></"
"parameter>, <parameter>int <replaceable>stolpec</replaceable></parameter>);"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:2719
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Sets the cursor position to <replaceable>line</replaceable> and "
"<replaceable>column</replaceable>."
msgstr ""
"Nastavi položaj kazalca na <replaceable>vrstica</replaceable> in "
"<replaceable>stolpec</replaceable>."

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:2721 development.docbook:2833
#, no-c-format
msgid "Since: &kde; 4.11"
msgstr "Od: &kde; 4.11"

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:2728
#, no-c-format
msgid "bool Cursor.isValid();"
msgstr "bool Cursor.isValid();"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:2729
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Check whether the cursor is valid. The cursor is invalid, if line and/or "
"column are set to <literal>-1</literal>."
msgstr ""
"Preverite, ali je kazalec veljaven. Kazalec ni veljaven, če sta vrstica in/"
"ali stolpec nastavljena na <literal>-1</literal>."

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:2733
#, no-c-format
msgid "Example: <function>var valid = cursor.isValid();</function>"
msgstr "Primer: <function>var valid = cursor.isValid();</function>"

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:2740
#, no-c-format
msgid "Cursor Cursor.invalid();"
msgstr "Kazalka Cursor.invalid();"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:2741
#, no-c-format
msgid "Returns a new invalid cursor located at <literal>(-1, -1)</literal>."
msgstr ""
"Vrne novo neveljavno kazalko, ki se nahaja na <literal>(-1, -1)</literal>."

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:2744
#, no-c-format
msgid "Example: <function>var invalidCursor = cursor.invalid();</function>"
msgstr "Primer: <function>var invalidCursor = cursor.invalid();</function>"

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:2749
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"int Cursor.compareTo(<parameter>Cursor <replaceable>other</replaceable></"
"parameter>);"
msgstr ""
"int Cursor.compareTo(<parameter>Kazalka <replaceable>drugo</replaceable></"
"parameter>);"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:2750
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Compares this cursor to the cursor <replaceable>other</replaceable>. Returns"
msgstr "Primerja ta kazalec s kazalcem <replaceable>drugo</replaceable>. Vrača"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:2753
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<literal>-1</literal>, if this cursor is located before the cursor "
"<replaceable>other</replaceable>,"
msgstr ""
"<literal>-1</literal>, če se ta kazalec nahaja pred kazalcem "
"<replaceable>other</replaceable>,"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:2754
#, no-c-format
msgid "<literal>0</literal>, if both cursors equal and"
msgstr "<literal>0</literal>, če sta oba kazalca enaka in"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:2755
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<literal>+1</literal>, if this cursor is located after the cursor "
"<replaceable>other</replaceable>."
msgstr ""
"<literal> 1</literal>, če se ta kazalec nahaja za kazalcem "
"<replaceable>other</replaceable>."

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:2762
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"bool Cursor.equals(<parameter>Cursor <replaceable>other</replaceable></"
"parameter>);"
msgstr ""
"bool Cursor.equals(<parameter>Kazalec <replaceable>other</replaceable></"
"parameter>);"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:2763
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Returns <literal>true</literal>, if this cursor and the cursor "
"<replaceable>other</replaceable> are equal, otherwise <literal>false</"
"literal>."
msgstr ""
"Vrne <literal>true</literal>, če sta ta kazalec in kazalec "
"<replaceable>other</replaceable> enaka, sicer <literal>false</literal>."

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:2771
#, no-c-format
msgid "String Cursor.toString();"
msgstr "Niz Cursor.toString();"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:2772
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Returns the cursor as a string of the form <quote><literal>Cursor(line, "
"column)</literal></quote>."
msgstr ""
"Vrne kazalec kot niz v obliki <quote><literal>Kazalec(vrstica, stolpec)</"
"literal></quote>."

#. Tag: title
#: development.docbook:2781
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Range Prototype"
msgstr "Prototip dometa"

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:2784
#, no-c-format
msgid "Range();"
msgstr "Obseg();"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:2785
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Constructor. Calling <literal>new Range()</literal> returns a Range at (0, "
"0) - (0, 0)."
msgstr ""
"Constructor. Calling <literal>new Range()</literal> returns a Range at (0, "
"0) - (0, 0)."

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:2792
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Range(<parameter>Cursor <replaceable>start</replaceable></parameter>, "
"<parameter>Cursor <replaceable>end</replaceable></parameter>);"
msgstr ""
"Range(<parameter>Kazalec <replaceable>start</replaceable></parameter>, "
"<parameter>Cursor <replaceable>end</replaceable></parameter>);"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:2793
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Constructor. Calling <literal>new Range(<replaceable>start</replaceable>, "
"<replaceable>end</replaceable>)</literal> returns the Range "
"(<replaceable>start</replaceable>, <replaceable>end</replaceable>)."
msgstr ""
"Konstruktor. Klic <literal>new Range(<replaceable>začetek</replaceable>, "
"<replaceable>konec</replaceable>)</literal> vrne obseg "
"(<replaceable>začetek</replaceable>, <replaceable>konec</replaceable> )."

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:2800
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Range(<parameter>int <replaceable>startLine</replaceable></parameter>, "
"<parameter>int <replaceable>startColumn</replaceable></parameter>, "
"<parameter>int <replaceable>endLine</replaceable></parameter>, "
"<parameter>int <replaceable>endColumn</replaceable></parameter>);"
msgstr ""
"Obseg(<parameter>int <replaceable>startLine</replaceable></parameter>, "
"<parameter>int <replaceable>startColumn</replaceable></parameter>, "
"<parameter>int <replaceable>endLine</replaceable></parameter>, "
"<parameter>int <replaceable>endColumn</replaceable></parameter>);"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:2801
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Constructor. Calling <literal>new Range(<replaceable>startLine</"
"replaceable>, <replaceable>startColumn</replaceable>, <replaceable>endLine</"
"replaceable>, <replaceable>endColumn</replaceable>)</literal> returns the "
"Range from (<replaceable>startLine</replaceable>, <replaceable>startColumn</"
"replaceable>) to (<replaceable>endLine</replaceable>, "
"<replaceable>endColumn</replaceable>)."
msgstr ""
"Konstruktor. Klic <literal>new Range(<replaceable>startLine</replaceable>, "
"<replaceable>startColumn</replaceable>, <replaceable>endLine</replaceable>, "
"<replaceable>endColumn</replaceable>)</literal> vrne obseg od "
"(<replaceable>začetna vrstica</replaceable>, <replaceable>startColumn</"
"replaceable>) v (<replaceable>endLine</replaceable>, <replaceable>endColumn</"
"replaceable>)."

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:2809
#, no-c-format
msgid "Range(<parameter>Range <replaceable>other</replaceable></parameter>);"
msgstr ""
"Razpon(<parameter>Razpon <replaceable>other</replaceable></parameter>);"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:2810
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Copy constructor. Returns a copy of Range <replaceable>other</replaceable>."
msgstr ""
"Konstruktor kopij. Vrne kopijo obsega <replaceable>drugo</replaceable>."

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:2817
#, no-c-format
msgid "Range Range.clone();"
msgstr "Obseg Range.clone();"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:2818
#, no-c-format
msgid "Returns a clone of the range."
msgstr "Vrne klon dosega."

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:2821
#, no-c-format
msgid "Example: <function>var clone = range.clone();</function>"
msgstr "Primer: <function>var clone = range.clone();</function>"

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:2827
#, no-c-format
msgid "bool Range.isEmpty();"
msgstr "bool Range.isEmpty();"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:2828
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Returns <literal>true</literal>, if the start and end cursors are equal."
msgstr "Vrne <literal>true</literal>, če sta začetni in končni kazalec enaka."

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:2831
#, no-c-format
msgid "Example: <function>var empty = range.isEmpty();</function>"
msgstr "Primer: <function>var empty = range.isEmpty();</function>"

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:2840
#, no-c-format
msgid "bool Range.isValid();"
msgstr "bool Range.isValid();"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:2841
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Returns <literal>true</literal>, if both start and end cursor are valid, "
"otherwise <literal>false</literal>."
msgstr ""
"Vrne <literal>true</literal>, če sta začetni in končni kazalec veljavna, "
"sicer <literal>false</literal>."

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:2844
#, no-c-format
msgid "Example: <function>var valid = range.isValid();</function>"
msgstr "Primer: <function>var valid = range.isValid();</function>"

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:2850
#, no-c-format
msgid "Range Range.invalid();"
msgstr "Obseg Range.invalid();"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:2851
#, no-c-format
msgid "Returns the Range from (-1, -1) to (-1, -1)."
msgstr "Vrne obseg od (-1, -1) do (-1, -1)."

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:2858
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"bool Range.contains(<parameter>Cursor <replaceable>cursor</replaceable></"
"parameter>);"
msgstr ""
"bool Range.contains(<parameter>Kazalec <replaceable>kazalka</replaceable></"
"parameter>);"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:2859
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Returns <literal>true</literal>, if this range contains the cursor position, "
"otherwise <literal>false</literal>."
msgstr ""
"Vrne <literal>true</literal>, če ta obseg vsebuje položaj kazalke, sicer "
"<literal>false</literal>."

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:2866
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"bool Range.contains(<parameter>Range <replaceable>other</replaceable></"
"parameter>);"
msgstr ""
"bool Range.contains(<parameter>Obseg <replaceable>other</replaceable></"
"parameter>);"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:2867
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Returns <literal>true</literal>, if this range contains the Range "
"<replaceable>other</replaceable>, otherwise <literal>false</literal>."
msgstr ""
"Vrne <literal>true</literal>, če ta obseg vsebuje obseg <replaceable>other</"
"replaceable>, sicer <literal>false</literal>."

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:2875
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"bool Range.containsColumn(<parameter>int <replaceable>column</replaceable></"
"parameter>);"
msgstr ""
"bool Range.containsColumn(<parameter>int <replaceable>stolpec</replaceable></"
"parameter>);"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:2876
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Returns <literal>true</literal>, if <replaceable>column</replaceable> is in "
"the half open interval <literal>[start.column, end.column)</literal>, "
"otherwise <literal>false</literal>."
msgstr ""
"Vrne <literal>true</literal>, če je <replaceable>stolpec</replaceable> v pol "
"odprtem intervalu <literal>[start.column, end.column)</literal>, drugače "
"<literal>false</literal >."

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:2884
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"bool Range.containsLine(<parameter>int <replaceable>line</replaceable></"
"parameter>);"
msgstr ""
"bool Range.containsLine(<parameter>int <replaceable>vrstica</replaceable></"
"parameter>);"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:2885
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Returns <literal>true</literal>, if <replaceable>line</replaceable> is in "
"the half open interval <literal>[start.line, end.line)</literal>, otherwise "
"<literal>false</literal>."
msgstr ""
"Vrne <literal>true</literal>, če je <replaceable>line</replaceable> v "
"polodprtem intervalu <literal>[start.line, end.line)</literal>, drugače "
"<literal>false</literal >."

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:2893
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"bool Range.overlaps(<parameter>Range <replaceable>other</replaceable></"
"parameter>);"
msgstr ""
"bool Range.overlaps(<parameter>Obseg <replaceable>other</replaceable></"
"parameter>);"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:2894
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Returns <literal>true</literal>, if this range and the range "
"<replaceable>other</replaceable> share a common region, otherwise "
"<literal>false</literal>."
msgstr ""
"Vrne <literal>true</literal>, če imata ta obseg in obseg <replaceable>other</"
"replaceable> skupno regijo, sicer <literal>false</literal>."

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:2902
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"bool Range.overlapsLine(<parameter>int <replaceable>line</replaceable></"
"parameter>);"
msgstr ""
"bool Range.overlapsLine(<parameter>int <replaceable>vrstica</replaceable></"
"parameter>);"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:2903
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Returns <literal>true</literal>, if <replaceable>line</replaceable> is in "
"the interval <literal>[start.line, end.line]</literal>, otherwise "
"<literal>false</literal>."
msgstr ""
"Vrne <literal>true</literal>, če je <replaceable>line</replaceable> v "
"intervalu <literal>[start.line, end.line]</literal>, sicer <literal>false</"
"literal>."

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:2911
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"bool Range.overlapsColumn(<parameter>int <replaceable>column</replaceable></"
"parameter>);"
msgstr ""
"bool Range.overlapsColumn(<parameter>int <replaceable>stolpec</replaceable></"
"parameter>);"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:2912
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Returns <literal>true</literal>, if <replaceable>column</replaceable> is in "
"the interval <literal>[start.column, end.column]</literal>, otherwise "
"<literal>false</literal>."
msgstr ""
"Vrne <literal>true</literal>, če je <replaceable>stolpec</replaceable> v "
"intervalu <literal>[start.column, end.column]</literal>, sicer "
"<literal>false</literal>."

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:2920
#, no-c-format
msgid "bool Range.onSingleLine();"
msgstr "bool Range.onSingleLine();"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:2921
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Returns <literal>true</literal>, if the range starts and ends at the same "
"line, &ie; if <replaceable>Range.start.line == Range.end.line</replaceable>."
msgstr ""
"Vrne <literal>true</literal>, če se obseg začne in konča v isti vrstici, "
"&ie; če <replaceable>Range.start.line == Range.end.line</replaceable>."

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:2925 development.docbook:3359 development.docbook:3498
#, no-c-format
msgid "Since: &kde; 4.9"
msgstr "Od: &kde; 4.9"

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:2932
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"bool Range.equals(<parameter>Range <replaceable>other</replaceable></"
"parameter>);"
msgstr ""
"bool Range.equals(<parameter>Doseg <replaceable>drugo</replaceable></"
"parameter>);"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:2933
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Returns <literal>true</literal>, if this range and the Range "
"<replaceable>other</replaceable> are equal, otherwise <literal>false</"
"literal>."
msgstr ""
"Vrne <literal>true</literal>, če sta ta obseg in obseg <replaceable>drugo</"
"replaceable> enaka, sicer <literal>false</literal>."

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:2941
#, no-c-format
msgid "String Range.toString();"
msgstr "Niz Range.toString();"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:2942
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Returns the range as a string of the form <quote><literal>Range(Cursor(line, "
"column), Cursor(line, column))</literal></quote>."
msgstr ""
"Vrne obseg kot niz v obliki <quote><literal>Doseg(Kazalka(vrstica, stolpec), "
"Kazalka(vrstica, stolpec))</literal></quote>."

#. Tag: title
#: development.docbook:2951
#, no-c-format
msgid "Global Functions"
msgstr "Globalne funkcije"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:2952
#, no-c-format
msgid "This section lists all global functions."
msgstr "V tem razdelku so navedene vse globalne funkcije."

#. Tag: title
#: development.docbook:2956
#, no-c-format
msgid "Reading &amp; Including Files"
msgstr "Branje &amp; Vključno z datotekami"

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:2959
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"String read(<parameter>String <replaceable>file</replaceable></parameter>);"
msgstr ""
"Preberi niz(<parameter>Niz <replaceable>datoteka</replaceable></parameter>);"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:2960
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Will search the given <replaceable>file</replaceable> relative to the "
"<literal>katepart5/script/files</literal> directory and return its content "
"as a string."
msgstr ""
"Preiskal bo podano <replaceable>datoteko</replaceable> glede na imenik "
"<literal>katepart5/script/files</literal> in vrnil njeno vsebino kot niz."

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:2966
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"void require(<parameter>String <replaceable>file</replaceable></parameter>);"
msgstr ""
"prazna zahteva(<parameter>Niz <replaceable>datoteka</replaceable></"
"parameter>);"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:2967
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Will search the given <replaceable>file</replaceable> relative to the "
"<literal>katepart5/script/libraries</literal> directory and evaluate it. "
"<literal>require</literal> is internally guarded against multiple inclusions "
"of the same <replaceable>file</replaceable>."
msgstr ""
"Preiskal bo dano <replaceable>datoteko</replaceable> glede na imenik "
"<literal>katepart5/script/libraries</literal> in jo ovrednotil. "
"<literal>require</literal> je interno zaščiten pred večkratnimi vključitvami "
"iste <replaceable>datoteke</replaceable>."

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:2971
#, no-c-format
msgid "Since: &kde; 4.10"
msgstr "Od: &kde; 4.10"

#. Tag: title
#: development.docbook:2980
#, no-c-format
msgid "Debugging"
msgstr "Odpravljanje napak"

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:2983
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"void debug(<parameter>String <replaceable>text</replaceable></parameter>);"
msgstr ""
"prazno odpravljanje napak(<parameter>Niz <replaceable>besedilo</"
"replaceable></parameter>);"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:2984
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Prints <replaceable>text</replaceable> to <literal>stdout</literal> in the "
"console launching the application."
msgstr ""
"Natisne <replaceable>besedilo</replaceable> v <literal>stdout</literal> v "
"konzoli, ki zažene aplikacijo."

#. Tag: title
#: development.docbook:2993
#, no-c-format
msgid "Translation"
msgstr "Prevajanje"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:2995
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In order to support full localization, there are several functions to "
"translate strings in scripts, namely <literal>i18n</literal>, "
"<literal>i18nc</literal>, <literal>i18np</literal> and <literal>i18ncp</"
"literal>. These functions behave exactly like <ulink url=\"https://techbase."
"kde.org/Development/Tutorials/Localization/i18n\"> &kde;'s translation "
"functions</ulink>."
msgstr ""
"Za podporo popolne lokalizacije obstaja več funkcij za prevajanje nizov v "
"skriptih, in sicer <literal>i18n</literal>, <literal>i18nc</literal>, "
"<literal>i18np</literal> in <literal>i18ncp</literal>. Te funkcije se "
"obnašajo natanko tako kot <ulink url=\"https://techbase.kde.org/Development/"
"Tutorials/Localization/i18n\"> prevajalske funkcije &kde;</ulink>."

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3002
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The translation functions translate the wrapped strings through &kde;'s "
"translation system to the language used in the application. Strings in "
"scripts being developed in the official &kappname; sources are automatically "
"extracted and translatable. In other words, as a &kappname; developer you do "
"not have to bother with message extraction and translation. It should be "
"noted though, that the translation only works inside the &kde; "
"infrastructure, &ie;, new strings in 3rd-party scripts developed outside of "
"&kde; are not translated. Therefore, please consider contributing your "
"scripts to &kate; such that proper translation is possible."
msgstr ""
"Prevajalske funkcije prevedejo zavite nize prek prevajalskega sistema &kde; "
"v jezik, uporabljen v aplikaciji. Nizi v skriptih, ki se razvijajo v uradnem "
"&kappname; viri so samodejno ekstrahirani in prevedljivi. Z drugimi "
"besedami, kot &kappname; razvijalec se vam ni treba truditi z ekstrakcijo in "
"prevodom sporočil. Upoštevati pa je treba, da prevod deluje samo znotraj "
"&kde; infrastrukture, &ie;, novi nizi v skriptih tretjih oseb, razvitih "
"zunaj &kde; niso prevedeni. Zato vas prosimo, da svoje skripte prispevate k "
"&kate; tako, da je možen ustrezen prevod."

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:3014
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"void i18n(<parameter>String <replaceable>text</replaceable></parameter>, "
"<replaceable>arg1</replaceable>, ...);"
msgstr ""
"void i18n(<parameter>Niz <replaceable>besedilo</replaceable></parameter>, "
"<replaceable>arg1</replaceable>, ...);"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3015
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Translates <replaceable>text</replaceable> into the language used by the "
"application. The arguments <replaceable>arg1</replaceable>, ..., are "
"optional and used to replace the placeholders <literal>%1</literal>, "
"<literal>%2</literal>, &etc;"
msgstr ""
"Prevede <replaceable>besedilo</replaceable> v jezik, ki ga uporablja "
"aplikacija. Argumenti <replaceable>arg1</replaceable>, ... so neobvezni in "
"se uporabljajo za zamenjavo polj <literal>%1</literal>, <literal>%2</"
"literal>, &etc;"

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:3022
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"void i18nc(<parameter>String <replaceable>context</replaceable></parameter>, "
"<parameter>String <replaceable>text</replaceable></parameter>, "
"<replaceable>arg1</replaceable>, ...);"
msgstr ""
"void i18nc(<parameter>Niz <replaceable>context</replaceable></parameter>, "
"<parameter>Niz <replaceable>besedilo</replaceable></parameter>, "
"<replaceable>arg1</replaceable>, ...) ;"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3023
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Translates <replaceable>text</replaceable> into the language used by the "
"application. Additionally, the string <replaceable>context</replaceable> is "
"visible to translators so they can provide a better translation. The "
"arguments <replaceable>arg1</replaceable>, ..., are optional and used to "
"replace the placeholders <literal>%1</literal>, <literal>%2</literal>, &etc;"
msgstr ""
"Prevede <replaceable>besedilo</replaceable> v jezik, ki ga uporablja "
"aplikacija. Poleg tega je niz <replaceable>context</replaceable> viden "
"prevajalcem, tako da lahko zagotovijo boljši prevod. Argumenti "
"<replaceable>arg1</replaceable>, ... so neobvezni in se uporabljajo za "
"zamenjavo ograd <literal>%1</literal>, <literal>%2</literal> &etc;"

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:3032
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"void i18np(<parameter>String <replaceable>singular</replaceable></"
"parameter>, <parameter>String <replaceable>plural</replaceable></parameter>, "
"<parameter>int <replaceable>number</replaceable></parameter>, "
"<replaceable>arg1</replaceable>, ...);"
msgstr ""
"void i18np(<parameter>String <replaceable>singular</replaceable></"
"parameter>, <parameter>String <replaceable>plural</replaceable></parameter>, "
"<parameter>int <replaceable>number</replaceable></parameter>, "
"<replaceable>arg1</replaceable>, ...);"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3033
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Translates either <replaceable>singular</replaceable> or "
"<replaceable>plural</replaceable> into the language used by the application, "
"depending on the given <replaceable>number</replaceable>. The arguments "
"<replaceable>arg1</replaceable>, ..., are optional and used to replace the "
"placeholders <literal>%1</literal>, <literal>%2</literal>, &etc;"
msgstr ""
"Prevaja <replaceable>ednino</replaceable> ali <replaceable>množino</"
"replaceable> v jezik, ki ga uporablja aplikacija, odvisno od danega "
"<replaceable>števila</replaceable>. Argumenti <replaceable>arg1</"
"replaceable>, ... so neobvezni in se uporabljajo za zamenjavo polj <literal>"
"%1</literal>, <literal>%2</literal>, &etc;"

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:3042
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"void i18ncp(<parameter>String <replaceable>context</replaceable></"
"parameter>, <parameter>String <replaceable>singular</replaceable></"
"parameter>, <parameter>String <replaceable>plural</replaceable></parameter>, "
"<parameter>int <replaceable>number</replaceable></parameter>, "
"<replaceable>arg1</replaceable>, ...);"
msgstr ""
"void i18ncp(<parameter>Niz <replaceable>kontekst</replaceable></parameter>, "
"<parameter>Niz <replaceable>ednina</replaceable></parameter>, <parameter>Niz "
"<replaceable>množina</replaceable></parameter>, <parameter>int "
"<replaceable>število</replaceable></parameter>, <replaceable>arg1</"
"replaceable>, ...);"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3043
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Translates either <replaceable>singular</replaceable> or "
"<replaceable>plural</replaceable> into the language used by the application, "
"depending on the given <replaceable>number</replaceable>. Additionally, the "
"string <replaceable>context</replaceable> is visible to translators so they "
"can provide a better translation. The arguments <replaceable>arg1</"
"replaceable>, ..., are optional and used to replace the placeholders "
"<literal>%1</literal>, <literal>%2</literal>, &etc;"
msgstr ""
"Prevaja <replaceable>ednino</replaceable> ali <replaceable>množino</"
"replaceable> v jezik, ki ga uporablja aplikacija, odvisno od danega "
"<replaceable>števila</replaceable>. Poleg tega je niz <replaceable>context</"
"replaceable> viden prevajalcem, tako da lahko zagotovijo boljši prevod. "
"Argumenti <replaceable>arg1</replaceable>, ... so neobvezni in se "
"uporabljajo za zamenjavo ograd <literal>%1</literal>, <literal>%2</literal> "
"&etc;"

#. Tag: title
#: development.docbook:3057
#, no-c-format
msgid "The View API"
msgstr "Pogled API"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3058
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Whenever a script is being executed, there is a global variable "
"<quote><literal>view</literal></quote> representing the current active "
"editor view. The following is a list of all available View functions."
msgstr ""
"Kadarkoli se izvaja skript, obstaja globalna spremenljivka "
"<quote><literal>pogled</literal></quote>, ki predstavlja trenutni aktivni "
"pogled urejevalnika. Sledi seznam vseh razpoložljivih funkcij Pogled."

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:3065
#, no-c-format
msgid "<function>void view.copy()</function>"
msgstr "<function>void view.copy()</function>"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3067
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Copy the selection if there is one, otherwise the current line if the option "
"<userinput>[ ] Copy/Cut the current line if no selection</userinput> is set."
msgstr ""
"Kopirajte izbor, če obstaja, sicer trenutno vrstico, če je možnost "
"<userinput>[ ] Kopiraj/Izreži trenutno vrstico, če ni nastavljen noben "
"izbor</userinput>."

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3068 development.docbook:3077 development.docbook:3086
#, no-c-format
msgid "Since: &kde-frameworks; 5.79"
msgstr "Od: &kde-frameworks; 5.79"

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:3074
#, no-c-format
msgid "<function>void view.cut()</function>"
msgstr "<function>void view.cut()</function>"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3076
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Cut the selection if there is one, otherwise the current line if the option "
"<userinput>[ ] Copy/Cut the current line if no selection</userinput> is set."
msgstr ""
"Izrežite izbor, če obstaja, sicer trenutno vrstico, če je možnost "
"<userinput>[ ] Kopiraj/Izreži trenutno vrstico, če ni nastavljena nobena "
"izbira</userinput>."

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:3083
#, no-c-format
msgid "<function>void view.paste()</function>"
msgstr "<function>void view.paste()</function>"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3085
#, no-c-format
msgid "Paste the clipboard content."
msgstr "Prilepite vsebino odložišča."

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:3092
#, no-c-format
msgid "<function>Cursor view.cursorPosition()</function>"
msgstr "<function>Cursor view.cursorPosition()</function>"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3093
#, no-c-format
msgid "Returns the current cursor position in the view."
msgstr "Vrne trenutni položaj kazalke v pogledu."

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:3098
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"void view.setCursorPosition(<parameter>int <replaceable>line</replaceable></"
"parameter>, <parameter>int <replaceable>column</replaceable></parameter>);\n"
"void view.setCursorPosition(<parameter>Cursor <replaceable>cursor</"
"replaceable></parameter>);"
msgstr ""
"void view.setCursorPosition(<parameter>int <replaceable>line</replaceable></"
"parameter>, <parameter>int <replaceable>column</replaceable></parameter>);\n"
"void view.setCursorPosition(<parameter>Kazalka <replaceable>kazalka</"
"replaceable></parameter>);"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3099
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Set the current cursor position to either (line, column) or to the given "
"cursor."
msgstr ""
"Trenutni položaj kazalca nastavite na (vrstica, stolpec) ali na dani kazalec."

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:3106
#, no-c-format
msgid "Cursor view.virtualCursorPosition();"
msgstr "Pogled kazalca.virtualCursorPosition();"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3107
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Returns the virtual cursor position with each tab counting the corresponding "
"amount of spaces depending on the current tab width."
msgstr ""
"Vrne položaj navideznega kazalca z vsakim zavihkom, ki šteje ustrezno "
"količino presledkov glede na trenutno širino zavihka."

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:3114
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"void view.setVirtualCursorPosition(<parameter>int <replaceable>line</"
"replaceable></parameter>, <parameter>int <replaceable>column</replaceable></"
"parameter>);\n"
"void view.setVirtualCursorPosition(<parameter>Cursor <replaceable>cursor</"
"replaceable></parameter>);"
msgstr ""
"void view.setVirtualCursorPosition(<parameter>int <replaceable>line</"
"replaceable></parameter>, <parameter>int <replaceable>column</replaceable></"
"parameter>);\n"
"void view.setVirtualCursorPosition(<parameter>Kazalka <replaceable>kazalka</"
"replaceable></parameter>);"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3115
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Set the current virtual cursor position to (line, column) or to the given "
"cursor."
msgstr ""
"Nastavite trenutni položaj virtualne kazalke na (vrstica, stolpec) ali na "
"dano kazalko."

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:3122
#, no-c-format
msgid "String view.selectedText();"
msgstr "String view.selectedText();"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3123
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Returns the selected text. If no text is selected, the returned string is "
"empty."
msgstr "Vrne izbrano besedilo. Če besedilo ni izbrano, je vrnjeni niz prazen."

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:3130
#, no-c-format
msgid "bool view.hasSelection();"
msgstr "bool view.hasSelection();"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3131
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Returns <literal>true</literal>, if the view has selected text, otherwise "
"<literal>false</literal>."
msgstr ""
"Vrne <literal>true</literal>, če ima pogled izbrano besedilo, sicer "
"<literal>false</literal>."

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:3138
#, no-c-format
msgid "Range view.selection();"
msgstr "Range view.selection();"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3139
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Returns the selected text range. The returned range is invalid if there is "
"no selected text."
msgstr ""
"Vrne izbrani obseg besedila. Vrnjeni obseg je neveljaven, če ni izbranega "
"besedila."

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:3147
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"void view.setSelection(<parameter>Range <replaceable>range</replaceable></"
"parameter>);"
msgstr ""
"void view.setSelection(<parameter>Obseg <replaceable>obseg</replaceable></"
"parameter>);"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3148
#, no-c-format
msgid "Set the selected text to the given range."
msgstr "Nastavite izbrano besedilo na dani obseg."

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:3155
#, no-c-format
msgid "void view.removeSelectedText();"
msgstr "void view.removeSelectedText();"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3156
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Remove the selected text. If the view does not have any selected text, this "
"does nothing."
msgstr ""
"Odstrani izbrano besedilo. Če pogled nima izbranega besedila, to ne naredi "
"nič."

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:3164
#, no-c-format
msgid "void view.selectAll();"
msgstr "void view.selectAll();"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3165
#, no-c-format
msgid "Selects the entire text in the document."
msgstr "Izbere celotno besedilo v dokumentu."

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:3172
#, no-c-format
msgid "void view.clearSelection();"
msgstr "void view.clearSelection();"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3173
#, no-c-format
msgid "Clears the text selection without removing the text."
msgstr "Počisti izbor besedila brez odstranitve besedila."

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:3180
#, no-c-format
msgid "void view.setBlockSelection(bool on);"
msgstr "void view.setBlockSelection(bool on);"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3181
#, no-c-format
msgid "Set block selection mode on or off."
msgstr "Vklopi ali izklopi način izbire bloka."

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:3187
#, no-c-format
msgid "bool view.blockSelection();"
msgstr "bool view.blockSelection();"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3188
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Returns <literal>true</literal>, if block selection mode is on, otherwise "
"<literal>false</literal>."
msgstr ""
"Vrne <literal>true</literal>, če je vklopljen način izbire blokov, sicer "
"<literal>false</literal>."

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:3195
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"void view.align(<parameter>Range <replaceable>range</replaceable></"
"parameter>);"
msgstr ""
"void view.align(<parameter>Razpon <replaceable>obseg</replaceable></"
"parameter>);"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3196
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Properly re-indent lines within <replaceable>range</replaceable> according "
"to current indentation settings."
msgstr ""
"Ustrezno znova zamakni vrstice znotraj <replaceable>obsega</replaceable> "
"glede na trenutne nastavitve zamika."

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:3203
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"void view.alignOn(<parameter>Range <replaceable>range</replaceable></"
"parameter>, <parameter>String <replaceable>pattern</replaceable> = &quot;"
"&quot;</parameter>);"
msgstr ""
"void view.alignOn(<parameter>Obseg <replaceable>razpon</replaceable></"
"parameter>, <parameter>Niz <replaceable>vzorec</replaceable> = &quot;&quot;</"
"parameter>);"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3204
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Aligns lines in <replaceable>range</replaceable> on the column given by the "
"regular expression <replaceable>pattern</replaceable>. With an empty "
"<replaceable>pattern</replaceable> it will align on the first non-blank "
"character by default. If the pattern has a capture it will indent on the "
"captured match."
msgstr ""
"Poravna vrstice v <replaceable>obseg</replaceable> v stolpcu, podanem z "
"regularnim izrazom <replaceable>vzorec</replaceable>. S praznim "
"<replaceable>vzorcem</replaceable> se bo privzeto poravnal na prvi znak, ki "
"ni prazen. Če ima vzorec zajem, bo zajeto ujemanje zamaknjeno."

#. Tag: emphasis
#: development.docbook:3209
#, no-c-format
msgid "Examples:"
msgstr "Primeri:"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3210
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<literal>view.alignOn(document.documentRange(), '-');</literal> will insert "
"spaces before the first <literal>-</literal> of each lines to align them all "
"on the same column."
msgstr ""
"<literal>view.alignOn(document.documentRange(), '-');</literal> bo vstavil "
"presledke pred prvim <literal>-</literal> vsake vrstice, da jih vse poravna "
"v isti stolpec."

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3211
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<literal>view.alignOn(document.documentRange(), ':\\\\s+(.)');</literal> "
"will insert spaces before the first non-blank character that occurs after a "
"colon to align them all on the same column."
msgstr ""
"<literal>view.alignOn(document.documentRange(), ':\\\\s+(.)');</literal> bo "
"vstavil presledke pred prvi neprazen znak, ki se pojavi za dvopičjem, da jih "
"vse poravna na isto stolpec."

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:3216
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"object view.executeCommand(<parameter>String <replaceable>command</"
"replaceable></parameter>,\n"
"                           <parameter>String <replaceable>args</"
"replaceable></parameter>,\n"
"                           <parameter>Range <replaceable>range</"
"replaceable></parameter>);"
msgstr ""
"object view.executeCommand(<parameter>Niz <replaceable>command</"
"replaceable></parameter>,\n"
"                            <parameter>Niz <replaceable>args</replaceable></"
"parameter>,\n"
"                            <parameter>Obseg <replaceable>obseg</"
"replaceable></parameter>);"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3217
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Executes the <link linkend=\"advanced-editing-tools-commandline\">command "
"line command</link> <replaceable>command</replaceable> with the optional "
"arguments <replaceable>args</replaceable> and the optional "
"<replaceable>range</replaceable>. The returned <replaceable>object</"
"replaceable> has a boolean property <replaceable>object.ok</replaceable> "
"that indicates whether execution of the <replaceable>command</replaceable> "
"was successful. In case of an error, the string <replaceable>object.status</"
"replaceable> contains an error message."
msgstr ""
"Izvede <link linkend=\"advanced-editing-tools-commandline\">ukaz ukazne "
"vrstice</link> <replaceable>ukaz</replaceable> z izbirnimi argumenti "
"<replaceable>args</replaceable> in izbirnim obsegom <replaceable> </"
"replaceable>. Vrnjeni <replaceable>object</replaceable> ima logično lastnost "
"<replaceable>object.ok</replaceable>, ki kaže, ali je bila izvedba "
"<replaceable>ukaza</replaceable> uspešna. V primeru napake vsebuje niz "
"<replaceable>object.status</replaceable> sporočilo o napaki."

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3224 development.docbook:3946 development.docbook:3956
#: development.docbook:3966
#, no-c-format
msgid "Since: &kde-frameworks; 5.50"
msgstr "Od: &kde-frameworks; 5.50"

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:3229
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Range view.searchText(<parameter>Range <replaceable>range</replaceable></"
"parameter>,\n"
"                      <parameter>String <replaceable>pattern</replaceable></"
"parameter>,\n"
"                      <parameter>bool <replaceable>backwards</replaceable> = "
"false</parameter>);"
msgstr ""
"Range view.searchText(<parameter>Range <replaceable>range</replaceable></"
"parameter>,\n"
"                      <parameter>String <replaceable>pattern</replaceable></"
"parameter>,\n"
"                      <parameter>bool <replaceable>backwards</replaceable> = "
"false</parameter>);"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3230
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Search for the first occurrence of <replaceable>pattern</replaceable> in "
"<replaceable>range</replaceable> and returns the matched range. Search is "
"performed backwards if the optional boolean parameter "
"<replaceable>backwards</replaceable> is set to <literal>true</literal>."
msgstr ""
"Poišče prvo pojavitev <replaceable>vzorca</replaceable> v "
"<replaceable>range</replaceable> in vrne ujemajoči se obseg. Iskanje se "
"izvede nazaj, če je izbirni logični parameter <replaceable>nazaj</"
"replaceable> nastavljen na <literal>true</literal>."

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3234
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The returned range is invalid (see Range.isValid()) if <replaceable>pattern</"
"replaceable> is not found in <replaceable>range</replaceable>."
msgstr ""
"Vrnjeni obseg je neveljaven (glejte Range.isValid()), če "
"<replaceable>vzorec</replaceable> ni najden v <replaceable>range</"
"replaceable>."

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3237
#, no-c-format
msgid "Since: &kde-frameworks; 5.97"
msgstr "Od: &kde-frameworks; 5,97"

#. Tag: title
#: development.docbook:3246
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Document API"
msgstr "API za dokumente"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3247
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Whenever a script is being executed, there is a global variable "
"<quote><literal>document</literal></quote> representing the current active "
"document. The following is a list of all available Document functions."
msgstr ""
"Kadarkoli se izvaja skript, obstaja globalna spremenljivka "
"<quote><literal>dokument</literal></quote>, ki predstavlja trenutni aktivni "
"dokument. Sledi seznam vseh razpoložljivih funkcij dokumenta."

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:3255
#, no-c-format
msgid "String document.fileName();"
msgstr "String document.fileName();"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3256
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Returns the document's filename or an empty string for unsaved text buffers."
msgstr ""
"Vrne ime datoteke dokumenta ali prazen niz za neshranjene medpomnilnike "
"besedila."

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:3263
#, no-c-format
msgid "String document.url();"
msgstr "String document.url();"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3264
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Returns the document's full &URL; or an empty string for unsaved text "
"buffers."
msgstr ""
"Vrne celoten dokument &URL; ali prazen niz za neshranjene medpomnilnike "
"besedila."

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:3271
#, no-c-format
msgid "String document.mimeType();"
msgstr "String document.mimeType();"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3272
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Returns the document's &MIME; type or the &MIME; type <literal>application/"
"octet-stream</literal> if no appropriate &MIME; type could be found."
msgstr ""
"Vrne &MIME; tip ali &MIME; vnesite <literal>application/octet-stream</"
"literal>, če ni ustreznega &MIME; vrsto je mogoče najti."

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:3280
#, no-c-format
msgid "String document.encoding();"
msgstr "String document.encoding();"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3281
#, no-c-format
msgid "Returns the currently used encoding to save the file."
msgstr "Vrne trenutno uporabljeno kodiranje za shranjevanje datoteke."

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:3287
#, no-c-format
msgid "String document.highlightingMode();"
msgstr "String document.highlightingMode();"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3288
#, no-c-format
msgid "Returns the global highlighting mode used for the whole document."
msgstr "Vrne način globalnega označevanja, uporabljen za celoten dokument."

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:3294
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"String document.highlightingModeAt(<parameter>Cursor <replaceable>pos</"
"replaceable></parameter>);"
msgstr ""
"Niz document.highlightingModeAt(<parameter>Kazalka <replaceable>pos</"
"replaceable></parameter>);"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3295
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Returns the highlighting mode used at the given position in the document."
msgstr "Vrne način označevanja, uporabljen na danem mestu v dokumentu."

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:3301
#, no-c-format
msgid "Array document.embeddedHighlightingModes();"
msgstr "Array document.embeddedHighlightingModes();"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3302
#, no-c-format
msgid "Returns an array of highlighting modes embedded in this document."
msgstr "Vrne niz načinov označevanja, vdelanih v ta dokument."

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:3308
#, no-c-format
msgid "bool document.isModified();"
msgstr "bool document.isModified();"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3309
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Returns <literal>true</literal>, if the document has unsaved changes "
"(modified), otherwise <literal>false</literal>."
msgstr ""
"Vrne <literal>true</literal>, če ima dokument neshranjene spremembe "
"(spremenjene), sicer <literal>false</literal>."

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:3316
#, no-c-format
msgid "String document.text();"
msgstr "String document.text();"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3317
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Returns the entire content of the document in a single text string. Newlines "
"are marked with the newline character <quote><literal>\\n</literal></quote>."
msgstr ""
"Vrne celotno vsebino dokumenta v enem besedilnem nizu. Nove vrstice so "
"označene z znakom za novo vrstico <quote><literal>\\n</literal></quote>."

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:3325
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"String document.text(<parameter>int <replaceable>fromLine</replaceable></"
"parameter>, <parameter>int <replaceable>fromColumn</replaceable></"
"parameter>, <parameter>int <replaceable>toLine</replaceable></parameter>, "
"<parameter>int <replaceable>toColumn</replaceable></parameter>);\n"
"String document.text(<parameter>Cursor <replaceable>from</replaceable></"
"parameter>, <parameter>Cursor <replaceable>to</replaceable></parameter>);\n"
"String document.text(<parameter>Range <replaceable>range</replaceable></"
"parameter>);"
msgstr ""
"String document.text(<parameter>int <replaceable>fromLine</replaceable></"
"parameter>, <parameter>int <replaceable>fromColumn</replaceable></"
"parameter>, <parameter>int <replaceable>toLine</replaceable ></parameter>, "
"<parameter>int <replaceable>toColumn</replaceable></parameter>);\n"
"String document.text(<parameter>Kazalka <replaceable>od</replaceable></"
"parameter>, <parameter>kazalke <replaceable>do</replaceable></parameter>);\n"
"Niz document.text(<parameter>Obseg <replaceable>obseg</replaceable></"
"parameter>);"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3326
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Returns the text in the given range. It is recommended to use the cursor and "
"range based version for better readability of the source code."
msgstr ""
"Vrne besedilo v danem obsegu. Za boljšo berljivost izvorne kode je "
"priporočljiva uporaba različice, ki temelji na kazalcu in območju."

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:3334
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"String document.line(<parameter>int <replaceable>line</replaceable></"
"parameter>);"
msgstr ""
"Niz document.line(<parameter>int <replaceable>vrstica</replaceable></"
"parameter>);"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3335
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Returns the given text line as string. The string is empty if the requested "
"line is out of range."
msgstr ""
"Vrne dano besedilno vrstico kot niz. Niz je prazen, če je zahtevana vrstica "
"izven obsega."

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:3343
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"String document.wordAt(<parameter>int <replaceable>line</replaceable></"
"parameter>, <parameter>int <replaceable>column</replaceable></parameter>);\n"
"String document.wordAt(<parameter>Cursor <replaceable>cursor</replaceable></"
"parameter>);"
msgstr ""
"String document.wordAt(<parameter>int <replaceable>line</replaceable></"
"parameter>, <parameter>int <replaceable>column</replaceable></parameter>);\n"
"String document.wordAt(<parameter>Kazalka <replaceable>kazalka</"
"replaceable></parameter>);"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3344
#, no-c-format
msgid "Returns the word at the given cursor position."
msgstr "Vrne besedo na danem položaju kazalke."

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:3352
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Range document.wordRangeAt(<parameter>int <replaceable>line</replaceable></"
"parameter>, <parameter>int <replaceable>column</replaceable></parameter>);\n"
"Range document.wordRangeAt(<parameter>Cursor <replaceable>cursor</"
"replaceable></parameter>);"
msgstr ""
"Obseg document.wordRangeAt(<parameter>int <replaceable>line</replaceable></"
"parameter>, <parameter>int <replaceable>column</replaceable></parameter>);\n"
"Obseg document.wordRangeAt(<parameter>Kazalka <replaceable>kazalka</"
"replaceable></parameter>);"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3354
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Return the range of the word at the given cursor position. The returned "
"range is invalid (see Range.isValid()), if the text position is after the "
"end of a line. If there is no word at the given cursor, an empty range is "
"returned."
msgstr ""
"Vrne obseg besede na danem položaju kazalca. Vrnjeni obseg je neveljaven "
"(glejte Range.isValid()), če je položaj besedila za koncem vrstice. Če na "
"danem kazalcu ni besede, se vrne prazen obseg."

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:3367
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"String document.charAt(<parameter>int <replaceable>line</replaceable></"
"parameter>, <parameter>int <replaceable>column</replaceable></parameter>);\n"
"String document.charAt(<parameter>Cursor <replaceable>cursor</replaceable></"
"parameter>);"
msgstr ""
"String document.charAt(<parameter>int <replaceable>line</replaceable></"
"parameter>, <parameter>int <replaceable>column</replaceable></parameter>);\n"
"String document.charAt(<parameter>Kazalka <replaceable>kazalka</"
"replaceable></parameter>);"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3368
#, no-c-format
msgid "Returns the character at the given cursor position."
msgstr "Vrne znak na danem položaju kazalke."

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:3375
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"String document.firstChar(<parameter>int <replaceable>line</replaceable></"
"parameter>);"
msgstr ""
"String document.firstChar(<parameter>int <replaceable>vrstica</replaceable></"
"parameter>);"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3376
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Returns the first character in the given <replaceable>line</replaceable> "
"that is not a whitespace. The first character is at column 0. If the line is "
"empty or only contains whitespace characters, the returned string is empty."
msgstr ""
"Vrne prvi znak v dani <replaceable>vrstici</replaceable>, ki ni presledek. "
"Prvi znak je v stolpcu 0. Če je vrstica prazna ali vsebuje le presledke, je "
"vrnjeni niz prazen."

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:3386
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"String document.lastChar(<parameter>int <replaceable>line</replaceable></"
"parameter>);"
msgstr ""
"String document.lastChar(<parameter>int <replaceable>vrstica</replaceable></"
"parameter>);"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3387
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Returns the last character in the given <replaceable>line</replaceable> that "
"is not a whitespace. If the line is empty or only contains whitespace "
"characters, the returned string is empty."
msgstr ""
"Vrne zadnji znak v dani <replaceable>vrstici</replaceable>, ki ni presledek. "
"Če je vrstica prazna ali vsebuje samo presledke, je vrnjeni niz prazen."

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:3396
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"bool document.isSpace(<parameter>int <replaceable>line</replaceable></"
"parameter>, <parameter>int <replaceable>column</replaceable></parameter>);\n"
"bool document.isSpace(<parameter>Cursor <replaceable>cursor</replaceable></"
"parameter>);"
msgstr ""
"bool document.isSpace(<parameter>int <replaceable>vrstica</replaceable></"
"parameter>, <parameter>int <replaceable>stolpec</replaceable></parameter>);\n"
"bool document.isSpace(<parameter>Kazalka <replaceable>kazalka</replaceable></"
"parameter>);"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3397
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Returns <literal>true</literal>, if the character at the given cursor "
"position is a whitespace, otherwise <literal>false</literal>."
msgstr ""
"Vrne <literal>true</literal>, če je znak na danem položaju kazalke "
"presledek, drugače <literal>false</literal>."

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:3405
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"bool document.matchesAt(<parameter>int <replaceable>line</replaceable></"
"parameter>, <parameter>int <replaceable>column</replaceable></parameter>, "
"<parameter>String <replaceable>text</replaceable></parameter>);\n"
"bool document.matchesAt(<parameter>Cursor <replaceable>cursor</replaceable></"
"parameter>, <parameter>String <replaceable>text</replaceable></parameter>);"
msgstr ""
"bool document.matchesAt(<parameter>int <replaceable>vrstica</replaceable></"
"parameter>, <parameter>int <replaceable>coln</replaceable></parameter>, "
"<parameter>String <replaceable>besedilo</replaceable ></parameter>);\n"
"bool document.matchesAt(<parameter>Kazalka <replaceable>kazalka</"
"replaceable></parameter>, <parameter>String <replaceable>besedilo</"
"replaceable></parameter>);"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3406
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Returns <literal>true</literal>, if the given <replaceable>text</"
"replaceable> matches at the corresponding cursor position, otherwise "
"<literal>false</literal>."
msgstr ""
"Vrne <literal>true</literal>, če se podano <replaceable>besedilo</"
"replaceable> ujema na ustreznem položaju kazalca, sicer <literal>false</"
"literal>."

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:3414
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"bool document.startsWith(<parameter>int <replaceable>line</replaceable></"
"parameter>, <parameter>String <replaceable>text</replaceable></parameter>, "
"<parameter>bool <replaceable>skipWhiteSpaces</replaceable></parameter>);"
msgstr ""
"bool document.startsWith(<parameter>int <replaceable>vrstica</replaceable></"
"parameter>, <parameter>String <replaceable>besedilo</replaceable></"
"parameter>, <parameter>bool <replaceable>skipWhiteSpaces</replaceable ></"
"parameter>);"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3415
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Returns <literal>true</literal>, if the line starts with <replaceable>text</"
"replaceable>, otherwise <literal>false</literal>. The argument "
"<replaceable>skipWhiteSpaces</replaceable> controls whether leading "
"whitespaces are ignored."
msgstr ""
"Vrne <literal>true</literal>, če se vrstica začne z <replaceable>besedilo</"
"replaceable>, sicer <literal>false</literal>. Argument "
"<replaceable>skipWhiteSpaces</replaceable> nadzira, ali se vodilni presledki "
"prezrejo."

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:3423
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"bool document.endsWith(<parameter>int <replaceable>line</replaceable></"
"parameter>, <parameter>String <replaceable>text</replaceable></parameter>, "
"<parameter>bool <replaceable>skipWhiteSpaces</replaceable></parameter>);"
msgstr ""
"bool document.endsWith(<parameter>int <replaceable>vrstica</replaceable></"
"parameter>, <parameter>String <replaceable>besedilo</replaceable></"
"parameter>, <parameter>bool <replaceable>skipWhiteSpaces</replaceable ></"
"parameter>);"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3424
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Returns <literal>true</literal>, if the line ends with <replaceable>text</"
"replaceable>, otherwise <literal>false</literal>. The argument "
"<replaceable>skipWhiteSpaces</replaceable> controls whether trailing "
"whitespaces are ignored."
msgstr ""
"Vrne <literal>true</literal>, če se vrstica konča z <replaceable>text</"
"replaceable>, sicer <literal>false</literal>. Argument "
"<replaceable>skipWhiteSpaces</replaceable> nadzira, ali se končni presledki "
"prezrejo."

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:3432
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"bool document.setText(<parameter>String <replaceable>text</replaceable></"
"parameter>);"
msgstr ""
"bool document.setText(<parameter>Niz <replaceable>besedilo</replaceable></"
"parameter>);"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3433
#, no-c-format
msgid "Sets the entire document text."
msgstr "Nastavi celotno besedilo dokumenta."

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:3440
#, no-c-format
msgid "bool document.clear();"
msgstr "bool document.clear();"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3441
#, no-c-format
msgid "Removes the entire text in the document."
msgstr "Odstrani celotno besedilo v dokumentu."

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:3448
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"bool document.truncate(<parameter>int <replaceable>line</replaceable></"
"parameter>, <parameter>int <replaceable>column</replaceable></parameter>);\n"
"bool document.truncate(<parameter>Cursor <replaceable>cursor</replaceable></"
"parameter>);"
msgstr ""
"bool document.truncate(<parameter>int <replaceable>vrstica</replaceable></"
"parameter>, <parameter>int <replaceable>stolpec</replaceable></parameter>);\n"
"bool document.truncate(<parameter>Kazalka <replaceable>kazalka</"
"replaceable></parameter>);"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3449
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Truncate the given line at the given column or cursor position. Returns "
"<literal>true</literal> on success, or <literal>false</literal> if the given "
"line is not part of the document range."
msgstr ""
"Odreži dano vrstico na danem stolpcu ali položaju kazalca. Vrne "
"<literal>true</literal> ob uspehu ali <literal>false</literal>, če podana "
"vrstica ni del obsega dokumenta."

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:3457
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"bool document.insertText(<parameter>int <replaceable>line</replaceable></"
"parameter>, <parameter>int <replaceable>column</replaceable></parameter>, "
"<parameter>String <replaceable>text</replaceable></parameter>);\n"
"bool document.insertText(<parameter>Cursor <replaceable>cursor</"
"replaceable></parameter>, <parameter>String <replaceable>text</replaceable></"
"parameter>);"
msgstr ""
"bool document.insertText(<parameter>int <replaceable>vrstica</replaceable></"
"parameter>, <parameter>int <replaceable>coln</replaceable></parameter>, "
"<parameter>String <replaceable>besedilo</replaceable ></parameter>);\n"
"bool document.insertText(<parameter>Kazalka <replaceable>kazalka</"
"replaceable></parameter>, <parameter>Niz <replaceable>besedilo</"
"replaceable></parameter>);"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3458
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Inserts the <replaceable>text</replaceable> at the given cursor position. "
"Returns <literal>true</literal> on success, or <literal>false</literal>, if "
"the document is in read-only mode."
msgstr ""
"Vstavi <replaceable>besedilo</replaceable> na dani položaj kazalke. Vrne "
"<literal>true</literal> ob uspehu ali <literal>false</literal>, če je "
"dokument v načinu samo za branje."

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:3466
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"bool document.removeText(<parameter>int <replaceable>fromLine</replaceable></"
"parameter>, <parameter>int <replaceable>fromColumn</replaceable></"
"parameter>, <parameter>int <replaceable>toLine</replaceable></parameter>, "
"<parameter>int <replaceable>toColumn</replaceable></parameter>);\n"
"bool document.removeText(<parameter>Cursor <replaceable>from</replaceable></"
"parameter>, <parameter>Cursor <replaceable>to</replaceable></parameter>);\n"
"bool document.removeText(<parameter>Range <replaceable>range</replaceable></"
"parameter>);"
msgstr ""
"bool document.removeText(<parameter>int <replaceable>fromLine</replaceable></"
"parameter>, <parameter>int <replaceable>fromColumn</replaceable></"
"parameter>, <parameter>int <replaceable>toLine</replaceable ></parameter>, "
"<parameter>int <replaceable>toColumn</replaceable></parameter>);\n"
"bool document.removeText(<parameter>Kazalka <replaceable>od</replaceable></"
"parameter>, <parameter>Kazalka <replaceable>do</replaceable></parameter>);\n"
"bool document.removeText(<parameter>Obseg <replaceable>razpon</replaceable></"
"parameter>);"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3467
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Removes the text in the given range. Returns <literal>true</literal> on "
"success, or <literal>false</literal>, if the document is in read-only mode."
msgstr ""
"Odstrani besedilo v danem obsegu. Vrne <literal>true</literal> ob uspehu ali "
"<literal>false</literal>, če je dokument v načinu samo za branje."

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:3475
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"bool document.insertLine(<parameter>int <replaceable>line</replaceable></"
"parameter>, <parameter>String <replaceable>text</replaceable></parameter>);"
msgstr ""
"bool document.insertLine(<parameter>int <replaceable>line</replaceable></"
"parameter>, <parameter>Niz <replaceable>besedilo</replaceable></parameter>);"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3476
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Inserts text in the given line. Returns <literal>true</literal> on success, "
"or <literal>false</literal>, if the document is in read-only mode or the "
"line is not in the document range."
msgstr ""
"Vstavi besedilo v dano vrstico. Vrne <literal>true</literal> ob uspehu ali "
"<literal>false</literal>, če je dokument v načinu samo za branje ali če "
"vrstica ni v obsegu dokumenta."

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:3484
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"bool document.removeLine(<parameter>int <replaceable>line</replaceable></"
"parameter>);"
msgstr ""
"bool document.removeLine(<parameter>int <replaceable>vrstica</replaceable></"
"parameter>);"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3485
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Removes the given text line. Returns <literal>true</literal> on success, or "
"<literal>false</literal>, if the document is in read-only mode or the line "
"is not in the document range."
msgstr ""
"Odstrani dano besedilno vrstico. Vrne <literal>true</literal> ob uspehu ali "
"<literal>false</literal>, če je dokument v načinu samo za branje ali če "
"vrstica ni v obsegu dokumenta."

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:3493
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"bool document.wrapLine(<parameter>int <replaceable>line</replaceable></"
"parameter>, <parameter>int <replaceable>column</replaceable></parameter>);\n"
"bool document.wrapLine(<parameter>Cursor <replaceable>cursor</replaceable></"
"parameter>);"
msgstr ""
"bool document.wrapLine(<parameter>int <replaceable>vrstica</replaceable></"
"parameter>, <parameter>int <replaceable>stolpec</replaceable></parameter>);\n"
"bool document.wrapLine(<parameter>Kazalka <replaceable>kazalka</"
"replaceable></parameter>);"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3494
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Wraps the line at the given cursor position. Returns <literal>true</literal> "
"on success, otherwise <literal>false</literal>, &eg; if line &lt; 0."
msgstr ""
"Prelomi vrstico na danem položaju kazalca. Vrne <literal>true</literal> ob "
"uspehu, sicer <literal>false</literal>, &eg; če vrstica &lt; 0."

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:3506
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"void document.joinLines(<parameter>int <replaceable>startLine</replaceable></"
"parameter>, <parameter>int <replaceable>endLine</replaceable></parameter>);"
msgstr ""
"void document.joinLines(<parameter>int <replaceable>začetekVrstice</"
"replaceable></parameter>, <parameter>int <replaceable>konecVrstice</"
"replaceable></parameter>);"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3507
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Joins the lines from <replaceable>startLine</replaceable> to "
"<replaceable>endLine</replaceable>. Two succeeding text lines are always "
"separated with a single space."
msgstr ""
"Združuje vrstice od <replaceable>zacetekVrstice</replaceable> do "
"<replaceable>konecVrstice</replaceable>. Dve vrstici besedila, ki si "
"sledita, sta vedno ločeni z enim presledkom."

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:3515
#, no-c-format
msgid "int document.lines();"
msgstr "int document.lines();"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3516
#, no-c-format
msgid "Returns the number of lines in the document."
msgstr "Vrne število vrstic v dokumentu."

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:3523
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"bool document.isLineModified(<parameter>int <replaceable>line</replaceable></"
"parameter>);"
msgstr ""
"bool document.isLineModified(<parameter>int <replaceable>vrstica</"
"replaceable></parameter>);"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3524
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Returns <literal>true</literal>, if <replaceable>line</replaceable> "
"currently contains unsaved data."
msgstr ""
"Vrne <literal>true</literal>, če <replaceable>vrstica</replaceable> trenutno "
"vsebuje neshranjene podatke."

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3527 development.docbook:3539 development.docbook:3550
#: development.docbook:3562 development.docbook:3736
#, no-c-format
msgid "Since: &kde; 5.0"
msgstr "Od: &kde; 5.0"

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:3534
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"bool document.isLineSaved(<parameter>int <replaceable>line</replaceable></"
"parameter>);"
msgstr ""
"bool document.isLineSaved(<parameter>int <replaceable>vrstica</replaceable></"
"parameter>);"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3535
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Returns <literal>true</literal>, if <replaceable>line</replaceable> was "
"changed, but the document was saved. Hence, the line currently does not "
"contain any unsaved data."
msgstr ""
"Vrne <literal>true</literal>, če je bila <replaceable>vrstica</replaceable> "
"spremenjena, vendar je bil dokument shranjen. Zato vrstica trenutno ne "
"vsebuje neshranjenih podatkov."

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:3546
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"bool document.isLineTouched(<parameter>int <replaceable>line</replaceable></"
"parameter>);"
msgstr ""
"bool document.isLineTouched(<parameter>int <replaceable>vrstica</"
"replaceable></parameter>);"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3547
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Returns <literal>true</literal>, if <replaceable>line</replaceable> "
"currently contains unsaved data or was changed before."
msgstr ""
"Vrne <literal>true</literal>, če <replaceable>vrstica</replaceable> trenutno "
"vsebuje neshranjene podatke ali je bil že spremenjen."

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:3557
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"bool document.findTouchedLine(<parameter>int <replaceable>startLine</"
"replaceable></parameter>, <parameter>bool <replaceable>down</replaceable></"
"parameter>);"
msgstr ""
"bool document.findTouchedLine(<parameter>int <replaceable>začetekVrstice</"
"replaceable></parameter>, <parameter>bool <replaceable>dol</replaceable></"
"parameter>);"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3558
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Search for the next touched line starting at <replaceable>line</"
"replaceable>. The search is performed either upwards or downwards depending "
"on the search direction specified in <replaceable>down</replaceable>."
msgstr ""
"Poiščite naslednjo dotaknjeno vrstico, ki se začne pri <replaceable>vrstica</"
"replaceable>. Iskanje se izvaja navzgor ali navzdol, odvisno od smeri "
"iskanja, določene v <replaceable>dol</replaceable>."

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:3569
#, no-c-format
msgid "int document.length();"
msgstr "int document.length();"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3570
#, no-c-format
msgid "Returns the number of characters in the document."
msgstr "Vrne število znakov v dokumentu."

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:3577
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"int document.lineLength(<parameter>int <replaceable>line</replaceable></"
"parameter>);"
msgstr ""
"int document.lineLength(<parameter>int <replaceable>vrstica</replaceable></"
"parameter>);"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3578
#, no-c-format
msgid "Returns the <replaceable>line</replaceable>'s length."
msgstr "Vrne dolžino <replaceable>vrstice</replaceable>."

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:3585
#, no-c-format
msgid "void document.editBegin();"
msgstr "ničen dokument.editBegin();"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3586
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Starts an edit group for undo/redo grouping. Make sure to always call "
"<function>editEnd()</function> as often as you call <function>editBegin()</"
"function>. Calling <function>editBegin()</function> internally uses a "
"reference counter, &ie;, this call can be nested."
msgstr ""
"Zažene skupino za urejanje za razveljavitev/uveljavitev združevanja. "
"Prepričajte se, da vedno kličete <function>editEnd()</function> tako "
"pogosto, kot kličete <function>editBegin()</function>. Klicanje "
"<function>editBegin()</function> interno uporablja referenčni števec, &ie; "
"ta klic je lahko ugnezden."

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:3596
#, no-c-format
msgid "void document.editEnd();"
msgstr "void document.editEnd();"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3597
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Ends an edit group. The last call of <function>editEnd()</function> (&ie; "
"the one for the first call of <function>editBegin()</function>) finishes the "
"edit step."
msgstr ""
"Konča skupino za urejanje. Zadnji klic <function>editEnd()</function> (&ie; "
"tisti za prvi klic <function>editBegin()</function>) zaključi korak urejanja."

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:3606
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"int document.firstColumn(<parameter>int <replaceable>line</replaceable></"
"parameter>);"
msgstr ""
"int document.firstColumn(<parameter>int <replaceable>vrstica</replaceable></"
"parameter>);"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3607
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Returns the first non-whitespace column in the given <replaceable>line</"
"replaceable>. If there are only whitespaces in the line, the return value is "
"<literal>-1</literal>."
msgstr ""
"Vrne prvi stolpec brez presledkov v dani <replaceable>vrstici</replaceable>. "
"Če so v vrstici samo presledki, je vrnjena vrednost <literal>-1</literal>."

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:3615
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"int document.lastColumn(<parameter>int <replaceable>line</replaceable></"
"parameter>);"
msgstr ""
"int document.lastColumn(<parameter>int <replaceable>vrstica</replaceable></"
"parameter>);"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3616
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Returns the last non-whitespace column in the given <replaceable>line</"
"replaceable>. If there are only whitespaces in the line, the return value is "
"<literal>-1</literal>."
msgstr ""
"Vrne zadnji stolpec brez presledkov v dani <replaceable>vrstici</"
"replaceable>. Če so v vrstici samo presledki, je vrnjena vrednost "
"<literal>-1</literal>."

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:3624
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"int document.prevNonSpaceColumn(<parameter>int <replaceable>line</"
"replaceable></parameter>, <parameter>int <replaceable>column</replaceable></"
"parameter>);\n"
"int document.prevNonSpaceColumn(<parameter>Cursor <replaceable>cursor</"
"replaceable></parameter>);"
msgstr ""
"int document.prevNonSpaceColumn(<parameter>int <replaceable>vrstica</"
"replaceable></parameter>, <parameter>int <replaceable>stolpec</replaceable></"
"parameter>);\n"
"int document.prevNonSpaceColumn(<parameter>Kazalka <replaceable>kazalka</"
"replaceable></parameter>);"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3625
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Returns the column with a non-whitespace character starting at the given "
"cursor position and searching backwards."
msgstr ""
"Vrne stolpec z znakom brez presledka, ki se začne na danem položaju kazalke "
"in išče nazaj."

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:3633
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"int document.nextNonSpaceColumn(<parameter>int <replaceable>line</"
"replaceable></parameter>, <parameter>int <replaceable>column</replaceable></"
"parameter>);\n"
"int document.nextNonSpaceColumn(<parameter>Cursor <replaceable>cursor</"
"replaceable></parameter>);"
msgstr ""
"int document.nextNonSpaceColumn(<parameter>int <replaceable>vrstica</"
"replaceable></parameter>, <parameter>int <replaceable>stolpec</replaceable></"
"parameter>);\n"
"int document.nextNonSpaceColumn(<parameter>Kazalka <replaceable>kazalka</"
"replaceable></parameter>);"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3634
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Returns the column with a non-whitespace character starting at the given "
"cursor position and searching forwards."
msgstr ""
"Vrne stolpec z znakom brez presledka, ki se začne na danem položaju kazalke "
"in išče naprej."

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:3642
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"int document.prevNonEmptyLine(<parameter>int <replaceable>line</"
"replaceable></parameter>);"
msgstr ""
"int document.prevNonEmptyLine(<parameter>int <replaceable>vrstica</"
"replaceable></parameter>);"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3643
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Returns the next non-empty line containing non-whitespace characters "
"searching backwards."
msgstr ""
"Vrne naslednjo neprazno vrstico, ki vsebuje znake, ki niso presledki, pri "
"iskanju nazaj."

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:3651
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"int document.nextNonEmptyLine(<parameter>int <replaceable>line</"
"replaceable></parameter>);"
msgstr ""
"int document.nextNonEmptyLine(<parameter>int <replaceable>vrstica</"
"replaceable></parameter>);"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3652
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Returns the next non-empty line containing non-whitespace characters "
"searching forwards."
msgstr ""
"Vrne naslednjo neprazno vrstico, ki vsebuje znake, ki niso presledki, pri "
"iskanju naprej."

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:3660
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"bool document.isInWord(<parameter>String <replaceable>character</"
"replaceable></parameter>, <parameter>int <replaceable>attribute</"
"replaceable></parameter>);"
msgstr ""
"bool document.isInWord(<parameter>Niz <replaceable>znak</replaceable></"
"parameter>, <parameter>int <replaceable>atribut</replaceable></parameter>);"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3661
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Returns <literal>true</literal>, if the given <replaceable>character</"
"replaceable> with the given <replaceable>attribute</replaceable> can be part "
"of a word, otherwise <literal>false</literal>."
msgstr ""
"Vrne <literal>true</literal>, če je dani <replaceable>znak</replaceable> z "
"danim <replaceable>atributom</replaceable> lahko del besede, sicer "
"<literal>false</literal>."

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:3670
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"bool document.canBreakAt(<parameter>String <replaceable>character</"
"replaceable></parameter>, <parameter>int <replaceable>attribute</"
"replaceable></parameter>);"
msgstr ""
"bool document.canBreakAt(<parameter>Niz <replaceable>znak</replaceable></"
"parameter>, <parameter>int <replaceable>atribut</replaceable></parameter>);"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3671
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Returns <literal>true</literal>, if the given <replaceable>character</"
"replaceable> with the given <replaceable>attribute</replaceable> is suited "
"to wrap a line, otherwise <literal>false</literal>."
msgstr ""
"Vrne <literal>true</literal>, če je dani <replaceable>znak</replaceable> z "
"danim <replaceable>atributom</replaceable> primeren za prelom vrstice, sicer "
"<literal>false</literal>."

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:3680
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"bool document.canComment(<parameter>int <replaceable>startAttribute</"
"replaceable></parameter>, <parameter>int <replaceable>endAttribute</"
"replaceable></parameter>);"
msgstr ""
"bool document.canComment(<parameter>int <replaceable>startAttribute</"
"replaceable></parameter>, <parameter>int <replaceable>endAttribute</"
"replaceable></parameter>);"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3681
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Returns <literal>true</literal>, if a range starting and ending with the "
"given attributes is suited to be commented out, otherwise <literal>false</"
"literal>."
msgstr ""
"Vrne <literal>true</literal>, če je obseg, ki se začne in konča z danimi "
"atributi, primeren za komentiranje, sicer <literal>false</literal>."

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:3689
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"String document.commentMarker(<parameter>int <replaceable>attribute</"
"replaceable></parameter>);"
msgstr ""
"String document.commentMarker(<parameter>int <replaceable>atribut</"
"replaceable></parameter>);"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3690
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Returns the comment marker for single line comments for a given "
"<replaceable>attribute</replaceable>."
msgstr ""
"Vrne oznako komentarja za enovrstične komentarje za dani "
"<replaceable>atribut</replaceable>."

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:3697
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"String document.commentStart(<parameter>int <replaceable>attribute</"
"replaceable></parameter>);"
msgstr ""
"String document.commentStart(<parameter>int <replaceable>atribut</"
"replaceable></parameter>);"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3698
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Returns the comment marker for the start of multi-line comments for a given "
"<replaceable>attribute</replaceable>."
msgstr ""
"Vrne oznako komentarja za začetek večvrstičnih komentarjev za dani "
"<replaceable>atribut</replaceable>."

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:3706
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"String document.commentEnd(<parameter>int <replaceable>attribute</"
"replaceable></parameter>);"
msgstr ""
"String document.commentEnd(<parameter>int <replaceable>atribut</"
"replaceable></parameter>);"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3707
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Returns the comment marker for the end of multi-line comments for a given "
"<replaceable>attribute</replaceable>."
msgstr ""
"Vrne oznako komentarja za konec večvrstičnih komentarjev za dani "
"<replaceable>atribut</replaceable>."

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:3715
#, no-c-format
msgid "Range document.documentRange();"
msgstr "Obseg document.documentRange();"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3716
#, no-c-format
msgid "Returns a range that encompasses the whole document."
msgstr "Vrne obseg, ki zajema celoten dokument."

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:3723
#, no-c-format
msgid "Cursor documentEnd();"
msgstr "Cursor documentEnd();"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3724
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Returns a cursor positioned at the last column of the last line in the "
"document."
msgstr "Vrne kazalko v zadnjem stolpcu zadnje vrstice v dokumentu."

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:3731
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"bool isValidTextPosition(<parameter>int <replaceable>line</replaceable></"
"parameter>, <parameter>int <replaceable>column</replaceable></parameter>);\n"
"bool isValidTextPosition(<parameter>Cursor <replaceable>cursor</"
"replaceable></parameter>);"
msgstr ""
"bool isValidTextPosition(<parameter>int <replaceable>vrstica</replaceable></"
"parameter>, <parameter>int <replaceable>stolpec</replaceable></parameter>);\n"
"bool isValidTextPosition(<parameter>Kazalka <replaceable>kazalka</"
"replaceable></parameter>);"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3732
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Returns <literal>true</literal>, if the given cursor position is positioned "
"at a valid text position. A text position is valid only if it locate at the "
"start, in the middle, or the end of a valid line. Further, a text position "
"is invalid if it is located in a Unicode surrogate."
msgstr ""
"Vrne <literal>true</literal>, če je dani položaj kazalca na veljavnem "
"položaju besedila. Položaj besedila je veljaven le, če se nahaja na začetku, "
"sredini ali koncu veljavne vrstice. Poleg tega položaj besedila ni veljaven, "
"če se nahaja v nadomestku Unicode."

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:3743
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"int document.attribute(<parameter>int <replaceable>line</replaceable></"
"parameter>, <parameter>int <replaceable>column</replaceable></parameter>);\n"
"int document.attribute(<parameter>Cursor <replaceable>cursor</replaceable></"
"parameter>);"
msgstr ""
"int document.attribute(<parameter>int <replaceable>vrstica</replaceable></"
"parameter>, <parameter>int <replaceable>stolpec</replaceable></parameter>);\n"
"int document.attribute(<parameter>Kazalka <replaceable>kazalka</"
"replaceable></parameter>);"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3744
#, no-c-format
msgid "Returns the attribute at the given cursor position."
msgstr "Vrne atribut na danem položaju kazalca."

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:3751
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"bool document.isAttribute(<parameter>int <replaceable>line</replaceable></"
"parameter>, <parameter>int <replaceable>column</replaceable></parameter>, "
"<parameter>int <replaceable>attribute</replaceable></parameter>);\n"
"bool document.isAttribute(<parameter>Cursor <replaceable>cursor</"
"replaceable></parameter>, <parameter>int <replaceable>attribute</"
"replaceable></parameter>);"
msgstr ""
"bool document.isAttribute(<parameter>int <replaceable>vrstica</replaceable></"
"parameter>, <parameter>int <replaceable>stolpec</replaceable></parameter>, "
"<parameter>int <replaceable>atribut</replaceable ></parameter>);\n"
"bool document.isAttribute(<parameter>Kazalka <replaceable>kazalka</"
"replaceable></parameter>, <parameter>int <replaceable>atribut</replaceable></"
"parameter>);"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3752
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Returns <literal>true</literal>, if the attribute at the given cursor "
"position equals <replaceable>attribute</replaceable>, otherwise "
"<literal>false</literal>."
msgstr ""
"Vrne <literal>true</literal>, če je atribut na danem položaju kazalca enak "
"<replaceable>attribute</replaceable>, sicer <literal>false</literal>."

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:3760
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"String document.attributeName(<parameter>int <replaceable>line</"
"replaceable></parameter>, <parameter>int <replaceable>column</replaceable></"
"parameter>);\n"
"String document.attributeName(<parameter>Cursor <replaceable>cursor</"
"replaceable></parameter>);"
msgstr ""
"String document.attributeName(<parameter>int <replaceable>vrstica</"
"replaceable></parameter>, <parameter>int <replaceable>stolpec</replaceable></"
"parameter>);\n"
"String document.attributeName(<parameter>Kazalka <replaceable>kazalka</"
"replaceable></parameter>);"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3761
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Returns the attribute name as human readable text. This is equal to the "
"<literal>itemData</literal> name in the syntax highlighting files."
msgstr ""
"Vrne ime atributa kot človeku berljivo besedilo. To je enako imenu "
"<literal>podatkiPredmeta</literal> v datotekah za označevanje sintakse."

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:3769
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"bool document.isAttributeName(<parameter>int <replaceable>line</"
"replaceable></parameter>, <parameter>int <replaceable>column</replaceable></"
"parameter>, <parameter>String <replaceable>name</replaceable></parameter>);\n"
"bool document.isAttributeName(<parameter>Cursor <replaceable>cursor</"
"replaceable></parameter>, <parameter>String <replaceable>name</replaceable></"
"parameter>);"
msgstr ""
"bool document.isAttributeName(<parameter>int <replaceable>vrstica</"
"replaceable></parameter>, <parameter>int <replaceable>stolpec</replaceable></"
"parameter>, <parameter>String <replaceable>ime</replaceable ></parameter>);\n"
"bool document.isAttributeName(<parameter>Kazalka <replaceable>kazalka</"
"replaceable></parameter>, <parameter>String <replaceable>name</replaceable></"
"parameter>);"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3770
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Returns <literal>true</literal>, if the attribute name at a certain cursor "
"position matches the given <replaceable>name</replaceable>, otherwise "
"<literal>false</literal>."
msgstr ""
"Vrne <literal>true</literal>, če se ime atributa na določenem položaju "
"kazalca ujema z danim <replaceable>ime</replaceable>, sicer <literal>false</"
"literal>."

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:3778
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"String document.variable(<parameter>String <replaceable>key</replaceable></"
"parameter>);"
msgstr ""
"String document.variable(<parameter>String <replaceable>key</replaceable></"
"parameter>);"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3779
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Returns the value of the requested document variable <replaceable>key</"
"replaceable>. If the document variable does not exist, the return value is "
"an empty string."
msgstr ""
"Vrne vrednost zahtevane spremenljivke dokumenta <replaceable>ključ</"
"replaceable>. Če spremenljivka dokumenta ne obstaja, je vrnjena vrednost "
"prazen niz."

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:3787
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"void document.setVariable(<parameter>String <replaceable>key</replaceable></"
"parameter>, <parameter>String <replaceable>value</replaceable></parameter>);"
msgstr ""
"void document.setVariable(<parameter>String <replaceable>ključ</"
"replaceable></parameter>, <parameter>String <replaceable>vrednost</"
"replaceable></parameter>);"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3788
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Set the value of the requested document variable <replaceable>key</"
"replaceable>."
msgstr ""
"Nastavite vrednost zahtevane spremenljivke dokumenta <replaceable>key</"
"replaceable>."

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3791
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"See also: <link linkend=\"config-variables\">Kate document variables</link>"
msgstr ""
"Glejte tudi: <link linkend=\"config-variables\">Spremenljivke dokumenta "
"Kate</link>"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3794
#, no-c-format
msgid "Since: &kde; 4.8"
msgstr "Od: &kde; 4.8"

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:3801
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"int document.firstVirtualColumn(<parameter>int <replaceable>line</"
"replaceable></parameter>);"
msgstr ""
"int document.firstVirtualColumn(<parameter>int <replaceable>vrstica</"
"replaceable></parameter>);"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3802
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Returns the virtual column of the first non-whitespace character in the "
"given line or <literal>-1</literal>, if the line is empty or contains only "
"whitespace characters."
msgstr ""
"Vrne navidezni stolpec prvega znaka, ki ni presledek, v dani vrstici ali "
"<literal>-1</literal>, če je vrstica prazna ali vsebuje samo presledke."

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:3810
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"int document.lastVirtualColumn(<parameter>int <replaceable>line</"
"replaceable></parameter>);"
msgstr ""
"int document.lastVirtualColumn(<parameter>int <replaceable>vrstica</"
"replaceable></parameter>);"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3811
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Returns the virtual column of the last non-whitespace character in the given "
"line or <literal>-1</literal>, if the line is empty or contains only "
"whitespace characters."
msgstr ""
"Vrne navidezni stolpec zadnjega znaka, ki ni presledek, v dani vrstici ali "
"<literal>-1</literal>, če je vrstica prazna ali vsebuje samo presledke."

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:3819
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"int document.toVirtualColumn(<parameter>int <replaceable>line</replaceable></"
"parameter>, <parameter>int <replaceable>column</replaceable></parameter>);\n"
"int document.toVirtualColumn(<parameter>Cursor <replaceable>cursor</"
"replaceable></parameter>);\n"
"Cursor document.toVirtualCursor(<parameter>Cursor <replaceable>cursor</"
"replaceable></parameter>);"
msgstr ""
"int document.toVirtualColumn(<parameter>int <replaceable>vrstica</"
"replaceable></parameter>, <parameter>int <replaceable>stolpec</replaceable></"
"parameter>);\n"
"int document.toVirtualColumn(<parameter>Kazalka <replaceable>kazalka</"
"replaceable></parameter>);\n"
"Cursor document.toVirtualCursor(<parameter>Kazalka <replaceable>kazalka</"
"replaceable></parameter>);"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3820
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Converts the given <quote>real</quote> cursor position to a virtual cursor "
"position, either returning an int or a Cursor object."
msgstr ""
"Pretvori dani <quote>pravi</quote> položaj kazalke v položaj navidezne "
"kazalke, bodisi vrne int ali objekt kazalke."

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:3828
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"int document.fromVirtualColumn(<parameter>int <replaceable>line</"
"replaceable></parameter>, <parameter>int <replaceable>virtualColumn</"
"replaceable></parameter>);\n"
"int document.fromVirtualColumn(<parameter>Cursor <replaceable>virtualCursor</"
"replaceable></parameter>);\n"
"Cursor document.fromVirtualCursor(<parameter>Cursor "
"<replaceable>virtualCursor</replaceable></parameter>);"
msgstr ""
"int document.fromVirtualColumn(<parameter>int <replaceable>line</"
"replaceable></parameter>, <parameter>int <replaceable>virtualColumn</"
"replaceable></parameter>);\n"
"int document.fromVirtualColumn(<parameter>Kazalka "
"<replaceable>virtualnaKazalka</replaceable></parameter>);\n"
"Kazalka document.fromVirtualCursor(<parameter>Kazalka "
"<replaceable>virtualnaKazalka</replaceable></parameter>);"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3829
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Converts the given virtual cursor position to a <quote>real</quote> cursor "
"position, either returning an int or a Cursor object."
msgstr ""
"Pretvori podani položaj navideznega kazalca v <quote>pravi</quote> položaj "
"kazalca, bodisi vrne int ali objekt kazalca."

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:3837
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Cursor document.anchor(<parameter>int <replaceable>line</replaceable></"
"parameter>, <parameter>int <replaceable>column</replaceable></parameter>, "
"<parameter>Char <replaceable>character</replaceable></parameter>);\n"
"Cursor document.anchor(<parameter>Cursor <replaceable>cursor</replaceable></"
"parameter>, <parameter>Char <replaceable>character</replaceable></"
"parameter>);"
msgstr ""
"Cursor document.anchor(<parameter>int <replaceable>line</replaceable></"
"parameter>, <parameter>int <replaceable>column</replaceable></parameter>, "
"<parameter>Char <replaceable>character</replaceable></parameter>);\n"
"Cursor document.anchor(<parameter>Cursor <replaceable>cursor</replaceable></"
"parameter>, <parameter>Char <replaceable>character</replaceable></"
"parameter>);"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3838
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Searches backward for the given character starting from the given cursor. As "
"an example, if '(' is passed as character, this function will return the "
"position of the opening '('. This reference counting, &ie; other '(...)' are "
"ignored."
msgstr ""
"Iskanje danega znaka nazaj od danega kazalca. Na primer, če je '(' "
"posredovan kot znak, bo ta funkcija vrnila položaj začetnega '('. To štetje "
"sklicev, &ie; drugi '(...)' so prezrti."

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:3848
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Cursor document.rfind(<parameter>int <replaceable>line</replaceable></"
"parameter>, <parameter>int <replaceable>column</replaceable></parameter>, "
"<parameter>String <replaceable>text</replaceable></parameter>, "
"<parameter>int <replaceable>attribute</replaceable> = -1</parameter>);\n"
"Cursor document.rfind(<parameter>Cursor <replaceable>cursor</replaceable></"
"parameter>, <parameter>String <replaceable>text</replaceable></parameter>, "
"<parameter>int <replaceable>attribute</replaceable> = -1</parameter>);"
msgstr ""
"Kazalka document.rfind(<parameter>int <replaceable>vrstica</replaceable></"
"parameter>, <parameter>int <replaceable>stolpec</replaceable></parameter>, "
"<parameter>String <replaceable>text</replaceable ></parameter>, "
"<parameter>int <replaceable>atribut</replaceable> = -1</parameter>);\n"
"Kazalka document.rfind(<parameter>Kazalka <replaceable>kazalka</"
"replaceable></parameter>, <parameter>String <replaceable>besedilo</"
"replaceable></parameter>, <parameter>int <replaceable>atribut</replaceable > "
"= -1</parameter>);"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3849
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Find searching backwards the given text with the appropriate "
"<replaceable>attribute</replaceable>. The argument <replaceable>attribute</"
"replaceable> is ignored if it is set to <literal>-1</literal>. The returned "
"cursor is invalid, if the text could not be found."
msgstr ""
"Iskanje nazaj po danem besedilu z ustreznim <replaceable>atributom</"
"replaceable>. Argument <replaceable>atribut</replaceable> je prezrt, če je "
"nastavljen na <literal>-1</literal>. Vrnjeni kazalec je neveljaven, če "
"besedila ni bilo mogoče najti."

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:3858
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"int document.defStyleNum(<parameter>int <replaceable>line</replaceable></"
"parameter>, <parameter>int <replaceable>column</replaceable></parameter>);\n"
"int document.defStyleNum(<parameter>Cursor <replaceable>cursor</"
"replaceable></parameter>);"
msgstr ""
"int document.defStyleNum(<parameter>int <replaceable>vrstica</replaceable></"
"parameter>, <parameter>int <replaceable>stolpec</replaceable></parameter>);\n"
"int document.defStyleNum(<parameter>Kazalka <replaceable>kazalka</"
"replaceable></parameter>);"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3859
#, no-c-format
msgid "Returns the default style used at the given cursor position."
msgstr "Vrne privzeti slog, uporabljen na danem položaju kazalke."

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:3866
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"bool document.isCode(<parameter>int <replaceable>line</replaceable></"
"parameter>, <parameter>int <replaceable>column</replaceable></parameter>);\n"
"bool document.isCode(<parameter>Cursor <replaceable>cursor</replaceable></"
"parameter>);"
msgstr ""
"bool document.isCode(<parameter>int <replaceable>vrstica</replaceable></"
"parameter>, <parameter>int <replaceable>stolpec</replaceable></parameter>);\n"
"bool document.isCode(<parameter>Kazalka <replaceable>kazalka</replaceable></"
"parameter>);"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3867
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Returns <literal>true</literal>, if the attribute at the given cursor "
"position is not equal to all of the following styles: <literal>dsComment</"
"literal>, <literal>dsString</literal>, <literal>dsRegionMarker</literal>, "
"<literal>dsChar</literal>, <literal>dsOthers</literal>."
msgstr ""
"Vrne <literal>true</literal>, če atribut na danem položaju kazalca ni enak "
"vsem naslednjim slogom: <literal>dsComment</literal>, <literal>dsString</"
"literal>, <literal>dsRegionMarker </literal>, <literal>dsChar</literal>, "
"<literal>dsOthers</literal>."

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:3878
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"bool document.isComment(<parameter>int <replaceable>line</replaceable></"
"parameter>, <parameter>int <replaceable>column</replaceable></parameter>);\n"
"bool document.isComment(<parameter>Cursor <replaceable>cursor</replaceable></"
"parameter>);"
msgstr ""
"bool document.isComment(<parameter>int <replaceable>vrstica</replaceable></"
"parameter>, <parameter>int <replaceable>stolpec</replaceable></parameter>);\n"
"bool document.isComment(<parameter>Kazalka <replaceable>kazalka</"
"replaceable></parameter>);"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3879
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Returns <literal>true</literal>, if the attribute of the character at the "
"cursor position is <literal>dsComment</literal>, otherwise <literal>false</"
"literal>."
msgstr ""
"Vrne <literal>true</literal>, če je atribut znaka na položaju kazalca "
"<literal>dsComment</literal>, sicer <literal>false</literal>."

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:3887
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"bool document.isString(<parameter>int <replaceable>line</replaceable></"
"parameter>, <parameter>int <replaceable>column</replaceable></parameter>);\n"
"bool document.isString(<parameter>Cursor <replaceable>cursor</replaceable></"
"parameter>);"
msgstr ""
"bool document.isString(<parameter>int <replaceable>vrstica</replaceable></"
"parameter>, <parameter>int <replaceable>stolpec</replaceable></parameter>);\n"
"bool document.isString(<parameter>Kazalka <replaceable>kazalka</"
"replaceable></parameter>);"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3888
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Returns <literal>true</literal>, if the attribute of the character at the "
"cursor position is <literal>dsString</literal>, otherwise <literal>false</"
"literal>."
msgstr ""
"Vrne <literal>true</literal>, če je atribut znaka na položaju kazalca "
"<literal>dsString</literal>, sicer <literal>false</literal>."

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:3896
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"bool document.isRegionMarker(<parameter>int <replaceable>line</replaceable></"
"parameter>, <parameter>int <replaceable>column</replaceable></parameter>);\n"
"bool document.isRegionMarker(<parameter>Cursor <replaceable>cursor</"
"replaceable></parameter>);"
msgstr ""
"bool document.isRegionMarker(<parameter>int <replaceable>vrstica</"
"replaceable></parameter>, <parameter>int <replaceable>stolpec</replaceable></"
"parameter>);\n"
"bool document.isRegionMarker(<parameter>Kazalka <replaceable>kazalka</"
"replaceable></parameter>);"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3897
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Returns <literal>true</literal>, if the attribute of the character at the "
"cursor position is <literal>dsRegionMarker</literal>, otherwise "
"<literal>false</literal>."
msgstr ""
"Vrne <literal>true</literal>, če je atribut znaka na položaju kazalca "
"<literal>dsRegionMarker</literal>, sicer <literal>false</literal>."

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:3905
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"bool document.isChar(<parameter>int <replaceable>line</replaceable></"
"parameter>, <parameter>int <replaceable>column</replaceable></parameter>);\n"
"bool document.isChar(<parameter>Cursor <replaceable>cursor</replaceable></"
"parameter>);"
msgstr ""
"bool document.isChar(<parameter>int <replaceable>vrstica</replaceable></"
"parameter>, <parameter>int <replaceable>stolpec</replaceable></parameter>);\n"
"bool document.isChar(<parameter>Kazalka <replaceable>kazalka</replaceable></"
"parameter>);"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3906
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Returns <literal>true</literal>, if the attribute of the character at the "
"cursor position is <literal>dsChar</literal>, otherwise <literal>false</"
"literal>."
msgstr ""
"Vrne <literal>true</literal>, če je atribut znaka na položaju kazalca "
"<literal>dsChar</literal>, sicer <literal>false</literal>."

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:3914
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"bool document.isOthers(<parameter>int <replaceable>line</replaceable></"
"parameter>, <parameter>int <replaceable>column</replaceable></parameter>);\n"
"bool document.isOthers(<parameter>Cursor <replaceable>cursor</replaceable></"
"parameter>);"
msgstr ""
"bool document.isOthers(<parameter>int <replaceable>vrstica</replaceable></"
"parameter>, <parameter>int <replaceable>stolpec</replaceable></parameter>);\n"
"bool document.isOthers(<parameter>Kazalka <replaceable>kazalka</"
"replaceable></parameter>);"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3915
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Returns <literal>true</literal>, if the attribute of the character at the "
"cursor position is <literal>dsOthers</literal>, otherwise <literal>false</"
"literal>."
msgstr ""
"Vrne <literal>true</literal>, če je atribut znaka na položaju kazalca "
"<literal>dsOthers</literal>, sicer <literal>false</literal>."

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:3922
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"void document.indent(<parameter>Range <replaceable>range</replaceable></"
"parameter>, <parameter>int <replaceable>change</replaceable></parameter>);"
msgstr ""
"void document.indent(<parameter>Obseg <replaceable>obseg</replaceable></"
"parameter>, <parameter>int <replaceable>sprememba</replaceable></parameter>);"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3923
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Indents all lines in <replaceable>range</replaceable> by "
"<replaceable>change</replaceable> tabs or <replaceable>change</replaceable> "
"times <literal>tabSize</literal> spaces depending on the users preferences. "
"The <replaceable>change</replaceable> parameter can be negative."
msgstr ""
"Zamika vse vrstice v <replaceable>obseg</replaceable> za "
"<replaceable>spremeni</replaceable> zavihke ali <replaceable>spremeni</"
"replaceable> krat <literal>tabSize</literal> presledke, odvisno od "
"uporabniških nastavitev. Parameter <replaceable>spremeni</replaceable> je "
"lahko negativen."

#. Tag: title
#: development.docbook:3934
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Editor API"
msgstr "API urejevalnika"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3935
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In addition to the document and view API, there is a general editor API that "
"provides functions for general editor scripting functionality."
msgstr ""
"Poleg API-ja za dokumente in poglede je na voljo API za splošni urejevalnik, "
"ki nudi funkcije za skriptno funkcionalnost splošnega urejevalnika."

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:3942
#, no-c-format
msgid "String editor.clipboardText();"
msgstr "String editor.clipboardText();"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3943
#, no-c-format
msgid "Returns the text that currently is in the global clipboard."
msgstr "Vrne besedilo, ki je trenutno v globalnem odložišču."

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:3951
#, no-c-format
msgid "String editor.clipboardHistory();"
msgstr "Urejevalnik nizov.clipboardHistory();"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3952
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The editor holds a clipboard history that contains up to 10 clipboard "
"entries. This function returns all entries that currently are in the "
"clipboard history."
msgstr ""
"Urejevalnik hrani zgodovino odložišča, ki vsebuje do 10 vnosov v odložišče. "
"Ta funkcija vrne vse vnose, ki so trenutno v zgodovini odložišča."

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:3961
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"void editor.setClipboardText(<parameter>String <replaceable>text</"
"replaceable></parameter>);"
msgstr ""
"void editor.setClipboardText(<parameter>Niz <replaceable>besedilo</"
"replaceable></parameter>);"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3962
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Set the contents of the clipboard to <replaceable>text</replaceable>. The "
"<replaceable>text</replaceable> will be added to the clipboard history."
msgstr ""
"Nastavite vsebino odložišča na <replaceable>besedilo</replaceable>. "
"<replaceable>besedilo</replaceable> bo dodano v zgodovino odložišča."
